NG0201:2: shri tsan+d+ra gu h+ya ka la tan+t+ra /
NG0201:4: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud /
NG0201:5: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0201:6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NG0201:7: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed po lha mchog ya man+ta
NG0201:8: ka / lho phyogs gshin rje'i gnas dur khrod chen
NG0201:9: po gtum drag tshal zhes bya ba na /
NG0201:10: rgya khyon dpag tu med pa /
NG0201:13: rtse mo gnam lcags ur mo ru snang ba //
NG0201:14: 'khor lo gtams pa'i bad btags pa /
NG0201:15: 'khor lo dang gnam lcags kyi 'od phyogs bzhir 'phro ba //
NG0201:17: mchog chen dang rkang chen mchog phra mo'i bral gtang ba /
NG0201:18: bam chen gyi ka ba la chu srin gyis ka zhu can //
NG0201:20: gnam lcags thog gi tsha tsha 'phro ba /
NG0201:21: thod pa brtsegs pa'i 'bur phyung ba //
NG0201:22: zhing chen po'i bla re dang */
NG0201:23: chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan dang */
NG0201:25: dpal dar phyogs bzhir bkram pa /
NG0201:26: tsit+ta dmar po sprin du gtibs pa //
NG0201:27: rtse na me ri sna tshogs pas brgyan pa //
NG0201:28: keng rus kyi dur khrod dang */
NG0201:29: gnam lcags kyi khang bzangs dang *//
NG0201:31: ro myags kyi dur khrod la sogs pa dur khrod kyi gnas stong yod pa /
NG0201:34: skar ma phra men gyi mthongs yod pa /
NG0201:35: gza' skar mang pos brgyan pa /
NG0201:37: rlung nag gi grib so dang */
NG0201:38: keng rus kyi ri rab dang */
NG0201:40: mtha' lcags ri nag pos bskor ba de lta bu'i gnas de na /
NG0201:41: dur khrod kyi ro bam pa mang po brtsegs pa /
NG0201:42: mi gtsang bas yongs su gang ba rnam par ro rul ba dang */
NG0201:45: rnam par rul pa dmar ba /
NG0201:57: dur khrod kyi ro la 'dral ba dang */
NG0201:60: ro la longs spyod cher spyod pa dang */
NG0201:61: dur khrod kyi btsas pa mnam pa dang */
NG0201:66: de lta bu'i gnas de na stag dang */
NG0201:76: ling du khra dang srin bu ka ka ri //
NG0201:77: de la sogs pa sha za khrag 'thung dang *//
NG0201:78: rus pa 'cha' dang ldag myong byed pa dang *//
NG0201:79: blta dang dgod dang ngu dang cho nges 'debs //
NG0201:80: ku co 'don zhing mchong rgal byed pa dang *//
NG0201:81: drag po'i rkan rdebs ltas ngan skad sgrogs dang *//
NG0201:82: gzugs mi sdug dang 'dzum pa'i mdangs ston dang *//
NG0201:83: 'khor lo'i bro brdung lcags kyi mda' 'phen dang *//
NG0201:84: bshugs pa'i glu len mi mgo'i dung 'bud dang *//
NG0201:85: dar nag g.yab 'dor rang la rang khro dang *//
NG0201:86: sha za khrag 'thung drag po'i rkan rdebs dang *//
NG0201:87: brda dang gar bsgyur rdo rje'i thog 'phen dang *//
NG0201:88: gti mug sha yi dur khrod ri ltar spungs pa dang *//
NG0201:89: 'dod chags rak+ta'i dur khrod rba klong 'khyil pa dang *//
NG0201:90: rab tu 'jigs shing skyi g.ya'i gnas de na //
NG0201:91: 'jam dpal lha tshogs ya man+ta ka ni //
NG0201:92: phyogs bcu dus gsum bde gshegs 'khor rnams dang *//
NG0201:93: phyogs skyong gshin rje yab yum 'khor rnams dang *//
NG0201:94: 'jig rten rlag byed gshin rje gshed bzhi dang *//
NG0201:95: stong gsum mun par gtong par pho bdud mo bdud dang *//
NG0201:96: 'jig rten mes bsreg btsan po btsan mo dang *//
NG0201:97: smyo 'bog gtong bar byed pa'i ging gi 'khor tshogs dang *//
NG0201:98: drag po gnam lcags 'bebs pa lhag dang sman gyi 'khor //
NG0201:99: chu 'khyags khrag tu 'bebs pa khyab 'jug gza' yi 'khor dang *//
NG0201:100: mdze nad dz+wa la gdug pa klu yi 'khor dang *//
NG0201:101: srog gcod spu gri thogs pa gnod sbyin 'khor tshogs dang *//
NG0201:102: yams dang nad gtong ma mo'i 'khor tshogs dang */
NG0201:103: gzhan yang dri za'i rgyal po kha thun rak+sha la sogs dri za'i 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:104: shan pa nag po la sogs gshin rje'i 'khor sre dang *//
NG0201:105: na ga dza la la sogs klu yi 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:106: yak+sha mgo dgu la sogs gnod sbyin 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:107: stong gsum kun nyul srid pa khram 'debs la sogs ma mo'i 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:108: ha nu bag sha la sogs bdud kyi 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:109: shu bo srog len la sogs btsan gyi 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:110: dkar po snying 'byin la sogs srog bdag 'khor sde dang *//
NG0201:111: gzhan yang lha srin sde brgyad rang rang 'khor na yang *//
NG0201:112: nad gtod khram 'debs bsam gyis mi khyab dang *//
NG0201:113: gzhan yang 'dod pa'i bu mo'i tshogs rnams la //
NG0201:114: rgyal mo dang ni rgyal mo'i yang rgyal mo //
NG0201:115: blon mo dang ni yang blon mo //
NG0201:116: bran mo dang ni g.yog mo'i tshogs //
NG0201:117: de dag la sogs 'khor na yang *//
NG0201:118: 'du ba rnam bzhi'i nad bdag mo //
NG0201:119: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad gtong tshogs //
NG0201:120: bsam gyis mi khyab thabs cig bzhugs //
NG0201:121: be ta li dang ral gcig gnyis //
NG0201:122: g.yas nas 'khril te gnyis med bzhugs //
NG0201:123: g.yon nas mdun gyis bltas te bzhugs //
NG0201:124: gzhan yang gshin rje'i 'khor tshogs 'di lta ste //
NG0201:125: ya ma ra dza 'chi bdag dmar po dang *//
NG0201:127: brag gyon a ba glang mgo dang *//
NG0201:128: ya ba ti dang mig dmar dang *//
NG0201:129: mig dmar tel ba lha mchog dang *//
NG0201:130: chos kyi rgyal po ral pa tshar dgu dang *//
NG0201:131: thod dbyug la sogs 'khor dang bcas //
NG0201:132: e ka dza ti be ta li /
NG0201:133: mi srin nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:134: brag srin nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:135: sa bdag nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:136: mi bzang bdud mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:137: mtshan mo nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:138: byin ling nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:139: bdud mo nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:140: sa srin nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:141: klu srin nag mo mgo 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:142: lha mo nag mo go 'phyangs dang *//
NG0201:143: de ltar yum yang thabs cig go / yab yum 'khor yang 'di lta ste //
NG0201:144: ya ma ra dza 'khor rnams dag / bdud kyi rgyal po dregs can gsus po che dang *//
NG0201:145: gshin rje dmar po'i 'khor dag na //
NG0201:146: srog bdud mched gnyis gnas pa ni //
NG0201:147: srog bdag gnod sbyin dmar po dang *//
NG0201:148: bdud kyi rgyal po stag dgu spyan gcig dang *//
NG0201:149: gzhan yang kong tse brag 'joms 'khor dag na //
NG0201:150: bdud kyi rgyal po stag thabs gnas //
NG0201:151: a ba glang mgo'i 'khor dag na //
NG0201:152: bdud kyi rgyal po u 'bi gnas //
NG0201:153: lcogs pa mgo dgu'i 'khor dag na //
NG0201:154: bdud kyi rgyal po gur bdud dang *//
NG0201:155: bdud kyi rgyal po 'jug med gnas //
NG0201:156: ya ba ti yi 'khor dag na //
NG0201:157: bdud kyi rgyal po be'u log nag po dang *//
NG0201:158: bdud kyi rgyal po nag po spyi ring gnas //
NG0201:159: tel pa'i 'khor dag na bdud kyi rgyal po gling bzhi phur byed gnas /
NG0201:160: phya sangs kyi 'khor dag na bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud dkar po dang */
NG0201:161: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud dmar po dang */
NG0201:162: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud ljang nag dang */
NG0201:163: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud nag po dang */
NG0201:164: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud sngon po dang */
NG0201:165: bdud kyi rgyal po phya bdud phung byed 'ug pa'i mgo can dang */
NG0201:167: bdud mi lag spre 'u'i mgo can dang */
NG0201:168: bdud rngam chen mi lag dung gi rna cha gnas /
NG0201:169: ral pa tshar dgu'i 'khor na bse'i skyes bu gdug pa can gnas /
NG0201:170: stag mgo can gyi 'khor na klu bdud nag po sbrul gyi rgyu ma can dang */
NG0201:171: gri thogs ging gi pho nya bcu dang thabs cig tu bzhugs so //
NG0201:172: de'i tshe mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na
NG0201:173: rdo rje yang mdun gyis bltas te bka' nod pa'i
NG0201:175: de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos khams gsum dbang du bsdus srid gsum zil gyis mnan /
NG0201:176: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig ten gyi khams thams cad mun nag tu gtibs te /
NG0201:177: thugs ye shes kyi rtse las 'khor lo'i tshogs dang gnam lcags kyi gzer dang *//
NG0201:178: lcags kyu dang zhags pa'i tshogs dang */
NG0201:180: dril bu'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros te /
NG0201:183: (8)@#// dang ha la ha la dang */
NG0201:185: e a ra li hrim hrim dzahzhes 'brug stong gi
NG0201:186: sgra dus gcig tu ldir ba tsam gyi sgra bsgrags
NG0201:187: nas dbang du bsdus pas rang gi 'khor rnams kyang
NG0201:193: kun tu rab tu sngangs nas thams cad bde ba la bkod do //
NG0201:194: 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:195: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste skabs dang po'o // // de'i
NG0201:196: tshe dus na bcom ldan 'das la mthu stobs kyi
NG0201:198: gdug pa can gyi 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu
NG0201:199: thal mo sbyar nas bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad
NG0201:200: ces gsol to // e ma ho 'jigs byed chen po lags //
NG0201:201: bdag cag gdug byed 'khor rnams kun //
NG0201:203: stong gsum mun par gtong ba dang *//
NG0201:204: 'jig rten khams kun bsreg pa dang *//
NG0201:205: log rtog 'joms dang gnam lcags lce //
NG0201:206: smyo 'bog yams nad srog gcod dang *//
NG0201:207: mdze rigs gtong ba'i las 'di dag / bdag cag rnams kyi rang las lags //
NG0201:208: dpa' bo chen pos ci la bkyon //
NG0201:209: thugs rjes bred yang mi mnga' 'am //
NG0201:210: dpa' bo chen po khyod nyid ni //
NG0201:211: thugs rje byams pa'i mnga' bdag na //
NG0201:213: gdug pa'i gsung sgra ci la sgrog / thugs rje'i sprul pa ci la 'gyed //
NG0201:214: 'jigs byed chen pos bdag cag la //
NG0201:216: 'bangs la nan tan ma chung zhig / ces brjod de //
NG0201:217: so sor rang rang gi snying po 'di phul lo //
NG0201:218: om sngags sor bzhag a kro d+hi ka ya man+ta
NG0201:219: ka ya ma ra dza dz+wa la ram pa ya
NG0201:220: hum / ni kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ram hum /
NG0201:221: ya tra trag sha dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0201:222: ra rag mo kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni hum /
NG0201:223: om a rak+sha dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0201:224: rag mo kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ram ni hum /
NG0201:225: om tra trag po dz+wa la ram pa ya hum phat /
NG0201:226: tsit+ta kro to la kod+hi shwa ri dzra la ram pa ya hum /
NG0201:227: om raka sha ga ma ya snying rtsa ra ya dz+wa la ram hum /
NG0201:228: om ni ra tsa ru tsa kro d+hi shwa ri ti ni dz+wa la ram /
NG0201:229: om tra trag sha rag po dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0201:230: om shri dz+wa la ram pa kro d+hi shwa ri dza hum /
NG0201:231: om tra trag sha ni dz+wa la ram pa ya hum //
NG0201:232: om tra trag mo rak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri hum /
NG0201:233: om many+dzu shri nag po trag tra sha ni ya hum /
NG0201:234: om nag mo rak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri ni hum /
NG0201:235: om many+dzu shri badzra ma ro trag sha dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0201:236: om na ga kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ram pa ya hum /
NG0201:237: zhes phyogs skyong gi gshin rje rnams kyis phul lo //
NG0201:238: ru tra pa tra mu khrag dza ra khrag tsa pa ti yar pa dun hab swa ha /
NG0201:239: sa ma ya a be sha / ru tsa rak+sha
NG0201:240: chal pa a nr-i tri ma ra am ku sha
NG0201:241: dza dza / om bi sha wa du ru du ma shi kha dza la a ta swa ha /
NG0201:242: hri shag ru rag ram na ge tsit+ta tram ma ma yong za 'gram ha ha ga shal dzahdzah /
NG0201:243: ma snying kha rag snying kha rag ma ma rag sha ma ma rag mo thun thun /
NG0201:248: ra dza sa ma ya dza hum hum dza /
NG0201:249: ra li pra ma ni hum hum phat phat swa ha /
NG0201:250: tri tri ra dza tsa pa la a shug me dza dza /
NG0201:251: b+ha hu yag sha pu ro tso to ra hu
NG0201:252: ra ma trig be tshil ma khug yag sha thang
NG0201:253: ma thang me ya dza dza /
NG0201:254: om na ga ra dza ma ha ka la ti
NG0201:255: pa tsa sa kha sa kha shra ru hum dza
NG0201:256: dza / na ga ra dza dzahdzah /
NG0201:257: de dag la sogs 'jig rten khams dag na //
NG0201:258: gnas pa'i lha dang lha ma yin //
NG0201:259: nam mkha' lding dang dri za dang *//
NG0201:261: gnod sbyin srin po yi dwags dang *//
NG0201:262: sha za 'byung po grul bum dang *//
NG0201:263: srul po dang ni lus srul po //
NG0201:264: skem byed dang ni 'jigs byed dang *//
NG0201:265: smyo byed dang ni grib gnon dang *//
NG0201:266: gnon po dag ni nam gru dang *//
NG0201:267: de dag la sogs 'khor na yang *//
NG0201:268: sha za khrag 'thung bsam mi khyab //
NG0201:269: bka' nyan zer zhing srog snying phul //
NG0201:270: gnas pa'i 'khor rnams mgrin gcig tu //
NG0201:271: thal mo sbyar nas gus phul ba //
NG0201:272: dur khrod me tog sna tshogs ni //
NG0201:273: srin po ro dang ro chung dang *//
NG0201:274: mi ro dang ni rta ro dang *//
NG0201:275: ro phyed gzhogs ni phyed pa dang *//
NG0201:276: ro yi phreng ba ro brtsegs dang *//
NG0201:277: bam dang rul dang rul pa brul //
NG0201:278: b+han+da de bzhin sgal tshigs dang *//
NG0201:279: dbang po rkang dang rgyu ma dang *//
NG0201:280: sha khrag la sogs tshil bu dang *//
NG0201:281: go ro tsa na la sogs te //
NG0201:282: gzhan yang ro yi rnam pa ni //
NG0201:283: phye bye ba yang ma la sogs char du phab /
NG0201:285: he he dpa' bo 'jigs byed gdong *//
NG0201:286: bdag cag rnams kyi srog tig ste //
NG0201:287: dpa' bo lha rjes bzhes su gsol //
NG0201:288: bdag cag rnams kyi rang las dang *//
NG0201:290: dpa' bo lha rjes bzhes su gsol //
NG0201:292: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NG0201:294: nga ni dus gsum rnam pa ru //
NG0201:295: thams cad ma lus 'dul ba'i bdag / nga yis bka' rnams khyod kyis nyon //
NG0201:296: sems can yongs la 'tshe ma byed //
NG0201:297: khyed cag rnams kyi rang las ni //
NG0201:298: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig pa dang *//
NG0201:300: khyed kyi 'dul skal zas skal gyis //
NG0201:302: bka' bzhin nyan par zhal gyis bzhes te /
NG0201:303: rang dmar rang gis bcas so //
NG0201:304: de'i tshe de'i dus nam thu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na rdo rje gdan las bzhengs te /
NG0201:305: dam tshig rdo rje rtse dgu thugs kar bzung ste /
NG0201:306: pus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs te 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0201:307: legs so legs so ston pa'i 'khor //
NG0201:308: de ltar dus gsum thams cad du //
NG0201:309: sems can rnams la gnod pa dang *//
NG0201:310: 'jig rten khams su sbyor ngan ma btang bar /
NG0201:312: rang rang tshul bzhin bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0201:313: las thabs bya ba gang yin pa //
NG0201:314: da lta nyid du dbul bar gyis //
NG0201:316: te rang gi gnas su 'khod par gyur to //
NG0201:317: de nas dregs pa can gyi 'khor rnams kyis //
NG0201:318: e ma 'jigs byed chen po lags //
NG0201:319: bdag cag rang rang bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0201:320: las dang bya thabs thams cad byang *//
NG0201:321: byams mgon chen po nyid la 'bul //
NG0201:322: dpal chen po yis bzhes su gsol //
NG0201:324: bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen po dgyes pa chen por gyur te /
NG0201:325: zhal 'dzum pa mdzad nas 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NG0201:326: bka' yi phyogs skyong gshin rje dang *//
NG0201:327: gdug byed lha srin pho mo rnams //
NG0201:328: nyon cig khyod rnams gus par nyon //
NG0201:329: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / da lta dus gsum thams cad du //
NG0201:330: sems can rnams la gnod pa dang *//
NG0201:331: 'jig rten khams su sbyor ngan ma btang bar //
NG0201:332: nga yi dam las ma 'da' zhig / 'on tang sems can thams cad kyang *//
NG0201:333: bde la khyed kyang bde bar 'gyur //
NG0201:334: khyed kyi zas skal las thabs kyang *//
NG0201:335: lnga brgya'i tha ma byung ba dang *//
NG0201:336: sangs rgyas bstan pa mi gnas shing *//
NG0201:337: chos nyid bden pas mi 'dul te //
NG0201:338: bstan pa thams cad nub pa dang */
NG0201:339: las ngan mtshams med byed pa dang *//
NG0201:340: zas ngan lci ba za ba dang *//
NG0201:341: gos ngan dug hrul gyon pa dang *//
NG0201:342: ma gshin bstan pa byung ba dang *//
NG0201:343: mu stegs bstan pa dar ba'i tshe //
NG0201:344: khyed kyi zas skal thams cad kyang *//
NG0201:345: dus der 'byung bar ngas bshad gyi //
NG0201:346: nga yi dam las ma mda' zhig / ces bka' stsal to //
NG0201:347: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:348: gleng bslang ba'i skabs te gnyis pa'o // // de
NG0201:349: nas phyogs skyong gi gshin rje rnams kyis thams cad
NG0201:350: zhi bar byed pa'i ched du //
NG0201:351: bcom ldan 'das la phrin las zhi ba'i sgrub thabs 'di phul lo //
NG0201:352: rab tu dkar ba'i yul dag la //
NG0201:353: mgu ba'i sems dang ldan byas te //
NG0201:354: dad pas mgu pa'i las bya zhes //
NG0201:355: gshin rje gshed po nyid la phul //
NG0201:356: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0201:357: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:358: thams cad zhi bar bya phyir du //
NG0201:359: sa gzhi gnas dang ri brag dkar //
NG0201:360: zlum po nyams dga' bkra shis gnas //
NG0201:361: zhi ba'i las kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0201:362: zlum po dkar ba'i dkyil 'khor bris //
NG0201:363: lte bar bcas pa'i rtsibs brgyad la //
NG0201:364: mkhas pas bsgrim ste bri bar bya //
NG0201:365: dkar dang ldan pa'i zla gam la /
NG0201:366: gcig dang gsum nas mgo btsugs nas //
NG0201:367: khams gsum rab tu mgu ba'i phyir //
NG0201:368: nyams su len par byas la bsgrub //
NG0201:369: dbus su ye shes bdag po la //
NG0201:370: shar du nag 'joms chen po ste //
NG0201:371: lho ru+u ya ba ti zhes bya //
NG0201:372: nub tu khro bo rmig pa la //
NG0201:373: byang du bdud 'joms dgod par bya //
NG0201:374: shar lho lho nub nub byang dang *//
NG0201:375: byang shar mtshams su dgod pa ni //
NG0201:376: glang mgo kong tse gcod sbyong rje //
NG0201:377: las grub brgyad de go rim bzhin //
NG0201:380: yab yum gnyis med bris te dgod //
NG0201:381: zla gam gsum la ma mo gsum //
NG0201:382: sgo bzhir sgo srung ma rnams bri //
NG0201:383: de ni yum dang bcas pa rnams //
NG0201:384: khro bo yab dang sku mthun pa'o //
NG0201:385: sems dpa'i 'dug stangs gnas byas la //
NG0201:386: sgeg mo g.yon du brten byas la //
NG0201:387: sngags g.yog mdzes pa tshogs par byas //
NG0201:388: mgu ba'i phrin las brtsam par byas //
NG0201:389: skye tshe thal ba rus pa la //
NG0201:390: dzam b+ha la yi gzugs lta bur //
NG0201:391: byas pa'i snying gar bri ba ni //
NG0201:393: gang 'dod pa yi yi ge de //
NG0201:394: phat dang swa ha mda' ltar bya //
NG0201:395: ming byang gang ltar bris byas la //
NG0201:396: gang ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du gzhag / de la 'di yang rab tu brjod //
NG0201:397: om a kro badzra shan ti na ga badzra swa ha /
NG0201:398: om a kro te ka shan ting ba la tsum zhes brjod nas /
NG0201:399: snying gar brgyab na thams cad mgu nas dad pa'i sems kyis zhi bar gyur to //
NG0201:400: des ni zhi ba'i las byas zin nas phyogs bcu'i gdug pa zhi bar byas te /
NG0201:401: bdag la mi dga' ba med na las 'grub pa yin no //
NG0201:402: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:403: thams cad zhi bar bsgrub pa'i skabs te gsum pa'o
NG0201:404: // // de nas phyogs skyong gi gshin rje rnams
NG0201:405: kyi phrin las rgyas pa'i sgrub thabs 'di /
NG0201:406: thams cad rgyas par bya ba'i ched du /
NG0201:407: bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed gshin rje'i gshed chen po la phrin las rgyas pa'i sgrub thabs phul //
NG0201:408: rab tu ser zhing gser las grub //
NG0201:409: btso ma 'dra ba'i dbyibs can la //
NG0201:410: dpal rgyas sems dang ldan byas la //
NG0201:411: rgyas par bya ba'i sems kyis su //
NG0201:412: rgyas pa'i sgrub thabs bshad par mdzod //
NG0201:413: ces pa gshin rje gshed la phul //
NG0201:414: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0201:415: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:416: thams cad rgyas par bya phyir du //
NG0201:417: sa gzhi gnas dang ri rab ser //
NG0201:418: gru bzhi khod snyoms btso ma 'dra //
NG0201:419: rgyas par bya ba'i sems kyis su //
NG0201:420: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi pa yi tshul //
NG0201:421: ldong ros chag chag btab byas te //
NG0201:422: rnal 'byor dam pa blo ldan pas //
NG0201:423: thig ni gdab par rab tu brtsam //
NG0201:424: gser las grub pa'i thig skud la //
NG0201:425: dpal dang gzi mdangs bsod nams tshogs //
NG0201:426: 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i sems dang chas //
NG0201:427: slob ma dam pa las grub par //
NG0201:428: bsams la thig ni gdab par bya //
NG0201:429: pho brang gser la rtse mo g.yu //
NG0201:430: rdo rje'i brtsig pa gser las grub //
NG0201:431: gru chad sgo snams lcags las grub //
NG0201:432: rnal 'byor sngags pa blo ldan pas //
NG0201:433: thig bzhi re cha brgyad du 'gyur //
NG0201:434: mtha' nas thig gdab man ngag can //
NG0201:435: de la sogs pa bsam par bya //
NG0201:436: rin chen skyil krung 'dug byas la //
NG0201:437: rin chen rigs kyi ngos su blta //
NG0201:438: dbus su gsang sngags bdag po ste //
NG0201:439: phyogs phyogs sgo ba dam pa rnams //
NG0201:440: snga ma bzhin du bsgoms nas kyang *//
NG0201:441: rang sngags skyes bus de bskyed @#//
NG0201:443: om a kro te ka push+tim pha ya ni hum /
NG0201:444: om a kro te ka push+tim ti ba ta na s+t+wam /
NG0201:445: zhes pas bdag po yab yum la /
NG0201:447: rang rang bskyed pa dam pa ste //
NG0201:448: sngags dang ldan par ting 'dzin bsam //
NG0201:449: gzhug dang brtan dang mchod pa dang *//
NG0201:450: phyag byed pa la sogs pa yi //
NG0201:451: las kyi bya ba ma lus pa /
NG0201:452: thams cad ma lus tshang bar bya //
NG0201:453: bskyed dang grub pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NG0201:454: rgyas par bsnyen te thag mi ring *//
NG0201:455: rang grub 'bras bu de lags so //
NG0201:456: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yis //
NG0201:457: dngos grub dam pa rab ster zhes //
NG0201:458: 'dren pa dpa' bos yang dag bshad //
NG0201:459: de nas gzhan yang rab bshad pa /
NG0201:460: dkyil 'khor snga ma bzhin byas la //
NG0201:461: sa zhag gser las grub pa las //
NG0201:462: gzugs ni dam pa rab tu bya //
NG0201:463: phyir rgan gan rkyal mnan byas nas //
NG0201:464: hum push+tim a yu she swa ha /
NG0201:465: snying gar bris nas brjod bya ba //
NG0201:466: snying po sngags kyi dam pa ste //
NG0201:467: bla med dam pas rab tu bshad //
NG0201:468: om badzra push+tim a yuhpha la ba sham shri push+tim swa ha /
NG0201:469: brjod na thams cad rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NG0201:470: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:471: thams cad rgyas par bya ba'i skabs te bzhi pa'o
NG0201:472: // // de nas yang phyogs skyong gi gshin rje
NG0201:473: rnams kyis / phrin las dbang gi sgrub thabs 'di //
NG0201:474: 'jigs byed gshin rje'i gshed po la phul lo //
NG0201:475: rab tu dmar zhing zangs las grub //
NG0201:476: zangs las 'brel ba'i yul dag la //
NG0201:477: rang dbang med par dbang bsdus nas //
NG0201:478: 'du ba'i sems dang ldan byas te //
NG0201:479: dbang gi dkyil 'khor bshad par mdzod //
NG0201:480: ces pa gshin rje gshed la phul //
NG0201:481: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0201:482: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:483: thams cad dbang du bsdu phyir du //
NG0201:484: zangs sam dmar po'i sa dag la //
NG0201:486: legs par khod snyoms zin pa dang *//
NG0201:487: thig ni rab tu gdab par bya /
NG0201:488: lte ba tsan la rtsibs brgyad la //
NG0201:489: kun tu zla gam dbang gis mdzes /
NG0201:490: lte dbus gzhu bdungs bris byas nas //
NG0201:491: de steng bdag po dam pa gzhag / thams cad
NG0201:492: ma lus mchog tu dgug / ci la bya yang
NG0201:493: thogs chags med // ces ni yang dag bla med des //
NG0201:494: bshad par byas te rab tu bstan //
NG0201:495: gzhan yang rab tu bshad bya ba //
NG0201:496: sems kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NG0201:497: bla med yang dag nges pa'i lam //
NG0201:498: sangs rgyas byang chub la sogs rnams //
NG0201:499: gzhung las 'byung ba'i tshig don rnams //
NG0201:500: ma nor gsungs pa'i bka' bzhin du //
NG0201:502: de dag dgug par 'gyur bas na //
NG0201:503: phal pa gzhan lta smos ci dgos //
NG0201:504: sdud dang 'dren pa byang chub lam //
NG0201:506: nyung dkar rkang rjes sa'am gzhan //
NG0201:507: khrag gsum thal chen bsres byas la //
NG0201:508: ga bu'i nang du blugs byas la //
NG0201:511: skud pa dmar po zangs la sogs //
NG0201:512: bcings nas bsdams te dam dkris nas //
NG0201:513: dkyil 'khor gyi ni thog tu gzhag / nyung dkar zangs ni bsres byas te //
NG0201:514: dud pas ga bu de la bdug / de la bdug par gyur pa dang *//
NG0201:515: bzlas pa'i snying po brjod bya zhing *//
NG0201:516: lan grangs khri tshar du ma ru //
NG0201:517: brjod na sangs rgyas la sogs rnams //
NG0201:518: 'gugs par gyur na phal pa gzhan //
NG0201:519: smos ci dgos te nges par 'gugs //
NG0201:520: om badzra a kro many+dzu shri ba sham ma ho sarba ti la b+h+rum /
NG0201:521: lan grangs mang du brjod byas na //
NG0201:522: ji ltar bsam pa thams cad 'gugs //
NG0201:523: rgya shug bkrus pa'i khu ba dang *//
NG0201:524: mi yi lag pa'i khu ba gnyis //
NG0201:525: snga ma bzhin du dgug byas na //
NG0201:526: 'gugs par gyur zhes dpa' bos bshad //
NG0201:527: yang na rang gi lag kyang rung *//
NG0201:528: zhes gsungs pas thams cad ma lus par dbang du 'dus pas dper na phyogs phyogs thams cad nas //
NG0201:529: mtsho la sbrang ma 'du ba ltar 'dus te bdag
NG0201:530: gi dbang du gang la bya ba de dbang du
NG0201:531: 'gyur ro // zhes pa gshin rje gshed pos gsungs so //
NG0201:532: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:533: thams cad dbang du bya ba'i skabs te lnga pa'o
NG0201:534: // // de nas yang phyogs skyong gi gshin rje
NG0201:535: gshed rnams kyis phrin las drag po'i bsgrub pa 'di
NG0201:536: bzhin gshin rje gshed la phul lo /
NG0201:537: rab tu gnag cing gnam lcags 'dra //
NG0201:538: mon nag sog po khros pa'am //
NG0201:539: srin mo'i mdung rtse gshibs pa 'dra //
NG0201:540: khro bo chen po'i tshul chen gyis //
NG0201:541: gdug pa'i sems dang ldan byas te //
NG0201:542: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bshad par mdzod //
NG0201:543: ces pa gshin rje gshed la phul //
NG0201:544: gshin rje gshed pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0201:545: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:546: phyogs skyong gshin rje ma lus kun //
NG0201:547: khro bo'i tshogs su 'dul mdzad de //
NG0201:548: rang bzhin mthu chen 'di brjod do //
NG0201:550: dkyil 'khor snga ma bzhin byas te //
NG0201:551: bdag nyid khro bo chen po ste //
NG0201:552: yum yang de bzhin de yi 'od //
NG0201:553: yab yum gnyis med byin rlabs las //
NG0201:555: thig skud rgyus pa dag las byas //
NG0201:556: de ni las kyi thig ces bgyi //
NG0201:557: thig bzhi btab pas le'u tshe dgu / 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NG0201:558: kun tu gru bzhi gru chad can //
NG0201:559: gru chad rgyan ldan dur khrod rgyan //
NG0201:560: mdzes par bris te gzhan du min //
NG0201:561: bsten pa'i lha ste snga ma bzhin //
NG0201:562: bskyed pa'i sngags 'di brjod byas pas //
NG0201:563: bdag dang 'dra bar bskyed par bya //
NG0201:564: om a kro te ka hum a badzra be ta li rag sha man //
NG0201:569: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yoh /
NG0201:572: zhes brjod pa tsam gyis 'jig rten gyi khams 'di dag g.yos so //
NG0201:573: rab tu kun tu g.yos so //
NG0201:574: rab tu kun tu ldeg go / rab tu @#//
NG0201:578: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di dag rab tu g.yos par gyur to //
NG0201:579: de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i bdag nyid des 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0201:580: bcom ldan 'das rab tu gsung gi gsang sngags gsungs pas bdag cag spro lags so //
NG0201:581: 'jig rten du mthu chen 'di lta bu la bdag zhu ba lags so //
NG0201:582: de nas bcom ldan 'das rang bzhin khro bar mdzad pa de la /
NG0201:583: bdag mngon du sems can thams cad kyi don rab tu yang zhu bar 'tshal lags so //
NG0201:584: bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen pos 'dul bar mdzad pa des 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0201:585: om shri pa ra yak+sha g+hu h+ya sarba ta ki
NG0201:586: badzra ka la ru pa ma ra ya phat ces
NG0201:587: gsungs pas 'jig rten na dbang che ba dang */
NG0201:588: mthu che ba la sogs pa btul nas 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0201:589: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gang nas kyang *//
NG0201:590: gsung du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NG0201:592: phyogs bcur gsungs pa de dag yin //
NG0201:594: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:595: drag po'i sgrub thabs te thams cad btul nas cho
NG0201:596: 'phrul bstan pa'i skabs te drug pa'o // // de
NG0201:597: nas nan tan bskyed byas te /
NG0201:598: 'jig rten gshed pos drag po'i tsham rngams bshad par bya //
NG0201:599: 'jig rten bcud kyi gdug pa kun //
NG0201:600: tsham rngams glog ltar 'gyu ba las //
NG0201:601: ngo mtshar ya mtshan bsgrag par bya //
NG0201:602: e ma'o yab yum gnyis med rol pa'i mkha' dkyil nas //
NG0201:603: phyogs bcur 'phro ba byang chub sems //
NG0201:604: rigs kyi yab dang de bzhin btsun mo ni //
NG0201:605: rtag par bsgom ste de bzhin shes par bya //
NG0201:606: rdzas dang phyag rgya sngags dang bcud rnams ni //
NG0201:607: gzugs dang 'dod pa'i 'bras bu gang 'dod 'grub par rol //
NG0201:608: mi dge bcu dang ldan pa yis //
NG0201:609: rnam par 'dren pa des byas te //
NG0201:610: sngags dang phyag rgya rdzas rnams dang *//
NG0201:611: ga bu pad+ma dam pa dang *//
NG0201:612: kham sa pa yi 'jim pa ni //
NG0201:613: khrag sna gsum dang gi wang ngo *//
NG0201:614: de dag phrin las mchog yin te //
NG0201:616: bla med dpa' bos yang dag gsungs //
NG0201:617: phyogs bcu'i gdug pa ma lus kun //
NG0201:619: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:620: drag po'i skabs te bdun pa'o // // de nas
NG0201:621: yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos 'di skad
NG0201:622: ces gsungs so // 'gal ba cham la 'bebs 'dod na //
NG0201:623: dur khrod lung dang mthun pa'i gnas //
NG0201:624: dgon pa lta bur song nas ni //
NG0201:625: thog mar bsod nams tshogs kyang bsag / phyir bshags 'bul la sogs pa gdon //
NG0201:626: tsha tsha nye 'don la sogs bya //
NG0201:627: ye shes sems dpa' bsgom par bya //
NG0201:631: rtag tu gdon par dam yang bca' //
NG0201:632: grub pa'i nyi ma gang yin la //
NG0201:633: bsod nams tshogs ni ci nus bsag / de nas drag po byed 'dod na //
NG0201:634: tha chung bzhi yi mar ngo la //
NG0201:635: man+dal gtsang ma dris byugs la //
NG0201:636: dka' thub drag pa'i sdom pa byas //
NG0201:637: ku sha'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NG0201:638: mgo bo rma bya bzhin du dgug / ru rak+sha yi phreng ba bgrang *//
NG0201:639: mgon po nyid la gus byas te //
NG0201:640: sngon du 'gro ba'i bsnyen pa ni //
NG0201:641: yi ge bcu bdun nus thang gis //
NG0201:642: drug 'bum dag tu bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:643: de ni bsnyen pa dang po yin //
NG0201:644: phyis ni ri rab rtse mo la //
NG0201:645: gsum 'bum dag tu bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:646: de ni bsnyen pa gnyis pa yin //
NG0201:647: de nas dkyil 'khor gtsang ma'i steng *//
NG0201:650: gzhug pa'i spyan sngar nyis 'thum bzlas //
NG0201:651: de ni bsnyen pa gsum pa ste //
NG0201:652: bye ba gcig 'bum thon pa dang *//
NG0201:653: me tog la sogs mchod pa bya //
NG0201:654: phyi dang nang gi mchod pas mchod //
NG0201:655: bstod pa la sogs ci rigs bya //
NG0201:656: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas rtags rnams 'byung *//
NG0201:658: rtags ni bzang po 'byung ba ni //
NG0201:659: dngos grub la sogs blang bar bya //
NG0201:660: de nas drag po'i sbyor la 'jug / dur khrod ma la yar song la //
NG0201:661: mi skra re tshil rab blangs te //
NG0201:662: khrag chen dag tu spang bar bya //
NG0201:663: khrag sna tshogs kyi khu+u bas bkru //
NG0201:664: btsir la thal chen sa dkar gyis //
NG0201:665: mdog bsgyur phur bzhis brgyang la bskam //
NG0201:666: zla ba nag po'i tshes drug nas //
NG0201:667: brtsams te phyi gtor la sogs gtong *//
NG0201:668: mtho gzug dpang gzug gser skyems gtong *//
NG0201:669: srid pa'i lha 'dre sde brgyad la //
NG0201:670: bden bdar rgyab brten ma byed bsgo //
NG0201:671: khram dmar btab la khrag nag la //
NG0201:672: gshin rje'i drag sngags dag dang bsgrag / sho rde'u dkar nag brdeg par bya'o //
NG0201:674: zla ba nag po'i tshes drug ni /
NG0201:675: nyi shu gcig la dbu btsug nas //
NG0201:676: nyi shu drug ni tshun chad du //
NG0201:677: nus thang su ni bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:678: om hrihsh+t-ihbi kr-i ta na na hum hum phat phat /
NG0201:679: che ge mo ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0201:680: nyin phyed tshun chod bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:681: mchod dang bstod pa la sogs bya //
NG0201:682: brgyangs pa'i ras chen blangs nas su //
NG0201:683: gzhan med sol ba thal ba gnyis //
NG0201:684: ka na ka yi khu ba dang *//
NG0201:685: pra rtsisogs dang dug sna tshogs //
NG0201:686: til dang nyung dkar mar khu dang *//
NG0201:687: rang gi srin lag khrag sna ni //
NG0201:688: rnyed na phyi sa ra khrag dang *//
NG0201:689: ske tshe sa dkar tsan+dan dang *//
NG0201:690: rgya skyegs ldong ros yung bas bris //
NG0201:691: ma ra gshin rje'i lto bar bcug / dbang ni chung ma'i snying gar bya //
NG0201:692: zhi ba tsan+d+ra'i dbus su bya //
NG0201:693: rgyas par 'dod na glang pos so //
NG0201:696: lkugs pa lug gi khog par bya //
NG0201:697: gnan pa ri rab 'og tu bya //
NG0201:699: so'i rdzas dang las rnams ni //
NG0201:700: rig pa can gyis shes par bya //
NG0201:701: gshin rje zla gsang nag po 'di //
NG0201:702: zla ba gsang bar sngags pa yin //
NG0201:703: phrin las bya ba'i rim pa ni //
NG0201:704: gsang ba'i las su shes par bya //
NG0201:705: 'khor lo bca' ba'i rim pa ni //
NG0201:706: brgyangs pa'i ras la dug byugs la //
NG0201:707: ma da ldum bu thang phrom dang *//
NG0201:708: kha shog dug sna tshogs rnams la //
NG0201:709: rang gi srin lag khrag dang sbyar //
NG0201:710: snag tsha byas la bri bar bya //
NG0201:711: smyug gu bya rog 'ug pa'i sgro //
NG0201:712: mi grir shi ba'i skra la yang *//
NG0201:713: pir la sogs pa bya bar gsungs //
NG0201:714: sgro rtsa skud pa sngo dmar bcing *//
NG0201:715: 'khor lo bri ba'i rim pa yang *//
NG0201:716: gsang ba'i las su shes par bya //
NG0201:717: 'khor lo bri nas smon lam gdab //
NG0201:718: rang gi a mr-i ta la sogs //
NG0201:719: mchod cing bstod pa la sogs bya //
NG0201:720: bdag nyid ya man+ta kar bsgom //
NG0201:721: sku mdog stang zil nag po'am //
NG0201:722: chu rlabs nag po'i sprin dang 'dra //
NG0201:723: kham nag ral pa gyen du brdzes //
NG0201:724: sma ra kham la smin ma ser //
NG0201:725: glog 'gyu smin ma zhal bgrad pa //
NG0201:726: ljags 'gril tshems gtsigs gsus khyim tshe //
NG0201:727: lus dang yan lag na gas dkris //
NG0201:728: ro nye kha nas 'dzag kyang 'dzab kyang zlos //
NG0201:729: gdug pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin //
NG0201:730: de lta bu ru bdag nyid bsgom //
NG0201:731: mkhas pas rang gi rig pas dpyad //
NG0201:732: thod pa 'og ma khri steng ngam //
NG0201:733: za ma tog gi khri steng gzhag / steng ma'i thod pa smyug ma la /
NG0201:734: sngon dmar brgyangs la yas man gdab //
NG0201:735: nyi shu bdun gyi snga dro la //
NG0201:736: nyi ma ri rab rtser shar nas //
NG0201:737: stag lpags bgo zhing bgrod dkar 'gro //
NG0201:738: ru rak+sha yi phreng ba bgrang *//
NG0201:739: dbyug to thogs la sdigs mdzub bsgreng *//
NG0201:740: phyag kyang mi 'tshal lam mi bzur //
NG0201:741: phrad na gang yin brlag par byed //
NG0201:742: smra bcad byas te khri khri bzlas //
NG0201:743: rnal 'byor nang la gtam zer na //
NG0201:744: lag gi brda yis gdab par bya //
NG0201:745: skom dang zas ni 'dod pa'i phyir //
NG0201:746: lag gi brda yis blang bar bya //
NG0201:747: smras na rnal 'byor rang don zad //
NG0201:748: de yi phyir na lag brda bya //
NG0201:749: de yi tshe na 'di yang gdon //
NG0201:750: ya ma ra tsas do me ya che ge mo phra ma ya hum phat /
NG0201:751: de nas dmar thag chad bar du //
NG0201:752: khri khri bzlas pa bya ba yin //
NG0201:753: dmar thag chad nas snga gzhug bcad //
NG0201:754: phur bu gdab dang nyung dkar brdeg / pho nya bcol bskul drag tu bya //
NG0201:755: ma nyes dpang btsug cho nges gdab //
NG0201:756: nyin gnyis pa la 'di yang gdon //
NG0201:757: ya me do ru na yo da ya che ge mo rak+ta tsa ra hum phat /
NG0201:758: dmar thag chad nas sngags gzhug gcad //
NG0201:759: las kyi rim pa gong dang 'dra //
NG0201:760: nyin gsum po la 'di yang gdon //
NG0201:761: ya ta yo ni ra yak+she ya che ge mo mur tsa ya hum phat /
NG0201:762: dmar thag chad nas sngags gzhug gcad //
NG0201:763: las kyi rim pa gong dang 'dra //
NG0201:765: yak+she yats+tsha ni ra ma ya che ge mo zhig ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0201:769: mnan pa'i 'khor lor gzhug par bya //
NG0201:770: mnan pa'i gzugs ni ri rab bri //
NG0201:771: thod pa rabs chad nag po'am //
NG0201:772: ngag dig glen pa bkra mi shis //
NG0201:773: nang du bcug la re bar gril //
NG0201:774: lha khang them pa'i 'og dag gam //
NG0201:775: ro khang dur khrod dag tu gnan //
NG0201:776: gtad pa gshin rje nyid la ste //
NG0201:777: dong ni ral pa tshar dgu'o //
NG0201:778: rgya mtsho chen po'i 'og tu gnan //
NG0201:779: gnan pa'i lha ni ral pa tshar dgu ste //
NG0201:780: chu nag 'dra ba'i gzugs chen la //

NG0201:782: gshin rje'i dbyug pa nag po thogs //
NG0201:783: de lta bu yi dngos po la //
NG0201:784: bdag gis ral gri'i phyag rgya bcas //
NG0201:785: sa gzhi chen po gshags nas ni //
NG0201:786: gshin rje yi ni lag tu gtad //
NG0201:787: ri rab chen po nyid kyis mnan //
NG0201:788: don yod grub pa'i pho brang gdab //
NG0201:789: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:790: drag po bca' gzhi'i skabs te brgyad pa'o // //
NG0201:791: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos
NG0201:793: drag po'i las dag byed 'dod pas //
NG0201:794: yid 'ong mthun pa'i gnas lam du //
NG0201:795: rnal 'byor mos dang dad pa yis //
NG0201:796: bla ma mnyes byas dbang dag mnos //
NG0201:797: lung dang man ngag thob nas kyang *//
NG0201:798: brtson 'grus chen pos myur du bsgrub //
NG0201:799: gnas dang gzungs ma dag dang ni //
NG0201:800: lta spyod ldan pa dag gis kyang *//
NG0201:801: 'khor lo'i rgyu dang snag tsha'i rgyu //
NG0201:802: smyug gu'i rgyu dang dus phyogs dang *//
NG0201:803: mkhas pas zla gsang rgyud nas bshad //
NG0201:804: drag po sa yi man+dal yang *//
NG0201:805: bskrad dang gzung dang bslang ba sogs //
NG0201:806: mkhas pas zla gsang rgyud las so //
NG0201:807: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bri ba yang *//
NG0201:808: thig g.yog mtshan ldan gzungs ma la //
NG0201:809: ba su ta yi thig dag thal chen tshon rgyu dang *//
NG0201:810: rgyu dang man ngag shes pas bya //
NG0201:811: shar nub lho dang phyogs dang mtshams //
NG0201:812: phyogs cha rig pas blta bar bya //
NG0201:813: stegs bu 'dom gang gru bzhi la //

NG0201:815: zla gsang rgyud las shes par bya //
NG0201:816: byin rlobs gnam sa thig btab pa //
NG0201:817: zla gsang las las shes par bya //
NG0201:818: thig ni brgyad kyi cha ru bya //
NG0201:819: thig skor bzhi dang ldan pa la //

NG0201:828: bcu gnyis rtsibs dang ldan pa la //

NG0201:836: rdo rje rwa ba'i phyi rol du //
NG0201:837: sgo dang sgo khyud ldan pa bya //
NG0201:839: gru gsum gnag / ling tse bzhi ni phyogs dang sbyar //

NG0201:841: bcu gnyis drag po bcu drug rgyas //
NG0201:842: rdo rje lcags la gru chad ljang *//
NG0201:843: mtha' ma lcags ri sgo ni phyogs dang sbyar //
NG0201:844: gshin rje lha ni lho shar byang *//

NG0201:846: sha khrag rdzas dang me tog sngo //
NG0201:847: lho yi phyogs nas dbul bar bya //
NG0201:848: drag po rdzas kyi ga bu de //
NG0201:849: mnga' gsol dbang bskur byas nas kyang *//
NG0201:850: dkyil 'khor steng du bzhugs su gsol //
NG0201:851: 'khor lo bcu gnyis rtse la yang *//
NG0201:852: phur pa bcu gnyis rim gyis so //
NG0201:853: 'khor lo bcu drug rtse mo la //
NG0201:854: ke seng bcu drug phur pa dgod //
NG0201:855: sgo bzhi bse mo'i phur pa bzhi //
NG0201:856: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rtsad la yang *//
NG0201:857: dbang phyug mnga' gsol bar khyams la'o //
NG0201:858: bsgrub bya'i dam rdzas gtor ma yang *//
NG0201:859: bsgrub bya'i lha ste dpal la gcig / bsnyen pa'i
NG0201:860: lha ste ya man+ta kar gcig / las su gnyer
NG0201:861: ba'i lha ste nyi ma bzhi pa la gcig /

NG0201:863: khram thogs bdud la gcig / ma mo'i tshogs la
NG0201:864: gcig kyang dbul // zhi khro'i lha la las gzhung bsrang *//
NG0201:865: de nas 'chi bdag las gzhung bsrang *//
NG0201:866: zhes pa gshin rje gshed pos bshad //
NG0201:867: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:868: dkyil 'khor gyi bca' gzhi'i le'u ste dgu pa'o //
NG0201:869: // de nas mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag
NG0201:870: na rdo rje la 'di skad ces zhus so //
NG0201:871: he he dpa' bo 'jam pa'i mgon //
NG0201:872: phyogs skyong 'dul ba'i gshed po ste //
NG0201:874: tshul bzhin bsgrub pa'i don bshad kyang *//
NG0201:875: phrin las gzhung bsrang ji ltar bsrang *//
NG0201:876: ting 'dzin rnam gsum ji ltar bskyed //
NG0201:877: spyan drang bzhugs mchod ji ltar bgyi //
NG0201:879: dpa' bo chen pos bka' stsol cig / de nas
NG0201:880: bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos phrin las kyi
NG0201:882: dmar nag brag gam sog po khros pa 'dra //
NG0201:883: mi ro mang po yod cing rkang gcig shing gi rtsar //
NG0201:884: gcan gzan mang po 'grul zhing 'dab chags mang po 'du //
NG0201:885: lha 'dre mang po tshogs sar drag po'i gnas btsal te //
NG0201:886: mchod pa bshams la dkon mchog gsum po spyan drangs la //
NG0201:887: mnyes par bya phyir mchod pa rnam lnga 'bul //
NG0201:888: sa bdag sa srin mang po spyan drangs la //
NG0201:889: gtor ma chang phud mchod rdzas byin brlabs te //
NG0201:890: bsngos la sa slong tshig kyang brjod //
NG0201:891: nga rgyal rdo rje khro bo yis //
NG0201:892: rdo rje 'gros kyis sa bskor te //
NG0201:893: sa bslang sa gzhi spyang ba ni //
NG0201:894: bdag nyid khro bor gyur pa'i thugs ka nas //
NG0201:895: ram las ye shes me yis dngos mtshan kun bsregs te //
NG0201:896: yam las rlung gis gtor nas kham las chu yis bkrus //
NG0201:897: don dam stong pa'i dang du bsgom //
NG0201:898: de nas kun rdzob mtshams bcad @#//
NG0201:900: dkyil 'khor rgya bcad dbus su bskor bar bya //
NG0201:901: rin chen sna lnga ldan pa'i chang phud sba //
NG0201:902: phung shul sa blangs mi rta'i khrag gis ljib //
NG0201:903: sa sbyangs grub nas dur khrod chag chag gdab //
NG0201:904: rdo rje dri chu rak+ta dang *//
NG0201:905: dug la sogs pa'i chag chag rab tu gdab //
NG0201:906: de nas thig gdab thig gi rgyu bstan pa //
NG0201:907: zhing gi rgyu ma yugs mo'i skra //
NG0201:908: gri bo log non ro sha kha ral skras //
NG0201:909: thig skud byas la byin brlab thig kyang gdab //
NG0201:910: shar dang nub dang de bzhin byang *//
NG0201:911: de bzhin byang shar mtshams su bya'o //
NG0201:912: shar lho nub byang lho nub dang *//
NG0201:913: de bzhin byang shar mtshams su'o //
NG0201:914: dbus kyi shar nub dbus kyi lho dang byang *//
NG0201:915: snam bu brgyad la gnyis gnyis bcu drug dag tu bshad //
NG0201:916: mtha' thig la sogs bri ba'i las su shes //
NG0201:917: dang po dur khrod ras brgyangs te //
NG0201:918: 'khor lo bri ba man ngag las su shes //
NG0201:919: ma ra ya yi gzugs bcas la //
NG0201:920: dri chen dri chu rkang rjes sa //

NG0201:922: nang du tsher ma rus pas dgang *//
NG0201:923: ming rus mgo dang snying gar gzhug / lus la dug chu tsha ba gsum gyis byung *//
NG0201:924: skud pa sngon dmar byad sngags bzlas //
NG0201:925: skud pa nag po dag gis ske nas gdags //
NG0201:926: de nas thod pa mtshan ngan zhig btsal te //
NG0201:927: lus kyi ngos la yab bri spyi bo'i ngos la yum //
NG0201:928: de bzhin gzugs de 'khor lo'i bar du gzhug /
NG0201:929: 'khor lo thod pa'i nang du gzhug / mi lpags
NG0201:931: de nas phur pa bcu gcig la //

NG0201:933: rgyal po dag kyang brdeg / gru gsum dbyings nas
NG0201:935: spyan drang bzhugs su gsol te rang rang gdan la dgod //
NG0201:936: shar du kong tse brag gyon dri za 'dul //
NG0201:937: lho phyogs 'chi bdag ya ba ti //
NG0201:938: nub tu klu bdag rmig pa 'dul //
NG0201:939: byang du lha mchog gnod sbyin 'dul //
NG0201:940: shar lhor glang mgo me lha 'dul //
NG0201:941: lho nub mig dmar srin po 'dul //
NG0201:942: nub byang tel pa rlung lha 'dul //
NG0201:943: byang shar las grub dbang ldan 'dul //
NG0201:946: de dag gshin rje'i yum rnams kyang *//
NG0201:947: phur pa rang rang grib la gnas //
NG0201:948: ku ma da ri bdud 'dul shar //
NG0201:949: k+shu ma da ri btsan 'dul lho //
NG0201:950: kang ka da ri gza' 'dul nub //
NG0201:951: tsa mun da ri klu 'dul byang *//
NG0201:952: phur pa bzhi yang sgo bzhi la'o //
NG0201:953: gshin rje'i bris sku lho ru dgram //
NG0201:954: thod pa 'khor lo bcas pa ste //
NG0201:955: gru gsum phub ste steng du bzhag / g.yang gzhi 'phan la sogs pas brgyan //
NG0201:956: sha chen tshil chen keng rus dang *//
NG0201:957: khrag chen la sogs ci mang sbyar //
NG0201:958: ske thag gshin rje'i phur la gdab //
NG0201:959: gtor ma la sogs gong bzhin gzhag / nyung dkar ske tshe dug khrag rnams //
NG0201:960: g.yag g.yon dag tu gzhag par bya //
NG0201:961: mchod pa lnga dang gtor ma @#//
NG0201:963: chang phud la sogs bshams nas kyang *//
NG0201:964: dkon mchog gsum po spyan drangs la //
NG0201:965: mchod dang sdig pa bshags pa bya //
NG0201:966: de nas chos kyi srung ma rnams //
NG0201:967: lha mgon klu mgon la sogs dang *//
NG0201:968: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu dang *//
NG0201:969: 'gro ba drug rnams la sogs par //
NG0201:970: gtor ma bsngos la bden pa bdar //
NG0201:971: 'di yi grogs ma byed par bsgo //
NG0201:972: dkyil 'khor bskor zhing dpang yang gzug / mtha' ma rdo rje'i 'gros kyis bskor //
NG0201:973: bgegs rnams bskrad la mtshams rnams gcad //
NG0201:974: de nas lho ru kha yang blta //
NG0201:975: de bzhin nyid dang kun tu snang *//

NG0201:983: phyag mtshan rdo rje gcig tu gyur //
NG0201:985: rdo rje mthing nag 'od du gyur //

NG0201:989: zhal gsum phyag drug mthing nag la //
NG0201:990: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //

NG0201:993: ral pa'i rtse nas rgya mtsho 'khrugs //

NG0201:996: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum ma he brdzis //

NG0201:998: klad par om bsam mgrin par amh /

NG0201:1003: a+om sarba ta tha ga ta ka ya swa ka tsit+ta at+ma ko\u0f85ham //

NG0201:1008: g.yon phyogs zhing gi gdan steng du /

NG0201:1125: ka kha dbyangs yig la sogs te //
NG0201:1126: yi ge rnams kyi dgod phyogs so //
NG0201:1127: gnyis ka rnal mar bris gyur na //
NG0201:1128: yab yum cho rol song gyur te //
NG0201:1130: de la dgug dang gnan dang myos //
NG0201:1131: bskrad dang myos 'bros la sogs pa //
NG0201:1132: zla gsang las las shes par bya //
NG0201:1133: de ltar 'khor lo bri ba dang *//
NG0201:1134: rabs chad pho mo'i thod pa dang *//
NG0201:1135: 'khor lo gong ma ltar bris la //
NG0201:1136: de yi bar du bcug byas la //
NG0201:1137: tshon skud nag pos phyogs bzhir bcings //
NG0201:1138: gzhan yang zhi rgyas las byed na //
NG0201:1139: kham sa'i gab tser gong bzhin gzhug / so so'i rigs kyi gzungs thag gdags //
NG0201:1140: de yis gang yang gdon mi za //
NG0201:1141: las rnams 'grub ces gshed pos gsungs //
NG0201:1142: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:1143: 'khor lo bca' gzhi'i skabs te bcu gcig pa'o //
NG0201:1144: // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen
NG0201:1146: dang por ting 'dzin rnam gsum gyis //
NG0201:1147: las kyi bya ba gzhan zin nas //
NG0201:1149: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / hum /
NG0201:1150: log rtog gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i chos nyid de //
NG0201:1151: sems kyis brtags pas cir yang mi snang ste //
NG0201:1152: mi g.yo mi bsam chos kyi dbyings nyid ngang *//
NG0201:1153: rig pa spros bral mi rtog bsgom //
NG0201:1154: om ma ha shu'u n+ya ta dz+nya na badzra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0201:1156: dbyings nyid nam mkha' stong pa'i rang bzhin las //
NG0201:1157: rang sems mam las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor te //
NG0201:1158: 'od kyi thig le nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsam //
NG0201:1161: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od kyi dkyil 'khor te //
NG0201:1162: hum las rdo rje rtse lnga rab 'bar ba //
NG0201:1163: brtan cing mi g.yo rdo rje 'bar bar bsgom //
NG0201:1167: rdo rje'i gur dang sa gzhi bsgom //
NG0201:1169: 'jig rten khams gsum ma lus kun //
NG0201:1170: ram yam kham gis bsreg sbyangs nas //
NG0201:1171: ye shes 'bar ba lnga ni rim gyis bsgom //
NG0201:1172: e yam ram bam sum kem e /
NG0201:1173: nam mkha' stong pa'i rang bzhin la //
NG0201:1174: brtan pa rlung gi dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NG0201:1175: de steng ram las gru gsum me //
NG0201:1176: bam las bdud rtsi ngo bo las //
NG0201:1177: smin pa sa yi dkyil 'khor bsam //
NG0201:1178: keng rus ri rab steng dag tu //
NG0201:1179: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgom //
NG0201:1180: b+h+rum las ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas mchog / gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bcas //
NG0201:1181: dkyil 'khor tshul du gzhal yas bsgom //
NG0201:1183: gzhal yas dbus su nyi zla'i steng *//
NG0201:1184: chu skyes steng du sems nyid d+hih /
NG0201:1187: om a ra pa tsa na d+hih //
NG0201:1188: 'jam pa'i rdo rje gzhon tshul zur phud can //
NG0201:1189: sku ni gser mdog zhi ba'i cha lugs 'chang *//
NG0201:1190: zhal gcig phyag gnyis shes rab ral gri g.yas //
NG0201:1191: gzhon nu sku sprul phyag g.yon ut+pal te //
NG0201:1192: mi 'gyur shes rab po tis mtshan par bsgom //
NG0201:1193: snying dkyil nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor d+hihlas ni //
NG0201:1194: 'od 'phros phyogs bcu'i bde gshegs spyan drang nas //
NG0201:1195: nyi ma la zhugs mgon po nyid dang ni //
NG0201:1196: bde gshegs spyan drangs 'od kyi gong bur bsam //
NG0201:1197: 'od phung de nyid kha dog nag po'i hum //
NG0201:1198: 'phro 'du'i tshul gyis rdo rje rtse lnga gnag / shin tu 'bar zhing brtan pa nyid du bsgom //
NG0201:1199: badzra de las 'od zer rab 'phros pas //
NG0201:1201: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NG0201:1202: dbu gsum phyag drug 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0201:1203: gyad kyi 'dor thabs yi dwags gnon //
NG0201:1204: tri shul ral gri dbyug dgra s+t+wa //
NG0201:1205: 'byin pa'i phyir na phyag brgyad pa //
NG0201:1206: lcags kyu'i mtshon cha phyag na bsnams //
NG0201:1207: thod pa shag ti to ma ra //
NG0201:1208: sdigs dang zhags pa g.yon pa ste //
NG0201:1209: las la gsang ba'i yum gnyis kyang *//
NG0201:1210: g.yas g.yon gnyis su bsam pa yang *//
NG0201:1211: lus dang grib ma'i tshul du bsgom //
NG0201:1212: om a kro te ka ya man+ta ka hum /
NG0201:1213: be ta li yak+sha rak+sha hum hum //
NG0201:1214: pad+ma rdo rje byin brlab pa //
NG0201:1215: hum las rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0201:1216: bam las pad+mar byin brlabs nas //
NG0201:1217: brda' yis bskul ba tshul bzhin bya //
NG0201:1224: hum /    hum /    hum /   hum /   hum /  hum /
NG0201:1225: yab yum mkha' la hum bcu gnyis //
NG0201:1226: gshin rje bcu gnyis gsal ba'i rtsa //
NG0201:1227: 'khor rnams bsam pa'i dbang gis bskyed //
NG0201:1228: spyan drar bzhugs mchod tshul bzhin bya //
NG0201:1229: gshin rje gshed pos gsungs pa'i don //
NG0201:1230: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /

NG0201:1232: mthu stobs kyi bdag pos 'di skad ces zhus so //
NG0201:1233: gshin rje gshed pos gsungs pa'i don //
NG0201:1234: bdag sdud 'di yi don shod cig / bsod nams tshogs kyi yan lag bshad pa dang *//
NG0201:1235: bsnyen pa dang ni nyer bsnyen po //
NG0201:1236: dngos grub len dang bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0201:1237: 'chi bdag bdud dang gshin rje'i bsnyen pa dang *//
NG0201:1238: bsad pa las kyi bsnyen pa gang la bgyi //

NG0201:1240: nyon cig lag na rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:1241: 'chi bdag rnams kyi bshad bya ba //
NG0201:1242: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / dang por yid 'thad gnas btsal nas //
NG0201:1244: bsod nams dag pa'i tshogs bsag pa //
NG0201:1245: tshad med bzhi dang yan lag lnga //
NG0201:1246: bdun gyis kun rdzob sems bskyed la //
NG0201:1247: don dam byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa //
NG0201:1248: rnam par mi rtog ngang du ci rigs bsgom //
NG0201:1249: de ltar ma rtogs rnams la snying rje bskyed //
NG0201:1250: ting 'dzin gnyis kyis rang rgyud dag sbyangs nas //
NG0201:1251: rig pa'i ye shes yi ge mum du gsal //
NG0201:1252: spro bsdus 'jam dpal sems dpa'i skur bskyed de //
NG0201:1253: gong ma lta bu'i las dag bya ba ni //
NG0201:1254: bsod nams tshogs kyi las dag go / rdo rje
NG0201:1255: sems dpas rab tu sems la zhog / dpal zla
NG0201:1257: bsod nams tshogs kyi yan lag gi skabs te bcu
NG0201:1258: gsum pa'o // // de nas 'jam dpal gshin rjes
NG0201:1260: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0201:1261: gong gi bsod nams tshogs la gnas pa yang *//
NG0201:1262: phyi nang gsang ba dag gi mtshams bcad nas //
NG0201:1263: zhi khro la sogs bskang bshags dag par bya //
NG0201:1264: de nas ting 'dzin rnam gsum spro bsdu yis //
NG0201:1265: bdag nyid gshin rje'i gshed kyi skur bskyed la //
NG0201:1266: g.yon du yum skyed mdun du sras mchog bskyed //
NG0201:1267: g.yas su yum bskyed la sogs rab byas te //
NG0201:1268: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs pa dang *//
NG0201:1269: ye shes chen po lnga ru dbang bskur nas //
NG0201:1270: ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drang dang *//
NG0201:1271: mchod bstod la sogs rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:1272: bdag thugs phyag rgya bzhi las mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi //
NG0201:1273: spros te spyan drangs phyag 'tshal gzhug pa dang *//
NG0201:1274: mchod pa la sogs lha mo bzhis byas te //
NG0201:1275: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i 'dzab grangs dbul ba ni //
NG0201:1276: rang rig ye shes gnas su dag pa'i rtags //
NG0201:1277: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang *//
NG0201:1279: dbyings nyid gting mtha' med pa las //
NG0201:1280: skye 'gro gzugs su snang ba las //
NG0201:1281: gshed po yab dang yum du ma gyur gang yang med //
NG0201:1282: dper na til 'bru mar gyis gang ba bzhin //
NG0201:1283: bdag nyid tsit+ta'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0201:1284: rin chen gur phub 'dra ba ru //
NG0201:1287: rig pa'i ye shes yongs su grub pa'i rtags //
NG0201:1288: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang gsal bar bsgom //
NG0201:1289: thugs kar rdo rje rtse lnga bsam //
NG0201:1290: de yi bum pa dag la yang *//
NG0201:1291: sngags kyi sa bon yi ge hum //
NG0201:1292: de mtha' bcu bdun bskor bar bsgom //
NG0201:1293: lha rnams thugs kar de bzhin ci 'drar bsgom //
NG0201:1294: de nas bdag nyid thugs ka nas //
NG0201:1295: sngags bzlas ljags steng sngags 'phros pas //
NG0201:1296: 'dom gang pha rol phyin tshad du //
NG0201:1297: sku rnams phra mor gyur nas kyang *//
NG0201:1298: de dag zhal nas gsang sngags bzlas pa las //
NG0201:1299: 'od zer mchod pa'i lha dang lha mor gyur //
NG0201:1300: phar 'phros 'phags pa rnams la 'od zer phog / sku gsung thugs nyid mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0201:1301: 'od zer de dag bdag la tshur 'dus pas //
NG0201:1302: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs bdag la thim par bsam //
NG0201:1303: de ltar bsnyen pa drug 'bum byas pa ni //
NG0201:1304: sngon du 'gro ba'i bsnyen pa ste //
NG0201:1305: lag na rdo rjes rab tu zung *//
NG0201:1306: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las //
NG0201:1307: lha yi bsnyen pa bgyi ba'i skabs te bcu bzhi
NG0201:1308: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed
NG0201:1309: chen pos 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0201:1310: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0201:1311: man+dal chag chag legs btab la //
NG0201:1312: me tog bris sku la sogs bkod nas kyang *//
NG0201:1313: gong ma lta bu'i bsnyen pa gsum 'bum bzlas pa ni //
NG0201:1314: nye ba'i bsnyen pa yin zhes gshed pos bshad //
NG0201:1315: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las //
NG0201:1316: nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i skabs te bco lnga pa'o //
NG0201:1317: // de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos
NG0201:1319: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu / gong ma'i las rnams mthar phyung ste //
NG0201:1320: nye bsnyen las la gnas nas kyang *//
NG0201:1321: des ni rtags bzang mthong bar 'gyur //
NG0201:1322: grub pa'i rtags ni byung ba dang *//
NG0201:1323: khyad par dngos grub rdzas bsags te //
NG0201:1324: dmar ser ba yi 'o ma dang *//
NG0201:1325: mar dang sbrang rtsi sbyar ba dang *//
NG0201:1326: dngos grub rdzas rnams bkod nas kyang *//
NG0201:1327: bdag gi thugs las 'od zer phar 'phros pas //
NG0201:1328: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs dam bskul //
NG0201:1329: bris sku dngos grub rdzas la thim bsams shing *//
NG0201:1330: 'bum phrag gcig gi bzlas pa bya'o //
NG0201:1331: g.yal dang sbrid pa brkyang bskum gnyid kyang spang *//
NG0201:1332: de bzhin spangs pas ci bsam 'grub ces bshad //
NG0201:1333: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:1334: bsgrub pa chen po'i skabs te bcu drug pa'o //
NG0201:1335: // de nas yang gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad
NG0201:1336: ces gsungs so // nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:1337: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0201:1338: 'bum phrag gcig gi bsnyen pa yang *//
NG0201:1339: snga ma'i las su bya bar gsungs //
NG0201:1340: bdag nyid gshed po'i mthu ldan pas //
NG0201:1341: mdun gyi ri rab bsam pa dang *//
NG0201:1344: bdag gi thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0201:1346: de mthar bzlas pa'i yig 'brus bskor bsam la //
NG0201:1347: de bzhin bdag gi thugs ka nas //
NG0201:1348: sngags ni rab tu bzlas pa las //
NG0201:1350: de yi 'od zer phog gyur pas //
NG0201:1351: thugs dam bskul nas dar cig kyang *//
NG0201:1353: gshed po'i bka' nyan gsung sdod bsam //
NG0201:1354: las la sbyor ba'i bsnyen pa ste //
NG0201:1355: 'chi bdag las kyi gshin rje rnams //
NG0201:1356: gnas su gtong ba gshed pos bshad //
NG0201:1357: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:1358: 'chi bdag bdud dang gshin rje'i bsnyen pa'i skabs te
NG0201:1359: bcu bdun pa'o // // de nas yang 'di skad
NG0201:1360: ces gsungs so // nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:1361: ngas gsungs pa la the tshom med //
NG0201:1362: gsad pa las kyi bsnyen pa ni //
NG0201:1363: yid 'thad mtshan ldan gnas dag tu //
NG0201:1364: gong gi las la gnas byas te //
NG0201:1365: de yang 'chi bdag bsnyen pa ni //
NG0201:1366: sum cu rtsa gnyis dril ba bzla zhes bshad //
NG0201:1367: las la sbyor ka'i dus de ru //
NG0201:1368: sna la ro tshas ras btsal te //
NG0201:1369: mas yar bgrang ba'i tshes brgyad dam //
NG0201:1370: nyi shu gnyis kyi nub mo ni //
NG0201:1371: dur khrod gling nas ras blangs la //
NG0201:1372: sme khrag gsum du bcug byas la //
NG0201:1373: 'chi bdag gshin rje de la bstim //
NG0201:1374: yab yum las la sbyor ka yi //
NG0201:1375: sngags 'di nyid kyang rab tu bzlas //
NG0201:1376: om sa ma ya many+dzu shri //
NG0201:1377: a kro te ka ka la ru pa hum phat /
NG0201:1379: nyi shu drug gi snga dro la //
NG0201:1380: ro ras bkru dang brgyad spyad bya //
NG0201:1381: nyi phyed man chad snag tsha mnye //
NG0201:1382: dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0201:1383: om du man+ta ka ra hum hum phat phat //
NG0201:1385: snag tsha mnye ba'i las zin nas //
NG0201:1386: de bzhin dgod ka 'khor lo bri //
NG0201:1387: bri ba zin nas lhar phyag 'tshal //
NG0201:1388: bka' bden pa 'grub par gyur cig ces bya //
NG0201:1389: yang na dur khrod ras med na //
NG0201:1390: thod pa dag la 'khor lo bri //
NG0201:1391: ag tse'i ngos su 'chi bdag gzugs bris la //
NG0201:1392: gzugs kyi snying gar ming byang bris //
NG0201:1393: dgra yi ming rus thod par gzhug / 'khor lo dbus kyi ya las kyang *//
NG0201:1394: 'chi bdag gshed po'i sku ru bskyed //
NG0201:1395: phyogs kyi ya ma me de k+she //
NG0201:1396: bzhi las gshed bzhi'i skur bskyed pas //
NG0201:1397: bdag gi mdun du ri rab las //
NG0201:1398: gser gyi ri bdun bcas pa bsam //
NG0201:1399: bdag nyid gshin rje gshed po yi //
NG0201:1400: rnal 'byor chu byad ldan byas la //
NG0201:1401: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthe bong yang *//
NG0201:1402: chang par bcug la be con bsam //
NG0201:1403: ri rab bdag gi spyir brdeg ste //
NG0201:1404: ri rab rgya gram gas par bsam //
NG0201:1405: de bzhin sngags 'di rab tu brjod //
NG0201:1406: om na mo bud+d+ha d+harma sang g+he b+h+yah sarba ta
NG0201:1407: tha ga ta kro d+ha bi dza ya ag+ni dz+wa
NG0201:1408: la ni dzi hwa bre ta shi ya hum hum
NG0201:1410: ri rab rgya gram gshag bsam @#//
NG0201:1412: gnas kyi gshin rje 'gugs bsam zhing *//
NG0201:1413: thugs ka'i yi ge ya nag po //
NG0201:1414: tha ma dbang sdud sngags kyis bskor ba las /
NG0201:1418: rang dbang med par de bkug nas //
NG0201:1419: de la sha khrag sna tshogs kyis //
NG0201:1420: gtor ma rdzas kyis mchod par bya //
NG0201:1422: dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags bzlas la /
NG0201:1423: bdag las 'phros pa'i gshed po dang *//
NG0201:1425: rang dbang med par bkug byas te //
NG0201:1426: thod pa'i nang du bcug pa la //
NG0201:1427: zhabs g.yas rdo rje'i phur pa yis //
NG0201:1429: rang dbang med par dbang du bsdus //
NG0201:1430: bka' nyan ci gsungs brjod par bsgom //
NG0201:1431: skya rengs dang po shar ba la //
NG0201:1433: gtor ma byin te gshin rje nyid //
NG0201:1434: pho nyar bkye la dgra bo dgug / lha dang dbral la sogs pa bya //
NG0201:1435: nyi ma rtse la shar ba dang *//
NG0201:1436: b+han+da dkyil 'khor gru gsum steng du bzhag / de bzhin bsad pa'i sngags bzlas te //
NG0201:1437: bdag nyid thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0201:1438: sngo nag gnag la 'tsher ba bsam //
NG0201:1439: tha ma drag sngags 'bru bdun pa //
NG0201:1441: gsad pa las kyi sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0201:1442: om hrihsh+t+rihbi kr-i ta na na che ge mo sha trum na sha ya hum phat /
NG0201:1443: ya ma ra dza sa do me ya che ge mo a mu kam pra ma ya hum phat /
NG0201:1445: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0201:1446: rang dbang med par bskur gyur nas //
NG0201:1447: gshed po ya ma ra dza bskul //
NG0201:1448: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0201:1449: de yis ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0201:1450: rdo rje ging pho ging mo dang *//
NG0201:1451: bdud la sogs pa dbang med bskul //
NG0201:1452: de bzhin gzas po dngos bkug nas //
NG0201:1453: thod par bcug ste gnas pa las //
NG0201:1454: gsad ba las kyi sngags bzlas pas //
NG0201:1455: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0201:1456: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0201:1457: dgong gi dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0201:1458: gshed chen ya ma ra dza la //
NG0201:1459: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma bshams //
NG0201:1460: be con phyag rgya bcas nas kyang *//
NG0201:1461: gnag pa'i spyi bor de brgyab pas //
NG0201:1462: tshangs pa'i rtsa bcad mgo 'khor bsam //
NG0201:1463: nyi shar rtse nas las brtsams te //
NG0201:1464: bdag nyid thugs kar yi ge ya /
NG0201:1466: gsad pa las kyi sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0201:1467: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbikr-i ta na na che ge mo sha trum na sha ya hum phat /
NG0201:1468: ya me do ru na yo da ya /
NG0201:1469: che ge mo a mu kam mu+u ra tsa ya hum phat /
NG0201:1471: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0201:1472: rang dbang med par bskul nas kyang *//
NG0201:1473: de yis myos byed 'bar ba bskul //
NG0201:1474: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0201:1475: de bzhin ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0201:1476: ging bdud 'dug pa'i dbang med bskul //
NG0201:1478: bzhin dmigs pa'i dngos bkug nas //
NG0201:1479: 'dug pa'i dbang med thod par bcug / gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas pas //
NG0201:1480: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0201:1481: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0201:1482: de bzhin dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0201:1483: gshed po myos byed 'bar ba la //
NG0201:1484: mnyes pa'i sha khrag gtor ma sbyin //
NG0201:1485: gshed la bcol bskul drag tu bya //
NG0201:1486: phyag rgya gong bzhin bcas nas kyang *//
NG0201:1487: be con lte bar brgyab pas ni //
NG0201:1489: bdag gi thugs ka'i ya nag po //
NG0201:1490: drag sngags bdun gyis bskor ba la //
NG0201:1491: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas te //
NG0201:1492: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i na na sha trum na sha ya hum phat /
NG0201:1493: ya da yo ni ra ya k+she ya che ge
NG0201:1494: mo a mu kam rak+ta tsa ra ya hum phat
NG0201:1495: / 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0201:1496: rang dbang med par bskul nas kyang *//
NG0201:1497: gshed chen ar+ya ma ru bskul //
NG0201:1498: de yis phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0201:1499: de bzhin ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0201:1500: ging dang ging mo bdud la sogs //
NG0201:1501: 'dug pa'i dbang med bskul bar bsam //
NG0201:1502: de yi gzas pa po bkug nas //
NG0201:1503: dbang med thod par bcug par bsam //
NG0201:1504: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas pas //
NG0201:1505: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0201:1506: gang la bya ba brlag par bsam //
NG0201:1507: de bzhin dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0201:1508: gshed chen ar+ya ma ru la //
NG0201:1509: sha khrag mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0201:1510: be con mgrin par brgyab pa yi //
NG0201:1511: khrag tsar lhug gis song bar bsam //
NG0201:1512: bdag gi thugs kar yi ge ya //
NG0201:1513: drag sngags 'bru bdun bskor ba la //
NG0201:1514: gsad pa las kyi sngags bzlas te //
NG0201:1515: om hrihsh+t+r-ihbi kr-i ta na na sha trum na sha ya hum phat /
NG0201:1516: ya k+she ya ts+tsha ni ra ma ya //
NG0201:1517: che ge mo a mu kam ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0201:1519: 'od zer bdag la phog gyur pas //
NG0201:1520: rang dbang med par bskul nas kyang *//
NG0201:1521: de yis ral pa tshar dgu bskul //
NG0201:1522: de yi phyogs skyong gshin rje bskul //
NG0201:1523: de bzhin ma mo mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0201:1524: ging pho ging mo bdud la sogs //
NG0201:1525: 'dug pa'i dbang med bskul bar bsam //
NG0201:1526: gzas pa bkug nas thod par bcug / de bzhin gsang ba'i sngags bzlas pas //
NG0201:1527: star tshan rtsi sbur mi chags bzhin //
NG0201:1528: gang la bya ba brlags par bsam //
NG0201:1529: dgong ka'i dmar thag chad pa dang *//
NG0201:1530: gshed chen ral pa tshar dgu la //
NG0201:1531: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma sbyin //
NG0201:1532: drag po'i phrin las bcol bskul bya //
NG0201:1533: de bzhin be con phyag rgya yis //
NG0201:1534: snying gar brgyab pas srog bcas nas //
NG0201:1535: dbugs kun phyi la phyung bar bsam //
NG0201:1536: gsad pa ma ra'i man ngag 'di //
NG0201:1537: gshin rje gshed po bdag gis kyang *//
NG0201:1538: thugs kyi sgrom bu kha phye nas //
NG0201:1539: rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod la byos //
NG0201:1540: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:1541: gsang ba las kyi bsnyen pa'i skabs te bcwo brgyad
NG0201:1542: pa'o // // de nas mthu stobs kyi bdag po
NG0201:1543: @#// lag na rdo rjes 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0201:1544: he he dpa' bo chen po 'jigs byed gshed //
NG0201:1545: drag po gsang ba'i 'khor lo la //
NG0201:1546: skyod pa'i rta dang 'bebs pa'i sngags //
NG0201:1547: sdebs pa'i grogs dang rno ba'i rdzas //
NG0201:1548: de bzhi'i rkyen dang ma ldan na //
NG0201:1551: mthu stobs bdag pos 'di skad gsol //
NG0201:1552: skyod pa'i rta ni gang la bgyi //
NG0201:1553: 'debs pa'i sngags ni gang la bgyi //
NG0201:1554: sdebs pa'i grogs ni gang la bgyi //
NG0201:1555: rno ba'i ngar ni gang la bgyi //
NG0201:1556: yab cig 'jam dpal bka' stsol cig / gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad brjod //
NG0201:1557: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:1558: drag po gsang ba'i 'khor lo la //
NG0201:1559: skyod pa'i rta dang mi ldan na //
NG0201:1561: 'debs pa'i sngags dang mi ldan na //
NG0201:1563: sdebs pa'i grogs dang ma ldan na //
NG0201:1564: dpa' bo gting gnon med pa 'dra //
NG0201:1565: rno ba'i ngar dang mi ldan na //
NG0201:1566: mtshon cha rtse mo rtul ba 'dra //
NG0201:1567: de bzhin grogs rnams ngas bshad kyi //
NG0201:1568: lag na rdo rjes rab tu zung *//
NG0201:1569: bka' dang gzhung bzhin ma nor ba'i //
NG0201:1570: bsrung ba'i sdom pa ma nyams par //
NG0201:1571: rdzas dang lag cha ldan pa dang *//
NG0201:1572: bsam ldan bzlas brjod sran tshugs shing *//
NG0201:1573: dam tshig bsrung zhing drag shul spyod //
NG0201:1574: lta spyod bsgrub pa ldan pa yi //
NG0201:1575: dpa' rtul can gyi rnal 'byor pas //
NG0201:1576: bstan pa gnyen po bsrung don du //
NG0201:1577: dgon pa chen po gnas mal der //
NG0201:1578: bya byed zang zing 'du long spang *//
NG0201:1579: 'tsho ba'i yo byad dpags te bstar //
NG0201:1580: bya ba thams cad zin nas ni //
NG0201:1581: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NG0201:1582: bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa de //
NG0201:1583: ting 'dzin gsal dang brtan pa yi //
NG0201:1584: lha yi rnal 'byor rtse gcig bya //
NG0201:1585: thun mong dam tshig bsrung zhing bsgrub //
NG0201:1586: khyad par dam tshig spyod cing dor //
NG0201:1587: bsnyen bsgrub phrin las gzhung bzhin bya //
NG0201:1588: tshang zhing rdzogs pa'i grangs bsnyen la //
NG0201:1589: 'khor zhing phyin pa dus bsnyen yin //
NG0201:1590: mthong ngam thos sam nyams su len //
NG0201:1591: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:1592: zhi rgyas gnyis kyi 'khor los mchod //
NG0201:1593: dbang drag gnyis kyi 'khor los mnan //
NG0201:1594: zhi rgyas gnyis kyi bsrung phan gdags //
NG0201:1595: dbang drag gnyis kyis bsgral bar bya //
NG0201:1596: 'khor lo gzhan yang ci rigs par //
NG0201:1597: dbye bskrad dgug sogs gzhung bzhin bya //
NG0201:1598: gang 'dod las de bsgrub byas na //
NG0201:1599: 'khor lo'i rgyu dang snag tsha dang *//
NG0201:1600: phyogs dang bsam sbyor rim pa dang *//
NG0201:1601: kha dog so so'i mthun rdzas ni //
NG0201:1602: rim pa can gyi de shes bya //
NG0201:1603: de la 'khor lo zhes grags pa //
NG0201:1604: ngo bo nges tshig rnam grangs so //
NG0201:1605: ngo bo spyi yi mtshan nyid ni //
NG0201:1607: so so rang gi mtshan nyid ni //
NG0201:1608: gang la btab pa de ltar snang *//
NG0201:1609: nges pa'i tshig kyang de bzhin te //
NG0201:1613: lte ba 'khor shing rtse mos gcod //
NG0201:1614: de la grangs ni mtha' yas te //
NG0201:1615: mdor na rnam pa gsum du shes //
NG0201:1616: thugs rje sprul pa'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0201:1617: las dang srid pa'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0201:1618: 'jig rten phan gnod byed pa yi //
NG0201:1620: dper na mo 'phang mgal me dang *//
NG0201:1621: glog dang sgra ldan 'khor lo dang *//
NG0201:1622: shing rta zo chu'i 'khor lo sogs //
NG0201:1623: las dang 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni //
NG0201:1624: thugs rje sprul pa'i 'khor los ni //
NG0201:1625: nyon mongs gcod cing sdug bsngal 'joms //
NG0201:1626: bsgrub dang bsgrub par bya ba yi //
NG0201:1627: sems bskyed pa dang rgyud dgrol zhing *//
NG0201:1628: ye shes sems mtshon rnal grol byed //
NG0201:1629: de las rnam pa gzhan du yang *//
NG0201:1630: zhi dang rgyas dang srung ba dang *//
NG0201:1631: dgug dang dbang du bya ba dang *//
NG0201:1632: dbye bskrad dgug dang smyo 'bog dang *//
NG0201:1633: gsad dang gnan pa la sogs pa //
NG0201:1634: de yi rkyen dang rtsol ba dang *//
NG0201:1635: dus dang las thabs byed pa yi //
NG0201:1636: 'phen zhing bskyod pa nus pa yi //
NG0201:1638: bsnur dang 'khrul zhing sdud pa dang *//
NG0201:1639: gzir zhing gnan zhing 'bigs pa dang *//
NG0201:1640: brdeg cing rnam par 'joms par byed //
NG0201:1641: las dang srid pa'i 'khor lo ni //
NG0201:1644: nyon mongs las dang sdug bsngal gyi //
NG0201:1645: rnam pa gsum dang 'khor zhing 'gro / 'das dang da ltar gnas pa dang *//
NG0201:1647: skad kyi 'byung ba'i rgyun gyis na //
NG0201:1648: skad cig ma yi rgyun gyis 'khor //
NG0201:1649: de bzhin phyi rol don rnams kyang *//
NG0201:1650: dbyar dgun staun dpyid zla ba los //
NG0201:1652: ngo bo nges tshig rnam grangs su //
NG0201:1653: 'khor lo'i rang bzhin bstan pa yin //
NG0201:1654: bde gshegs bka' la gnod pa la //
NG0201:1656: yi dwags grong khyer bcom byas la //
NG0201:1657: snel gri'i mu su'i mgo thod blangs //
NG0201:1658: yi dwags gos la khram bris te //
NG0201:1659: dbyibs ni zla ba lta bu ste //
NG0201:1660: kun nas yongs su zlum pa ste //
NG0201:1661: rim pa gsum ldan le'u tshe dgu //
NG0201:1662: bcu gnyis bcu drug rtsibs bcas te //
NG0201:1663: le'u tse dgu dang bcu gnyis la //
NG0201:1664: bcu bdun la sogs sngags kyis mdzes //
NG0201:1666: phyin ci log gi bcings pa yi //
NG0201:1667: log pa'i shes pa ldan pa des //
NG0201:1668: rgyu mthun mtshan ma'i 'khor lo la //
NG0201:1669: man ngag can gyi rnal 'byor pas //
NG0201:1670: kha nas drag po'i sngags bzlas te //
NG0201:1671: chos kyi rgyal po la sogs pa'i //
NG0201:1672: las kyi shan pa'i go bkram ste //
NG0201:1673: lcags kyu shag ti to ma ra //
NG0201:1674: kha t+wam ber ka la sogs pas //
NG0201:1675: brdeg cing 'joms par byed pa ni //
NG0201:1677: 'dzin cing gsod par bsam pa yis //
NG0201:1678: gang la bya ba'i rnam shes de //
NG0201:1681: khro bdag gshin rje gshed po ru //
NG0201:1682: bdag nyid bsam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0201:1683: mtshan ma'i ming rus bcas pa la //
NG0201:1684: ske tshe dug dang nyung nag dang *//
NG0201:1685: thal chen gu gul nyung dkar gyis //
NG0201:1686: brab dang gzir dang dbab pa dang *//
NG0201:1687: dgug cing rdo rje'i mtshon gyis gdab //
NG0201:1688: sngon dmar byad du gzhug byas la //
NG0201:1689: ga'u kha sbyar nang du gzhug / smra bcad zhi khro'i sngags bzlas pa'i //
NG0201:1690: drag po'i sngags kyis phog 'gyur na //
NG0201:1691: gang la dmigs pa'i bsgrub bya de //
NG0201:1692: mgo 'khor pa dang khrag skyugs pa //
NG0201:1693: myos par ma ra gdon mi za //
NG0201:1694: drag po'i las rnams rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:1695: mtshan ma ming rus bcas pa rnams //
NG0201:1696: thod pa nag por rgyas btab la //
NG0201:1697: sme bas bkrus pas tshan chus byug / mu sa la yi g.yogs shing gtums //
NG0201:1698: kha ral ma yi zhabs mas gril //
NG0201:1699: yi dwags grong ngam sme brtseg khyim //
NG0201:1700: mchod rten 'og gam lha khang sgo //
NG0201:1701: rgya mtsho'i 'gram mam lung mdo du //
NG0201:1702: rdo la ri rab gzugs bris la //
NG0201:1703: steng du lam dang d+h+ri yis mnan //
NG0201:1704: gshin rje'i lag tu gtad khram bya /
NG0201:1705: bzlas pa'i tshe dang bklag pa'i tshe /
NG0201:1706: 'dra min 'dug 'di'i mchan bu 'di gang la sbyar
NG0201:1707: dgos ma shes pas dpyad / thun kha brgyad kyang
NG0201:1708: brdab par bya // sbos pa dug thun lkugs pa kha //
NG0201:1709: nyi ma dang po'i thun gyis mnan //
NG0201:1710: gzer ba mda' thun brla la gzer //
NG0201:1711: nyi ma gnyis pa'i thun gyis brab //
NG0201:1712: lkugs pa khrag thun myos pa phur //
NG0201:1713: nyi ma gsum pa'i thun gyis brab //
NG0201:1714: gsang ba nyung nag sa yi tshon //
NG0201:1715: nyi ma bzhi pa'i thun gyis mnan //
NG0201:1716: mtshan ngan thod pa khrag gis byug / khrag sna dug sna sbyar byas nas //
NG0201:1717: shan dmar dug skyogs dug thun bzlas //
NG0201:1718: glen lkugs thod pa'i kha thun te //
NG0201:1719: lcags mda' lcags gzhu mda' thun bzlas //
NG0201:1720: gri bo'i thod par mtshon brdar pa'o //
NG0201:1721: mkhris nad thod par sa ser gser //
NG0201:1722: gla ba gser thun sngags kyis so //
NG0201:1723: smyo ba'i thod pa khrag thun dang */
NG0201:1724: smyos pa phur thun bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:1725: rabs chad thod pa nyung thun dang *//
NG0201:1726: sa tshon thun du shes par bya //
NG0201:1727: chu shel sgron ma rlabs po che //
NG0201:1728: lkugs pa mon mo'i lag g.yabs kyi //
NG0201:1729: srid pa'i dmag dpung ra mda' bzlog / ya ma ra dza'i g.yab kyis g.yab //
NG0201:1730: gsur dang sme ba'i dud pas bdug / gcer bu spyi tshug ngu 'bod bya //
NG0201:1731: mi mthun gnyen po'i phyogs dag tu //
NG0201:1732: gzir gnon drag po'i mngon spyod bya //
NG0201:1733: drag po'i thun sngags kha nas bzlas //
NG0201:1734: zhung thun ya rbad na thun ya rbad phung phur yang thun ya //
NG0201:1736: dang po dang lo lo kyi gye //
NG0201:1737: srog la yam yam snying la thun //
NG0201:1738: kha brgyad thun yang brdeg par bya //
NG0201:1739: lha srin sde brgyad la sogs pa'i //
NG0201:1740: srid pa'i dmag dpung phab nas ni //
NG0201:1741: drang srong dmod pa'i sngags zor dang *//
NG0201:1742: sna tshogs sngags kyi sbyor ba dang *//
NG0201:1743: lha yi rnal 'byor ldan pas bya //
NG0201:1744: khru gang gru bzhi zabs yod @#//
NG0201:1746: ga bu rdzas kyi sbyor ba de //
NG0201:1747: 'byung po'i gtor ma gshin rje la //
NG0201:1748: byin la lag tu gtad khram bya //
NG0201:1749: rang gi yi dam bsgom bya zhing *//
NG0201:1750: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gtor ma ni //
NG0201:1751: sa sros tshe na lho phyogs gtang *//
NG0201:1752: sgrol ba'i drag sngags brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0201:1753: bstan pa bsrung ba gnan pa'i gter //
NG0201:1754: phr-in las drag po sngags kyi mtshon //
NG0201:1756: rdo rje sems dpa' gzungs shing chongs //
NG0201:1757: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las //
NG0201:1758: 'khor lo thun sdebs kyi skabs te bcu dgu pa'o
NG0201:1759: // // de nas gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad
NG0201:1760: brjod // bstan pa srung ba brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0201:1761: thugs kyi man ngag sngags zor mchog / sgrol ba'i phrin las sbyor thabs su //
NG0201:1763: bka' yi bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0201:1764: rang sems dag pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0201:1765: snying rje dag tu srog ltar brten //
NG0201:1766: byams dga' btang snyoms de bzhin du'o //
NG0201:1767: mdo sogs 'don zhing bsam gtan bya //
NG0201:1768: rgyun gyi yi dam rtse gcig pas //
NG0201:1769: bla ma dag la rtag tu bkur //
NG0201:1770: des kyang dkyil 'khor tshul bzhin gzhug / theg chen dam tshig sdom pa bshad //
NG0201:1771: rang gi sngags dang phyag rgya bsten //
NG0201:1772: sgrub thabs man ngag legs par blang *//
NG0201:1773: de nas mchod pa cho ga bzhin //
NG0201:1774: nyin re dag tu byas nas kyang *//
NG0201:1775: sku gzugs dang kyang 'bad de bya //
NG0201:1776: bde ba'i stan la lus sems gzhag / sum 'bum mi skyo'i bar du bzlas //
NG0201:1777: de 'og ri rtser gnas byas la //
NG0201:1778: rlung za zhing ni bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:1779: 'bum bcu'i mtha' ru phrin las brtsams //
NG0201:1780: nam mkha'i sgron ma mar dus tshe //
NG0201:1781: yi dwags grong bcom shi gos la //
NG0201:1782: yi dwags 'khor lo gdug pa yi //
NG0201:1783: 'khor lo gdug pa'i lte ba la //
NG0201:1784: re'u mig dgu mi mtshams bor te //
NG0201:1785: bcu gnyis 'khor lo gdug pa'i nang *//
NG0201:1786: bcu bdun la sogs gsang sngags dang *//
NG0201:1787: zlum pos bskor ba'i phyi rim na //
NG0201:1789: dur khrod sol ba dug gsol gyis //
NG0201:1790: srin mtheb gung 'dzub sbyar ba yis //
NG0201:1791: khru gang gos gnyis ras mchog la //
NG0201:1792: gdug pa'i yi ge g.yas g.yon bzlog / de nang chud pa'i skyes bu gnyis //
NG0201:1794: phyag zhabs mgur chu ro nye brgyan //
NG0201:1795: mi smra dbang po bsdams te bri //
NG0201:1796: gnyis sbyar rgyab la ro nye yis //
NG0201:1797: bsdams pa'i tshul du mkhas pas bri //
NG0201:1798: gdug pas bzung zhing gdug pa zung gcig thod nang du /
NG0201:1800: dril byas sngon dmar byad kyis bsdams //
NG0201:1801: gdug pa'i thod nag ltos 'phro bri //
NG0201:1802: mngar dang klu sman rtsi mchog gis //
NG0201:1803: mchod cing snal la mgu bar bya //
NG0201:1804: gdug pas bzung zhing thod par gzhug / sngon dmar byad thag bzhis btab la //
NG0201:1805: bzung ste nyin mtshan ma nor bzlas //
NG0201:1808: rdo rje rlung lcai sbyar ba las //
NG0201:1809: sngon dmar gdug pa'i ro nye'i tshogs //
NG0201:1810: dur khrod sol bas dug sogs sbyar //
NG0201:1811: lcags sam 'ug pa'i sgrau rtsa yis //
NG0201:1812: gsang ba'i sngags dang ming rus bri //
NG0201:1813: dug can nad kyi bsgrub bya la //
NG0201:1814: dug lce nag pos bsdams par bsam //
NG0201:1815: 'chi bdag bshan pa'i yi dwags tshogs //
NG0201:1816: gtum po dug gi kha rlangs can //
NG0201:1817: chos kyi rgyal po la sogs pas //
NG0201:1818: 'dzab cing skugs shing bzung nas ni //
NG0201:1819: gshin rje gdug pa'i khang pa ru //
NG0201:1820: dbang med las kyi 'jug par bsam //
NG0201:1822: hum dang ming spel a kar sha //
NG0201:1823: dza gnyis dgug pa'i gsang sngags bzlas //
NG0201:1824: ske tshe dug nyung sngags kyis brab //
NG0201:1825: zla ba nag po'i mar dus tshe //
NG0201:1826: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru gsum ste //
NG0201:1827: lcags khri nag po'i steng dag tu //
NG0201:1828: yi dwags gdug pa'i ga bu gzhag / ya sogs gdug pa'i gsang sngags rnams //
NG0201:1829: zhi khro rdzogs nas ga bu de //
NG0201:1830: rdza mkhan sa la ga bu rgyu //
NG0201:1831: gdug pa'i ga bu shang ba'i tshad //
NG0201:1832: gnyis byas nang du ro nye gnyis //
NG0201:1833: phyi nang gnyis su 'bur du bya //
NG0201:1834: ga bu dag la 'khril pa'i tshul //
NG0201:1835: me yi smin ma ga bu gnag / gdug pa'i
NG0201:1836: thod nag ga bur gzhug / sngon dmar gnyis kyi
NG0201:1837: thi gus bsdams // shar nub lho byang phyogs mtshams su //
NG0201:1838: gdug pa gnas pa'i yul dag la //
NG0201:1839: sgo bltas khyim nas 'dom gang du //
NG0201:1840: rdo la 'jig rten gzugs bris la //
NG0201:1841: sa sgo phye la khyim bdag rbad //
NG0201:1842: mthun pa'i rdzas sbyin mgu bar bya //
NG0201:1843: ga bu gdug pa'i sbyor ba de //
NG0201:1844: legs sbas steng nas 'jig rten gzhug / gang la bya ba'i dus dang lo //
NG0201:1845: gnyen po gang shis mkhas pas dpyad //

NG0201:1872: byang chub sems nyid sems la bzhag / dam @#//

NG0201:1874: bka' la bshad pa rjes mthun par //
NG0201:1875: rdzas dang lag cha mthun bsdebs shing *//
NG0201:1876: rtag tu dur khrod dgon par dga' //

NG0201:1885: mi 'jigs dpa' bo brtul zhugs can //
NG0201:1886: man ngag yod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0201:1887: rang don phran tshegs ma yin pa'i //
NG0201:1888: dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod pa dang *//
NG0201:1889: bstan la zhe sdang gnod byed pa //
NG0201:1890: bka' gsang ston pas bshad pa yi //
NG0201:1891: drag po'i mngon spyod zab mo'i lung *//
NG0201:1892: gshin rje gshed po bdag gis kyang *//
NG0201:1893: thugs kyi sgrom nas bton pa 'di //
NG0201:1894: 'khor lo byad stems brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0201:1895: man ngag can gyis de shes bya //
