NG0201:1897: man ngag don gyis shes par bya //
NG0201:1898: cung zad mi mthun mchod bstod rnams //
NG0201:1899: zla gsang nag po'i rgyud dag las //
NG0201:1900: gsang ba mdzes thun gzhung ltar bya //
NG0201:1901: de la mchod pa gsungs pa ni //
NG0201:1902: mchod pa chen po 'dod chags che //
NG0201:1903: dkyil 'khor chen po yang pa yin //
NG0201:1904: tshigs bcad bcu drug tha ma la //
NG0201:1905: 'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog / 'gro la phan pa'i gtso chen gyis //
NG0201:1906: sman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NG0201:1907: tshig gnyis btags la dbul bar bya //
NG0201:1908: bstod pa la sogs byed pa na //
NG0201:1909: de bzhin rtsa ba mtshan brjod las //
NG0201:1911: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas a las byung *//
NG0201:1912: bdud sogs kun gyis bstod byas mthar //
NG0201:1913: mtshan gyi sngags brjod bstod chen bya //
NG0201:1914: sngags mchog mnga' bdag rig sngags rgyal //
NG0201:1916: ma rig sgo nga'i sbubs 'byed pa //
NG0201:1917: srid pa'i dra ba 'joms pa po //
NG0201:1918: zhes bstod pa tshig rkang drug pa dang *//
NG0201:1919: drug cu rtsa bzhi bstod pa 'bul //
NG0201:1920: yang na 'dud pa nyi shu nas //
NG0201:1921: mtshan sngags brjod la bstod chung bya //
NG0201:1922: yang na mdzes thun gzhung bzhin bya //
NG0201:1923: bskal pa sbrul nag 'khyil ces gtad //
NG0201:1925: dkon mchog gnod cing bstan pa 'jig / mngon spyod thugs rjes bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0201:1926: mi tshig tha snyad tsam du brjod mi bya //
NG0201:1927: chu srin mgrin par rin chen chud pa ltar //
NG0201:1928: khong du sbas te yongs su bsgrag pa min //
NG0201:1929: gshin rje gshed po'i thugs kyi yong bcud 'di //
NG0201:1930: phyag na rdo rjes rab tu gzung zhing nyon //
NG0201:1931: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyun las /
NG0201:1932: tshon gyi gru gu sngon dmar byad stems kyi skabs
NG0201:1933: te nyi shu pa'o // // de nas yang bcom
NG0201:1934: ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos 'di skad ces gsungs
NG0201:1935: so // las kyi bya ba gzhan zin nas //
NG0201:1938: lag na rdo rjes rab tu zung *//
NG0201:1939: shin tu dgon pa'i gnas nyid du //
NG0201:1940: dur khrod gling nas ras blangs te / 'khor lo rim pa tshul bzhin du //
NG0201:1941: ma ra ya yi ling+ga nyid //
NG0201:1942: ji bzhin 'dod pa'i dbyibs su bca' //
NG0201:1943: gong ma'i bsnyen pa rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:1944: 'khor lo thabs kyi dam rdzas de //

NG0201:1946: bdag nyid gshed por bsgom byas la //

NG0201:1953: de bzhin rab tu mnan cing gzir //

NG0201:1955: de las gling phran bcu gnyis bsam //
NG0201:1956: ri rab 'og tu gzas pa po //
NG0201:1957: gshin rje ral pa tshar dgu yis //
NG0201:1958: lcags thag sngon pos bcings pa de //
NG0201:1959: bam ril mnan nas lcags phur la //
NG0201:1960: dpag bsam shing tsam btags pa ste //
NG0201:1961: sgra sgrogs kha nas khrag skyugs gan bub cing *//
NG0201:1963: ci mdzad thong zhig zer zing mnan par bsam //
NG0201:1964: 'khor lo bri ba'i dus su yang *//
NG0201:1965: dmigs pa'i ming dag gzhug pa ni //
NG0201:1966: 'khor lo nyid la mi shong zhing *//
NG0201:1967: mi btub pa rnams gud du bri //

NG0201:1969: gnas dang thabs ni 'di yin te //

NG0201:1971: gra bzhi hum phat bar mtshams bzhi //
NG0201:1972: rtsibs kyi re'u cha bcu gnyis dang *//
NG0201:1973: mtha' bskor ming bris le'u tse brgyad //

NG0201:1975: gud du ming gi mjug tu yang *//
NG0201:1976: ma ra ya zhes bris pa'i 'khor lo gnyis //
NG0201:1977: kha sbyar ba yi nang du gzhug / 'khor lo
NG0201:1978: skud pas sbrel la bzhag / ngan sngags bzlas pa'i
NG0201:1979: dus su yang *// bzhi pa'i ngan sngags khri phrag 'don //
NG0201:1980: de dag bton pa'i rjes la yang *//
NG0201:1981: yi ge bcu pa nus tshad bzlas //

NG0201:1983: de tshe gtor ma gtong ba dang *//

NG0201:1985: las kyi gshin rje ma mo rnams //
NG0201:1986: rak+ta gsol zhing dgug pa'i phrin las bya //
NG0201:1987: 'khor lo sgreng pa'i dus su yang *//
NG0201:1988: gshin rje dag la gtad pa ni /
NG0201:1989: can gyi dang chas kyi yang snang */
NG0201:1990: 'di'i mchan bu 'di gang gi yin ma shes pas dpyad / rdzas kyi mchod pa bsham pa dang *//
NG0201:1991: bdag nyid gshed por bsgom pa dang *//
NG0201:1992: 'chi bdag dgongs su gsol ba dang *//
NG0201:1993: rang gi las kyi ltang brtsi dang *//
NG0201:1994: bsgrub bya'i chad pa brtsi ba dang *//

NG0201:2006: drang srong dmod pa'i smon mal gdab par bya //

NG0201:2009: pho rog 'ug pa pu shud sgro //

NG0201:2016: gtad khram bcu gnyis cho gas mnan pa dang *//

NG0201:2019: drag po'i sngags kyis gnan pa dang *//
NG0201:2020: smon lam gdab cing gnan pa dang *//
NG0201:2021: drang srong dmod pas gnan pa'o //
NG0201:2022: 'di nas lho yi phyogs rol na //
NG0201:2023: dpag tshad brgyad khri bzhi stong pha rol na //
NG0201:2024: thod pa lcags kyi grong khyer na //
NG0201:2025: yi dwags kun gyi sde dpon po //

NG0201:2027: gson gshin gnyis kyi zam kha pa //
NG0201:2028: gson po skos la 'debs pa po //
NG0201:2029: shi ba rnams kyi gshin bu rje //
NG0201:2030: dge ba can gyi ltang 'dzin la //
NG0201:2031: sdig pa can gyi chad pa mkhan //
NG0201:2032: legs nyes chos bzhin gcod pa yis //
NG0201:2033: chos rgyal gshin rje zhes bya ba //
NG0201:2034: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul mthur ldan pas //

NG0201:2036: de dag rab tu mnan gyur na //
NG0201:2037: de yi cho ga 'dir ma bshad //

NG0201:2039: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /

NG0201:2041: // de nas bcom ldan gshin rje'i gshed pos 'di
NG0201:2043: bdag don ma yin gzhan don nam //

NG0201:2045: ru tra gdug pa tshar gcad na //

NG0201:2048: g.yul ngo bzlog par 'dod pa yis //

NG0201:2053: mgar gyis rdo la lcags su bzhu //

NG0201:2056: til mar ngar yang yid 'thad blud //
NG0201:2057: de nas brdeg thabs shes par bya //
NG0201:2058: de bzhin rnal 'byor chen pos kyang *//
NG0201:2059: thogs mar bla ma mnyes bya'i phyir //
NG0201:2060: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NG0201:2061: gnang bar dka' ba'i dbang yang mnos //

NG0201:2063: snying po don thabs lhar shes bya //

NG0201:2068: phrin las dag la rnam pa gsum //
NG0201:2071: dang po 'khor lo'i las byas nas //

NG0201:2074: me lha bsnyen pas las rnams 'grub //
NG0201:2075: dang por bsnyen pa rdzogs nas kyang *//
NG0201:2076: 'khor lo bskor ba'i las byas nas //
NG0201:2078: gnan pa'i las thabs byas nas ni //

NG0201:2080: thab khung gru gsum brtseg pa la //
NG0201:2081: rdo rje rgya gram nag po bri //
NG0201:2082: gzas pa'i ling+ga gzhag par bya //

NG0201:2084: bam po bsgred dang gru gsum brtsig / dug chu khrag gis byug par bya //
NG0201:2086: sman phud til dmar 'bru bshos dang *//

NG0201:2091: rak+sha'i phreng ba ser la kha //
NG0201:2092: dpral bar me long zhig gi stan //
NG0201:2093: rus sbal 'dug stangs lho phyogs blta //
NG0201:2094: lcags sam mi rkang gzar bu thogs //
NG0201:2095: dri chen dri chu gos dum gyis //
NG0201:2096: sa la dmigs pa'i gzugs byas la //
NG0201:2097: snying gar ming dang rus bcas gzhug / gzhan yang ming yig mang po dang *//
NG0201:2098: mi bsad mtshon gyis ling+ga gtub //
NG0201:2099: dum bu re dang ming byang re //

NG0201:2102: ting 'dzin rnam gsum tshig bshad dang *//

NG0201:2104: om swa b+ha wa shud+d+hahsarba d+harma swa b+ha ba bi shud+d+ho\u0f85ham /
NG0201:2105: chos rnams stong pa'i rang bzhin sbyang *//
NG0201:2106: de yi ngang nas nga rgyal lha //

NG0201:2109: rgyan dang cha lugs gsal bar bsgom //
NG0201:2110: thab khung e las 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0201:2111: drag po 'bar ba'i gnas su gsal bar bsgom //
NG0201:2112: yugs sa rdo nag shing nag gtsubs pa'i me //
NG0201:2113: rlung g.yab nag pos g.yab pa'am //

NG0201:2116: rgyan dang cha lugs nag po gsal bar bsgom //
NG0201:2117: ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phro 'dus gnas nas kyang *//
NG0201:2118: 'od zer lcags kyus ye shes me lha de //

NG0201:2120: me yi lha nyid sngags 'dis spyan drangs te //
NG0201:2124: sku mdog nag po ra skyes kham pa zhon //
NG0201:2126: zhing gi ya mgal snga ru+u la //
NG0201:2127: zhing gi ma mgal phyi ru la //

NG0201:2129: sbrul nag gis ni gong rmed bgyis //
NG0201:2130: phyag na dril bu bgrang phreng bsnams //

NG0201:2146: ag+ne dmar ser me yi lha /

NG0201:2188: gsang ba'i gsum du phye ba las //
NG0201:2189: phyi yi dus su bskor ba ni //
NG0201:2190: bsgrub pa'i drag sngags bcu bdun pa //
NG0201:2191: g.yon du bskor te bgrang ba'o //
NG0201:2192: gsang ba'i nang du bskor ba ni //
NG0201:2193: gsang ba'i drag sngags bcu bdun pa //
NG0201:2194: g.yas su bdun bskor bgrang ba'o //
NG0201:2195: gsang ba'i gsang bar grangs pa ni //
NG0201:2196: rtsa ba dam tshig yang snying ni //

NG0201:2618: ya la sogs pa bcu gnyis ni //
NG0201:2619: ya man+ta ka yab yum gnyis //
NG0201:2620: phyogs skyong bcu yi snying po yin //
NG0201:2621: phyi ma lha gzhan snying po ste //
NG0201:2622: yig 'bru sum cu rtsa gnyis ni //
NG0201:2624: ya stsogs brgyad pa zhes kyang grags //
NG0201:2625: tshogs brgyad 'joms pa'i phung sri ste //
NG0201:2626: ye shes lha yi snying po dang *//
NG0201:2627: 'jigs byed lha srin kun gyi snying po ste //
NG0201:2628: shin tu gsang bar gshed pos bshad //
NG0201:2629: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:2630: ka bzhi gdung brgyad kyi skabs te rtsa drug pa'o
NG0201:2631: // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed
NG0201:2632: chen pos / thugs gsang ba 'bru shag grong khyer 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:2729: yi ge gshin rje'i 'bru shag ste //
NG0201:2730: yi ge gshin rje'i 'bru shag yin //
NG0201:2731: rdo rje 'dzin pas rab tu zung *//
NG0201:2732: 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:2733: 'bru shag grong khyer gyi skabs te rtsa bdun pa'o
NG0201:2734: // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed
NG0201:2735: chen pos 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0201:2736: nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:2737: ngas gsungs pa la sems thud cig / lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NG0201:2738: bstan pa 'dzin skyong bsrung dang gsum //
NG0201:2739: bstan pa bshigs pa'i dgra de la //
NG0201:2740: drag po las kyi mthar bya ba //
NG0201:2741: dus ni rang byung dgra la bya //
NG0201:2742: dus dang khams dang gyur pa dang *//
NG0201:2743: rang byung don de bzhi ru 'dod //
NG0201:2744: de la bskul ba rnam bzhi bya //
NG0201:2745: rdzas dang sngags dang ting 'dzin dang *//
NG0201:2746: bskul ba'i don de bzhi ru 'dod //
NG0201:2747: de yi sngon du bsnyen bsgrub bya //
NG0201:2748: bsnyen bsgrub song nas bskul ba ni //
NG0201:2750: nyi ma dang ni gshin rje dang *//
NG0201:2751: gsang sngags dang ni ting 'dzin dag dang drug / 'khor lo la yang rnam gsum ste //
NG0201:2754: 'khor lo de dag re re la //
NG0201:2755: bri dang sgra dang las dang ni //
NG0201:2756: rang gi ngo bo dag dang lnga'o //
NG0201:2757: de bzhin ling+ga dag la gsum //
NG0201:2758: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NG0201:2759: ling+ga de dag re re la //
NG0201:2760: rgyu dang bca' dang sgra dang las //
NG0201:2761: rang gi ngo bo dag dang lnga'o //
NG0201:2762: de bzhin sngags la rnam gsum ste //
NG0201:2763: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NG0201:2764: de bzhin drag sngags re re la //
NG0201:2765: rgyu dang btu dang las sngags dang *//
NG0201:2766: bzlas dang nga ro sgra dang las //
NG0201:2767: nyi ma la yang rnam gsum ste //
NG0201:2768: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NG0201:2769: nyi ma de dag re re la //
NG0201:2770: rang gi ngo bo rgyu dang gnas //
NG0201:2771: sgra dang las de rnam pa lnga'o //
NG0201:2772: gshin rje la yang rnam gsum ste //
NG0201:2773: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NG0201:2774: gshin rje de dag re re la //
NG0201:2775: rang gi ngo bo rgyu dang sgra //
NG0201:2776: gnas dang las te lnga ru bstan //
NG0201:2777: gshin rje de dag gnas pas na //
NG0201:2778: gshin rje'i grong khyer zhes kyang bya //
NG0201:2779: grong khyer de ru sems can kun //
NG0201:2780: khri dang dgug dang gnas pas na //
NG0201:2781: srid pa gsum gyi gnas sa yin //
NG0201:2782: ting nge 'dzin la rnam gsum ste //
NG0201:2783: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NG0201:2784: gsum po de dag re re la /
NG0201:2785: byin brlab bzlas pa ting 'dzin dang *//
NG0201:2786: ngo bo rgyu dang las dang sgra //
NG0201:2787: de dag rnam pa drug tu 'dod //
NG0201:2788: pho dang mo yi mtshan nyid kyang *//
NG0201:2789: g.yas dang g.yon gyi bye brag gis //
NG0201:2790: 'gro ba'i chos bzhin gcod par byed //
NG0201:2791: drag po'i ngan sngags phung byed 'di //
NG0201:2792: gshin rje gshed pos rab tu bsngags //
NG0201:2793: rdo rje 'dzin pas rab tu zung *//
NG0201:2794: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:2795: nag po gsal byed sgron ma'i skabs te rtsa brgyad
NG0201:2796: pa'o // // gshin rje gshed kyis gsungs pa'i don
NG0201:2797: // nyon cig zung zhig rdo rje 'dzin //
NG0201:2798: gsang bar brgyud du brnag pa'i lung *//
NG0201:2799: don gnyis dag tu shes par bya //
NG0201:2800: bsnyen bsgrub dang ni phrin las so //
NG0201:2801: bsnyen pa la yang rnam gnyis te //
NG0201:2802: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga ste //
NG0201:2803: bsod nams bsag par bstan pa dang *//
NG0201:2804: bsnyen pa dngos nyid bstan pa'o //
NG0201:2805: thabs dang dgos pa rnam gnyis kyis //
NG0201:2806: bsod nams bsags pa'i cho gar 'dod //
NG0201:2807: ngo bo dbye ba nges pa'i tshig / dgos ched rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NG0201:2808: bsnyen pa'i dbye ba bstan pa yin //
NG0201:2809: bsgrub pa la yang bcu gnyis te //
NG0201:2810: gnas dang brtul zhugs mtshan ma gzhag / mchod rdzas gzhag dang dngos grub rten //
NG0201:2812: grub pa'i rtags dang blang ba'i thabs //
NG0201:2813: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang ni //
NG0201:2814: sgrub pa'i dus dang spogs pa'i thabs //
NG0201:2815: spogs pa chen po'i cho ga ste //
NG0201:2816: drag shul ting 'dzin bcu gnyis kyis //
NG0201:2817: dngos grub blang ba'i cho gar 'dod //
NG0201:2818: phrin las dag la rnam gsum ste //
NG0201:2819: 'khor lo bskor dang gnan bsreg pa'o //
NG0201:2820: dus dang gang zag bskor ba'i gnas //
NG0201:2821: ngo bo dbye ba nges pa'i tshig / 'khor lo rgyu rkyen @#//
NG0201:2823: sgrub byed grogs dang ma grub skyon //
NG0201:2824: grub pa'i thabs dang spogs pa'i thabs //
NG0201:2825: dbye ba bcu gsum ma yi ngag / ces gshin rje gshed pos rab tu brjod //
NG0201:2826: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:2827: las kyi mdo byang gi skabs te rtsa dgu pa'o
NG0201:2828: // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje
NG0201:2829: gshed pos 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0201:2830: dus tshod mtshon cha rnon po la //
NG0201:2831: rdo rje slob dpon sku dgra sogs //
NG0201:2832: the tshom med par bsgral bas 'grub //
NG0201:2833: phag sbrul ston dpyid ra ba la //
NG0201:2834: byi ba rta ni ston dpyid 'bring *//
NG0201:2835: ston dpyid tha chung glang lug la'o //
NG0201:2836: stag sprel dbyar dgun ra bar shes //
NG0201:2837: dbyar dgun 'bring po bya yos la'o //
NG0201:2839: de ni lo gshed zla ba'i keg par nyi ma'i gshed gnyis te //
NG0201:2841: de yi dus su gsad pa shis //
NG0201:2842: zhag gi gshed du gyur pa yang *//
NG0201:2843: ra ba bzhi la bcu bzhi shis //
NG0201:2844: 'bring po bzhi yi bco lnga la //
NG0201:2845: tha chung bzhi yi bcu drug go / tshes bzhi brgyad dang bcu gcig dang *//
NG0201:2846: bco lnga bco brgyad nyi shu gnyis //
NG0201:2847: nyi shu lnga dang nyi shu dgu / dus ni srod dang snga dro dang *//
NG0201:2848: 'jing dang nam gung gung chung dang *//
NG0201:2849: nyi myur skya rengs shar ba dang *//
NG0201:2850: nyin mtshan zhag gi go rim bzhin //
NG0201:2851: de phyir ma gshin 'tshol phyir rgyu //
NG0201:2852: btsal nas gsad pa'i dus bstan pa //
NG0201:2853: dpyid ra tshes bdun dag la shis //
NG0201:2854: 'bring po bcu bdun dag la shis //
NG0201:2855: tha chung nyi shu bdun la shis //
NG0201:2856: dbyar ra tshes brgyad 'bring po ni //
NG0201:2857: bco brgyad tha chung nyi shu brgyad //
NG0201:2858: ston ra tshes dgu 'bring po ni //
NG0201:2859: bcu dgu tha chung nyi shu dgu / dgun zla gsum yang de bzhin te //
NG0201:2860: dus su gsad pa'i las la 'jug / sa yi khams sa dpyid zla gsum /
NG0201:2861: shing gi dbyar zla ston zla me /
NG0201:2862: dgun ni lcags khams 'chi ba'i dus //
NG0201:2863: de dus zhag gshed rgyu bar bya //
NG0201:2864: ra ba bzhi ni rta la dang yang gcod //
NG0201:2865: tha chung dus su 'bring ra chung yang bzhi ste //
NG0201:2866: tha chung khra la brdeg par bya //
NG0201:2867: dgun gsum skar ma gsum 'char te //
NG0201:2868: skar ma'i gshed kyi dus su ni //
NG0201:2869: sbyor ba thams cad rab na yang *//
NG0201:2870: khrag thun la sogs zor rnams shis //
NG0201:2871: lo zla zhag gi dus bstan nas //
NG0201:2872: dus tshod rnon po bstan par bya //
NG0201:2873: sems can yid ni gnyid log pas //
NG0201:2874: de dus rgyu zhing 'khyam pa'i tshe //
NG0201:2875: kun kyang rnam rtog las byung bas //
NG0201:2876: sbyor ba'i stobs bskyed gsad par shis //
NG0201:2877: sha ba srod dang nam phyed na //
NG0201:2878: lug dang gnyan gyi bla yang rgyu //
NG0201:2879: phag pa tho rangs bya nyid ni //
NG0201:2880: nyi ma zer la rgyu bar bshad //
NG0201:2881: ra bla nyi ma nub ka ste //
NG0201:2882: bya bla nyi ma zer la rgyu //
NG0201:2883: g.yag dang glang bla srod la rgyu //
NG0201:2884: rta bla nyi ma gung la rgyu //
NG0201:2885: de dag dgug cing gsad par shis //
NG0201:2886: thun mong bsgral ba'i thabs su gsungs //
NG0201:2889: 'gyur ba'i bla dang sbyar te bya'o //
NG0201:2890: khams kyi gshed du bstan pa ni //
NG0201:2891: sgrub pa po dang lo zla dang *//
NG0201:2892: dus tshod kyis ni gsod par byed //
NG0201:2893: keg ni gshed po glang dang lug / lo dgra bya dang sprel nyid de //
NG0201:2894: dgun zla dbyar zla tha chung gnyis //
NG0201:2895: dus tshod nyin phyed nam phyed yol //
NG0201:2896: ha la sman gyis gsod 'gyur na //
NG0201:2897: bsgrub pa'i sbyor bas smos ci dgos //
NG0201:2898: khyi 'brug ji yi gshed po ste //
NG0201:2899: phag dang byi ba lo dgra nyid //
NG0201:2900: mi mthun bdun zur the tshom med //
NG0201:2901: zla gshed ston dpyid tha chung ste //
NG0201:2902: zla ba'i bdun zur rdo rjes gcod //
NG0201:2903: tho rangs srod la gsod par byed //
NG0201:2905: sbyor bas bdun rgyud the tshom med //
NG0201:2906: gung la khyi 'brug shing khams pa //
NG0201:2907: shing dang kha dog 'dra ba ste //
NG0201:2908: gsod pa'i las la the tshom med //
NG0201:2909: stag dang yos bu dar ba dgra //
NG0201:2910: bdun zur gshed du gyur pa ste //
NG0201:2911: tshangs pa'i me bzhin gsod par byed //
NG0201:2912: zla gshed srog dang mi mthun pa'i //
NG0201:2913: bdun zur gsod de the tshom med //
NG0201:2914: dus tshod nam phyed dus la shes //
NG0201:2915: shang gi khams te gshed chen po //
NG0201:2916: shang gi gshed dang 'u yi tshig thog ma chad /
NG0201:2917: 'dus pa sa yi khams la gcod //
NG0201:2918: lo dgra glang lug gnyis kyis te //
NG0201:2919: mi mthun bdun zur shin tu 'joms //
NG0201:2920: dus tshod mtshan ma rang sar shis //
NG0201:2921: de nas mthun 'phrod bshad pa ni //
NG0201:2922: bzang zhing 'grub par bya ba'i las //
NG0201:2923: bdud rgyal nyi ma bdun po la //
NG0201:2924: drag sngags tshogs kyis cham la dbab //
NG0201:2925: nyi ma gru sogs bre ru 'byor //
NG0201:2926: bi rdzi bya gzhus zla bar 'byor //
NG0201:2927: mig dmar khrums smad la ro sman //
NG0201:2928: gza' lhag sgrog dang smin drug 'dzom //
NG0201:2929: phur bu rgyal stod rgyal smad mthun //
NG0201:2930: pa sangs bya gzhug rta chung nyid //
NG0201:2931: spen pa sa ri sa ga ste //
NG0201:2932: de ltar mthun sbyor dus su ni //
NG0201:2934: de phyir bzang po'i las la 'jug / bdud kyi nyi ma bshad pa ni //
NG0201:2935: nyi ma lag sor bya cha spyad kyang skyor gsum //
NG0201:2936: zla ba rgyal smad bre ru gsod //
NG0201:2937: mig dmar bre dang sgrog gis te //
NG0201:2938: gza' lhag dbyug pa nyid kyis 'jig / phur bu
NG0201:2939: mgo ru 'byor bas 'jig / pa sangs wa dang
NG0201:2940: lag sor gsum // spen pa bya ma bdud kyi nyi //
NG0201:2941: bzang po'i las kyis gsod 'gyur na //
NG0201:2942: ngan pa'i las kyis smos ci dgos //
NG0201:2943: mi 'phrod bdun du bshad pa ni //
NG0201:2944: nyi ma khrums smad zla ba dang *//
NG0201:2945: sa ga mi 'phrod mig dmar dang *//
NG0201:2946: lag tu mi 'phrod gza' lhag dang *//
NG0201:2947: gru sog mi 'phrod phur bu sgrog / pa wa sangs dang bre mi 'phrod //
NG0201:2948: spen pa dag ni khrums stod dang *//
NG0201:2949: de lta'i mi 'phrod bdun po la //
NG0201:2950: phan gdags las ni gcig mi 'grub //
NG0201:2951: nyi ma dang ni sa ga 'jig / zla ba dang ni bi rdzi ste //
NG0201:2952: mig dmar sgrog tu 'jig par bstan //
NG0201:2954: phur bu la ni be'u rdzi 'jig / pa wa sangs @#//
NG0201:2955: la bya gzhug 'jig / spen pa la ni bya
NG0201:2956: ma 'jig / mi 'phrod bdun dang 'jig pa bdun
NG0201:2957: // bdun kye nyi mar gsad pa shis //
NG0201:2958: 'tsho byed yul lhas skyob pa ni //
NG0201:2959: g.yag dkar mi dkar tshul gyis 'gegs //
NG0201:2960: bud med rtug pa bsreg nas kyang *//
NG0201:2961: 'chi bdag rnams kyi bla rkun bzlas //
NG0201:2962: zhang blon bzang po lta bu ni //
NG0201:2963: pho lhas 'ges pas de dus su //
NG0201:2964: glang rog ra bsreg gong bzhin bya //
NG0201:2965: khra'am spyang ki lta bus skyob //
NG0201:2966: dgra bla yin te gsur chen btang *//
NG0201:2967: khyi lud bsreg pas 'bros par byed //
NG0201:2968: bud med sha ba lta bu ni //
NG0201:2969: ma lha ma sman 'go ba ste //
NG0201:2970: ra dang rta sbangs tal nag bsreg / ting 'dzin mi gsal bying rmugs na //
NG0201:2971: pho lhas 'geg pa yin par brjod //
NG0201:2972: til nag nyung nag gu gul ni //
NG0201:2973: sbyar mas bsreg na 'bros par byed //
NG0201:2974: ma 'phrod dbye ba'i thabs bstan pa //
NG0201:2975: bya rog 'ug pa'i gung ru la //
NG0201:2976: gro gar a dang shog shog nr-i //
NG0201:2977: go rim bzhin du glan bar bya //
NG0201:2978: yug sa mo yi rkang dreg dang *//
NG0201:2979: 'bog dang glang rog ra khrag sogs //
NG0201:2980: sme ba'i dud pas dus gsum bdug / 'di ni dbye ba'i mchog tu gsungs //
NG0201:2981: nag po gsal byed sgron ma las //
NG0201:2982: bya thabs nyams len nying khu 'di //
NG0201:2983: rang byung dgra la bya ba'i dus su gsungs //
NG0201:2984: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:2985: bya thabs nyams len nying khu'i skabs te sum cu
NG0201:2986: pa'o // // de nas 'jam dbyangs khro bos phyogs
NG0201:2987: skyong gshin rje las la skul ba 'di gsungs so
NG0201:2988: // bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NG0201:2989: yab yum gnyis med thugs kyi sras //
NG0201:2990: steng phyogs gshin rje nag 'joms ni //
NG0201:2991: nag po g.yas na dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0201:2992: chibs su lkugs pa lug la chibs //
NG0201:2993: khro mo srin mo mgo 'phyang ma //
NG0201:2994: nag mo chen mo ral pa can //
NG0201:2995: g.yas pa thabs kyi gtso la 'khyud //
NG0201:2996: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NG0201:2997: yab gcig 'jam dpal bka' byung gis //
NG0201:2999: bstan pa 'jig pa'i gshed ma mdzod //
NG0201:3000: bdud po bcu yis khram la thob //
NG0201:3001: ging chen bco brgyad las la bskul //
NG0201:3003: dus la bab po sa ma ya /
NG0201:3004: dam las ma 'da' phrin las mdzod //

NG0201:3007: dkar po lag na bum pa thogs //
NG0201:3008: chibs su ban glang dkar po chibs //
NG0201:3009: khro mo kham rgya mthu mo che //
NG0201:3010: nag mo mgo 'phyangs ral pa can //
NG0201:3011: g.yas pa thabs kyis gtso la 'khyud //
NG0201:3012: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NG0201:3013: yab gcig 'jam dpal bka' byung gis //

NG0201:3017: ging chen bco brgyad las la skul //
NG0201:3019: dus la bab po sa ma @#//

NG0201:3792: lug nag lcags ru gser mig la //
NG0201:3793: re ba'i sgye ni khal du bkal /
NG0201:3794: g.yas su pho rnams ming rus gzhug / g.yon du
NG0201:3795: mo rnams ming rus gzhug / sngo dmar skud pos
NG0201:3796: gong rmed bya // ra la dar lce mthing nag gdab /
NG0201:3797: mig gnyis nang du rin chen brdar /
NG0201:3798: dar dkar yug gis mig gnyis dgab //
NG0201:3799: dkyil 'khor byang shang gra ru dgod //
NG0201:3800: dur khrod ras la 'khor lo bca' //
NG0201:3801: thod pa dug khrag bsres la dgang */
NG0201:3802: gos nag gyon la thod nag bcings //
NG0201:3803: bdud kyi g.yab dar lag tu thogs //
NG0201:3804: gtum chen bstod la bdud rnams rbad //
NG0201:3806: hum phat pa hum le ma pa sha sta ha
NG0201:3807: sta pa ba le rang ba mang sha pa ra
NG0201:3808: ya hum ma he pa mang ga la ya hum
NG0201:3809: phat / sum 'bum bzlas na gang yang 'grub //
NG0201:3810: de bzhin bsgrub na mngon du 'gyur //
NG0201:3811: dpal 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:3812: bdud gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te so drug
NG0201:3813: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das gshed pos
NG0201:3814: 'jig rten gyi khams mer bsreg pa'i btsan phyi ltar
NG0201:3816: brag dmar rtsa'am dur khrod du //
NG0201:3817: sa bdag zhi bya klu gtor gtang *//
NG0201:3819: ra dmar khrag gis chag chag gdag / dbus kyi lte ba dmar po la //
NG0201:3820: zla gam dmar po brgyad kyis bskor //
NG0201:3822: zla gam re la ma ra ya //
NG0201:3823: ra dmar bse 'gram phyi rten bca' //
NG0201:3824: dbus su bshos bu gru gang gzhag / ra khrag
NG0201:3825: dag gis dmar por byug / za 'og dmar po
NG0201:3826: mda' gang gdags // ra lpags dmar po mda' gang la //
NG0201:3827: zer mo ldem pa'i phod kyis brgyan //
NG0201:3828: dbus kyi zla gam steng du gzhag / de 'khor zla gam brgyad po la //
NG0201:3829: bshos cha brgyad la mda' dmar brgyad //
NG0201:3830: dar dang ra lpags dmar po dang *//
NG0201:3831: zer mo'i phod kyi brgyan pa brgyad //
NG0201:3832: phyi rim zla gam brgyad la dgod //
NG0201:3833: gser brdar chang phud bya'o dgu //
NG0201:3834: 'bras dang til nag la sogs pas //
NG0201:3835: zla gam dgu la phul dgu gzhag / dur khrod ras la 'khor lo ni //
NG0201:3836: rtsibs brgyad pa ru bya bar bshad //
NG0201:3837: om la li pra ma ni ri tse thal ba ni /
NG0201:3838: tri nyi nyi sham tri mu tri ri tri tri /
NG0201:3839: re tri ham sham stam sarba karma se pa be ba swa ha /
NG0201:3840: 'di ni dbang dang drag po'i sngags //
NG0201:3841: dgug dang rbad pa'i sngags 'di brjod //
NG0201:3842: srog la li pra na ma ni bam ril dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3844: bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3845: kro d+hi ko ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3846: kro d+hi ki la ya sha la bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3847: om tri gam sham ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3849: tri ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3850: re tri ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo ma ra ya nr-i dza /
NG0201:3851: ham sham stam bu ma ra ya bam ri li li dgra bo nr-i dza /
NG0201:3852: rang gsang dpon g.yog dgu'i snying brjod par bya'o //
NG0201:3853: srog la li pra ma ni dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dzah /
NG0201:3854: srog la ma ra ya nr-i dam nyams dgra bo'i srog la dza dz+wa dzah /
NG0201:3855: srog kro d+hi ki la ya ma ra ya dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dz+wah //
NG0201:3856: srog kro d+hi sho la ya ya ma ra ya dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dzah /
NG0201:3857: srog kam ti kam sham ma ra ya dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dzah /
NG0201:3858: srog gi sham tri ma ra ya dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dzah /
NG0201:3859: srog mu tri re'u tri dam nyams dgra bo'i snying la dza dza dzah /
NG0201:3860: dmigs pa'i gzugs la sngags kyis brdeg / gshin rje bstod la btsan rnams rbad //
NG0201:3864: mi ring dmar po mthu rtsal can //
NG0201:3865: dbu la skra med bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar //
NG0201:3866: 'jig rten khams kun me yis bsreg / smin ma lcags gyu 'khril ba 'dra //
NG0201:3867: spyan rtsa dmar po dam nyams dgra la bzlog / sku+u la le brgan dmar po'i 'jol ber gsol //
NG0201:3868: g.yas nas btsan gyi rgyu zhags dgra la 'debs //
NG0201:3869: g.yon na hu lu'i ltas ngan dgra la 'bebs //
NG0201:3870: zhabs la lcags lham yu thung gsol //
NG0201:3871: sbrul nag stong gi chun bskor can //
NG0201:3872: sbrul nag gzhibs pa'i sku regs bcings //
NG0201:3873: skar chen dmar po'i tshar tshar can //
NG0201:3874: bzhugs ni gling bzhi khyab par bzhugs //
NG0201:3875: nam gyi gung la rgyu tsa na //
NG0201:3876: brag gi wa mo kha nag chibs //
NG0201:3877: nyi ma'i zer la rgyu tsa na //
NG0201:3878: chibs su ltas ngan gla ba chibs //
NG0201:3879: nyi ma'i gung la rgyu tsha na //
NG0201:3880: chibs su bra bo rting dkar chibs //
NG0201:3881: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di longs la //
NG0201:3883: 'khor gyi btsan rnams las la bskul //
NG0201:3884: 'jig rten khams su me yi bskal pa thongs //
NG0201:3885: dgra bo'i rnam shes brgyad po thal bar rlogs //
NG0201:3886: skyes bu chen po dgra la ya //
NG0201:3887: rang gsang mched dgu dgra la ya //
NG0201:3888: btsan gyi zhags pa da sdogs la //
NG0201:3889: tha ram dgra la da thob cig / khrag skyug gze thabs pur gyis thob //
NG0201:3890: ces phrin las bcol tsa ra bam rog rten du bca' //
NG0201:3891: lo dang zla bar brlag par 'gyur ro //
NG0201:3892: be'u rdzi wa dang rta chung dang *//
NG0201:3893: lag sor rnams la gong bzhin bskul //
NG0201:3894: chang phud gtor zhing las gnyer gtad //
NG0201:3895: rtags phyin pa dang gtang rag gtang *//
NG0201:3896: gsob dang bshos cha dbul bar bya //
NG0201:3897: gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:3898: 'jig rten khams kun mes bsreg pa'i btsan gyi zla
NG0201:3899: gsang phyi ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te so bdun pa'o
NG0201:3900: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen
NG0201:3901: pos // btsan nang ltar sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:3904: dur khrod nags tshal 'thug po ru //
NG0201:3906: dug dang khrag gis chag chag gdab //
NG0201:3907: dbus su gru gsum thur du brko //
NG0201:3908: mu su ra yi thod pa ru //
NG0201:3909: rdo sol spra ba ras la sogs //
NG0201:3910: til mar bsres te gzhag par bya //
NG0201:3911: de la zla gam gsum gyis bskor //
NG0201:3912: phyi rim 'dzam bu'i gling bzhi bris //
NG0201:3913: lcags ri la sogs me 'od bris //
NG0201:3914: dbus su ya ma gshed po ste //
NG0201:3915: zla gam gsum la yum sras dgod //
NG0201:3916: zla gam steng du btsan gyi rgyal //
NG0201:3917: rdo rje reg bya gser mig dgod //
NG0201:3918: lho ru rdo rje grags mchog dgod //
NG0201:3919: nub tu rdo rje mgyogs byed rtsal //
NG0201:3920: byang du rdo rje shu bo 'bar //
NG0201:3921: yab yum rdzas su bshams pa yang *//
NG0201:3922: mi sha rta sha'i gtor ma dang *//
NG0201:3923: snying chen gcig la brten te bsgrub //
NG0201:3924: phyogs bzhir gtor ma bzhi byas la //
NG0201:3925: shu bo mched bzhi'i rdzas su dgod //
NG0201:3926: rang mar snying dang bya se'i snying *//
NG0201:3927: rta mtshal snying la btsan rnams brten //
NG0201:3928: bya rgod mda' la le brgan dar //
NG0201:3929: lag tu thogs la rtag tu g.yab //
NG0201:3930: gri bo'i thod par tha ram bca' //
NG0201:3931: rtag tu ra gsur rgyun tu gtang *//
NG0201:3932: gser skyems la sogs gser sbyar bas //
NG0201:3933: rtag tu btsan la mchod pa bya //
NG0201:3934: spyugs pa'i glu blang rnga gling 'bud //
NG0201:3935: rtag tu nyung dkar nyung nag la //
NG0201:3936: sngags bzlas gru gsum thod par gsib //
NG0201:3937: rnam gsum ting 'dzin btsan rnams bskyed //
NG0201:3938: a bi shu+u sa ma ya ra dza be ni
NG0201:3939: a na na sta tri shal rbad dz+ha ra ga
NG0201:3940: ting san d+ha ra shu+u na tsit+ta b+ha smi ku
NG0201:3941: ku dza dza / khri'am 'bum du bzlas gyur na //
NG0201:3942: sku yang dngos su ston par 'gyur //
NG0201:3943: gzhan yang rta med srab sgra dang *//
NG0201:3944: mi med spyugs pa di re 'ong *//
NG0201:3945: de bzhin las la sbyor bar bya //
NG0201:3946: gshed po bskul la btsan rnams rbad //
NG0201:3948: rdo sol rdzas sbyar dam rdzas la //
NG0201:3949: rtsa ba'i sngags la ram ram sbyar //
NG0201:3950: de yi sngags rnams rab tu bzlas //
NG0201:3951: zla gsang bu la shes bya zhing *//
NG0201:3952: gsad pa'i las kyang gong dang 'dra //
NG0201:3953: gtso ru rang gi dam tshig bsrung *//
NG0201:3954: ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod lam bya //
NG0201:3955: yengs na gang yang mi 'grub ste //
NG0201:3956: rtag tu mi dang nye mi bya //
NG0201:3957: tha ram bcas pa'i thod pa de //
NG0201:3959: brag btsan mu btsan yod sar sba //
NG0201:3961: 'jam dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:3962: 'jig rten gyi khams mes bsreg pa btsan gyi zla
NG0201:3963: gsang nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te so brgyad pa'o
NG0201:3964: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen
NG0201:3965: pos btsan gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa 'di gsungs so
NG0201:3966: // dgon pa dur khrod lta bu ru //
NG0201:3967: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum brtsigs //
NG0201:3968: dbus su rabs chad thod pa ru //
NG0201:3969: khrag sogs dug sogs rdo sol dang *//
NG0201:3970: dur khraud ras dang til gyi mar //
NG0201:3973: ming dang rus bris thod par bzhug / bse phor zangs gzhong gtor mas dgang *//
NG0201:3974: zung gzhag srog snying tshad du grangs //
NG0201:3975: om des tri mang gan dza mus mus ma ra na ya ma ra ya na ya /
NG0201:3976: dgra bo che go mo'i srog breng breng thum b+h+yo dza dza /
NG0201:3977: 'di ni rab tu mi 'grub bsgrub yang sngags //
NG0201:3980: ri la sbas na ri mes tshig / khyad par rgya mtsho lta bu'am //
NG0201:3981: chu mig sbas na chu yang khol //
NG0201:3982: dgra yi gdung gseb sbas gyur na //
NG0201:3984: de nas sngags de nyid 'od zu'i sdong po la //
NG0201:3985: lan stong du bzlas nas byin na smyo bar 'gyur ro //
NG0201:3986: d+ha du ra'i lo ma dang sha pra ba de dang */
NG0201:3987: ka ka ri la bzlas nas byin na mdzer 'gyur ro //
NG0201:3988: be'u be dang ka ni la bzlas nas byin na /
NG0201:3990: za'i 'bras la bzlas nas phyogs su gtor na /
NG0201:3991: sbrul chen po khang pa'i nang du 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
NG0201:3992: rdo sol la bzlas nas b+han d+ha'i nang du chang
NG0201:3993: dung sbyar nas rtsa gseb bam shing gseb tu sbas
NG0201:3995: rdo sol la bzlas te chang gral du grogs po'i
NG0201:3996: chang la btab na mer rang gis 'gro bar 'gyur
NG0201:3997: ro // bse zho dang btsan dug sbyar la btab
NG0201:3998: nas dgra'i lus sam sha la reg pa'i gos la
NG0201:3999: bskus na lhog pa dkar pos 'chi bar 'gyur ro
NG0201:4000: ro // // 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:4001: 'jig rten mes sreg btsan gyi zla gsang gsang ba
NG0201:4002: ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te so dgu pa'o // //
NG0201:4003: de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos /
NG0201:4004: chu 'khyags drag tu dbab pa khyab 'jug gza'i drag sngags 'di gsungs te /
NG0201:4005: gza' phyi ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs bshad pa //
NG0201:4006: thog mar dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NG0201:4007: ri gsum rtse'am dur khrod du //
NG0201:4008: dbang thob bya phyir bla ma mnyes bya zhing *//
NG0201:4009: dkyil 'khor bris nas dam tshig dbang dag nod //
NG0201:4010: dgos pa bsgrub phyir man ngag thob par bya //
NG0201:4011: man ngag thob nas bsnyen bsgrub mtha' ru dbyung *//
NG0201:4012: bsnyen pa bya zhing mthun rdzas 'bad de bsag / khyab 'jug las kyi go rim ni //
NG0201:4013: gzhan dang mthun par cho ga dang *//
NG0201:4014: mchod dang gzu dpang gsol ba gdab //
NG0201:4015: gtor ma la sogs cho ga bya //
NG0201:4016: dbab gsad las kyi go rim ni //
NG0201:4017: chos grangs phyogs dang dus tshod dang *//
NG0201:4019: go rim bzhin du so sor sbyar //
NG0201:4020: bzhi la nub nas shar du srod //
NG0201:4021: ma mor sprul te rkang pa g.yas //
NG0201:4022: brgyad la shar lho mtshams nas su //
NG0201:4023: nyi ma dros te nub byang du //
NG0201:4024: dgra lha'i rgyal mor mjug ma sprul //
NG0201:4025: bcu gcig 'jing la byang nas lho //
NG0201:4026: bdud tu sprul te lag pa gnyis //
NG0201:4027: bco lnga nam phyed lho nub nas //
NG0201:4028: byang shar mtshams su rgyu ba ste //
NG0201:4029: srin por sprul te mgo bo @#//
NG0201:4031: bco brgyad nam yol shar nas nub //
NG0201:4032: dmu ru sprul nas dpung mgo g.yon //
NG0201:4033: nyi shu gnyis la nyi ma myur //
NG0201:4034: nub byang mtshams nas shar lho ru //
NG0201:4035: gshin rjer sprul nas lag pa g.yon //
NG0201:4036: nyi shu lnga la lho nas byang *//
NG0201:4037: skya rengs chas te dpung mgo mig / klu btsan gdon du sprul te rgyu //
NG0201:4038: nyi shu dgu ste myur chung na //
NG0201:4039: byang shar mtshams nas lho nub tu //
NG0201:4040: gza' bdud chen por sprul te rgyu //
NG0201:4041: de yi dbab gsad sbyor ba ni //
NG0201:4042: phyogs kyi gdon sprul re re la //
NG0201:4043: gsad pa'i sbyor ba so sor bya //
NG0201:4044: gdon sprul so sor rgyu ba ste //
NG0201:4045: ma mor sprul pa'i gzugs brnyan ni //
NG0201:4046: nag mo chen mo ral pa can //
NG0201:4047: 'jigs pa'i rgyan cha mang po dang *//
NG0201:4048: lag na thod khrag 'thor zhing rgyu //
NG0201:4049: rlung drag thog dang rdzi kha rgyu //
NG0201:4050: rgyal mo sngo skya ka dar thogs //
NG0201:4051: sngo skya zhon te 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0201:4052: sgra dang ser ba mtshan mo'o //
NG0201:4053: sprul pa dud ni mdog nag po //
NG0201:4054: lag na gri nag zhags pa thogs //
NG0201:4055: rta nag zhon te gdon dang bcas //
NG0201:4056: btsan thabs drag po'i nad rnams dang *//
NG0201:4057: dus med mtshan ma mang du 'byung *//
NG0201:4058: 'jigs pa'i srin po sngo nag la //
NG0201:4059: mig rtsa dmar la sdang mig bgrad //
NG0201:4060: mche ba gtsigs te za ba'i tshul //
NG0201:4061: mda' gzhu thogs te gdon dang rgyu //
NG0201:4063: sprul pa dmu ste thog ser 'bebs //
NG0201:4064: dmar po khrag gi thig le can //
NG0201:4065: ba glang zhon te 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0201:4066: mtshan ma thob dang sprin nag 'khrugs //
NG0201:4067: klu gdon drag por sprul pa ni //
NG0201:4068: sprul nag chen po 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NG0201:4070: chu drag glog dang chas pa'o //
NG0201:4071: nag po chen po 'khor lo thogs //
NG0201:4072: gdon gyi gtso bor sprul te 'ong *//
NG0201:4073: rgyu ba'i dus dang mtshungs nges na //
NG0201:4074: mtshan ma myur du phung bar 'gyur //
NG0201:4075: de la dbang gsang sbyor ba brgyad //
NG0201:4076: nges par rgyu ba'i dus su bya //
NG0201:4078: gru bzhi'i dkyil 'khor dbus su ni //
NG0201:4079: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dbus su e /
NG0201:4080: phyogs mtshams brgyad la e brgyad bkod //
NG0201:4081: e dgu nag po'i 'khor lo bskor //
NG0201:4082: 'khor lo'i rtsibs la sprul pa brgyad //
NG0201:4083: bskyed la dbab gsad sbyor ba bri //
NG0201:4084: dbus su gshed po yab yum ste //
NG0201:4085: kha hir bcas pas gtor ma sbyin //
NG0201:4086: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi sprul pa la //
NG0201:4087: so so'i las kyi bya ba brtsam //
NG0201:4088: dgug dang brdeg dang bstab pa'i las //
NG0201:4089: 'grogs pa'i tshul te gdong tshugs min //
NG0201:4090: bsreg dang mchod pa la sogs pa //
NG0201:4091: phyogs mtshams brgyad nas drangs te dbul //
NG0201:4092: phyogs mtshams brgyad du gsad pa ste //
NG0201:4093: dbus kyi e la bsreg pa'o //
NG0201:4094: sprul pa'i mgo bo rgyu ba'i tshe //
NG0201:4095: brnag pa'i dpral ba'i dbyings su gdab //
NG0201:4096: rkang pa g.yas g.yon rgyu ba ni //
NG0201:4097: bol gong g.yas g.yon gnyis su gdab //
NG0201:4100: gdab pa'i las kyang de bzhin gdab //
NG0201:4101: tsher ma can gyi shing la bsreg / rgyu ba'i dus su mtshungs nges na //
NG0201:4102: phung bar 'gyur te gdon mi za //
NG0201:4103: gdon dang phye ma rnam pa gnyis //
NG0201:4104: gdon gyi rdzas la nus pa yod //
NG0201:4105: phye ma gdon gyi bya ba de //
NG0201:4106: zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las gsungs //
NG0201:4107: gza' bdud rgyu ba'i dus nges na //
NG0201:4108: rjes dang dri ma'i 'dag pa la //
NG0201:4109: gos dum dri ma rnying pa dang *//
NG0201:4110: gdug pa'i gzugs brnyan bzhi byas te //
NG0201:4111: rnam grangs nang du gsad byad na //
NG0201:4112: gong ma'i rdzas dang tsha ba gsum //
NG0201:4113: bsres te gzugs brnyan bya bar gsungs //
NG0201:4114: myur du gsad pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0201:4115: gong ma'i steng du ha las bya //
NG0201:4116: gong ma bzhi la lcags phye dang *//
NG0201:4117: khrag gi sbyor bas gri nyid du //
NG0201:4118: til dang ske tshe nyung nag dang *//
NG0201:4119: khrag sna zi ra gu gul dang *//
NG0201:4120: gong gi rdzas kyis ma nges bsad //
NG0201:4121: dur khrod ras sam shing shun la //
NG0201:4122: skyang nul byas te smug nag gam //
NG0201:4123: yang na so nag dmar por bya //
NG0201:4124: de la brnag pa'i sbyor ba bya'o //
NG0201:4125: myur du dbab pa'i las bya na //
NG0201:4126: dam sri yul gyi chu sogs bsag / yugs sa mo'am rabs chad thod //
NG0201:4127: yang na mdzecan thod pa ru //
NG0201:4128: mi khrag khyi khrag ra khrag dang *//
NG0201:4129: mngal khrag la sogs dme khrag sogs //
NG0201:4130: ba dkar 'o ma mdzo dang ra'i //
NG0201:4131: 'o ma la sogs sbyar ba bya //
NG0201:4132: sngo sna dug sna gu gul sbyar //
NG0201:4133: gar 'bebs chu mig klu yod sar //
NG0201:4134: bsregs sam bskol na klu rnams dang *//
NG0201:4135: dus tshod gza' yi gdong thug na //
NG0201:4137: ma ha tsan+d+ha rak+sha tri tha ni ma tha ya //
NG0201:4138: che ge mo la tri b+h+yo /
NG0201:4139: zhes pa ni sprul pa srin po'i gdon gyis dbab cing gsad pa'o //
NG0201:4140: na ga ra dza be ni ne a nan sta /
NG0201:4141: na ga ra dza ra sha ting san d+ha ra k+shu na /
NG0201:4144: klu'i gdon gyis dbab cing gsad pa'o //
NG0201:4145: rmu+u tri tsa d+ha dum dum bum bum kha la rak+sha thum ri li li /
NG0201:4146: kha shag bam raka stam thum ri li li //
NG0201:4147: dmu bdud sprul pas dbab cing gsad pa'o //
NG0201:4148: ma ma sa ma ya ma trag sha ma tra
NG0201:4149: 'ga' nas kha ya ku ru te tso pa la
NG0201:4150: ya a / yu shwa ha ra d+ha ra /
NG0201:4151: u ma ma dam ni sha tru na sha ya ni dza dzah /
NG0201:4152: ma mo'i gdon gyis dbab gsad pa'o //
NG0201:4153: tri dkar mo tri dul dul snying khrag la ril ril /
NG0201:4154: chom chom tsa la thun shig ma ra na dza /
NG0201:4155: rgyal mo sngo skyas dbab gsad pa'o //
NG0201:4156: ya ma tsan d+ha d+hi ta dza la tsakra d+ha
NG0201:4157: ra na sha ya dgra bo nr-i ma ra ya
NG0201:4158: sod sod chom chom shig shig / gshin rje'i gdon
NG0201:4160: ma ha bid+he ba tra bish+nu tsan+d+ha tu ba ni ra hu la dgra bo'i tsit+ta la /
NG0201:4162: he ka li ma ha tsan d+ha ma ra ya nr-i khug khug dza dza /
NG0201:4163: gza' bdud chen pos dbab gsad pa'o //
NG0201:4164: bdud tri ni ri tra pa na tri ya /
NG0201:4167: srog rtsa thun che ge mo nr-i nr-i dzah /
NG0201:4168: ces bzlas gar dmigs thogs pa med //
NG0201:4169: gtum chen nyid la rab bstod @#//
NG0201:4171: gza' bdud chen po rab tu rbad //
NG0201:4173: ri rab phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad nas //
NG0201:4174: lha srin sde brgyad bskul re ran //
NG0201:4175: khyab 'jug chen po sku bzhengs shig / gtum po chen po bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4177: de yis ki kang 'bebs byed na //
NG0201:4178: gza' bdud chen po mi srin pa //
NG0201:4179: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyug / 'jigs byed rog ti sprul pa'i lus //
NG0201:4180: lus po gcig la mgo bo dgu / mgo lus med bar mig gis khengs //
NG0201:4181: ro stod mi la ro smad sbrul //
NG0201:4182: lus ni brjid pa'i dud kha la //
NG0201:4183: lag na chu srin zhags pa thogs //
NG0201:4184: pha ni srin la ma ni klu //
NG0201:4185: klu srin tshogs pa'i mthu bo che //
NG0201:4186: lho nub mtshams nas sku bzhengs nas //
NG0201:4187: zla ba'i rjes gcod shar du rgyug / nyi ma'i
NG0201:4188: rjes gcod nub tu rgyug / nyi mo rgyu zhing
NG0201:4189: mtshan mo 'joms // bar snang khams nas rgyu tsa na //
NG0201:4190: 'jig rten khams kun sgrol bar mdzad //
NG0201:4191: lo nyes 'khrug pa yams nad gtong *//
NG0201:4192: nyi ma zla ba lto ru za //
NG0201:4193: rgya mtsho'i gting na gnas pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4194: klu rnams kun kyang 'khrug ces slong *//
NG0201:4195: thog ser sa g.yos ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4196: 'jigs byed chen po mi srun pa //
NG0201:4197: ming brgya pa la mtshan stong po //
NG0201:4198: dus tshod tshes grangs kun gyis bdag / lha srin kun gyi nang dbyen byed //
NG0201:4199: lha srin sde brgyad dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4200: 'byung ba lnga yi bdud chen po //
NG0201:4201: mtshan ni rnam pa dgu ru grags //
NG0201:4203: kun nas rgyug cing ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4204: lho nub mtshams nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4205: srin po rak+sha bi tri ba //
NG0201:4206: ki kang ba ta chen po bya //
NG0201:4207: srin po'i ki kang chen po 'bebs //
NG0201:4208: shar lho mtshams nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4209: drang srong chen po ra hu la /
NG0201:4210: drang srong gi ni ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4211: ki kang bdag nyid can zhes bya //
NG0201:4212: byang shar mtshams nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4214: byi na ya ga pho nyar 'gyed //
NG0201:4215: ki kang 'bebs pa'i las la brtson //
NG0201:4216: nub byang mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4217: du ba mjug rings chen po bya //
NG0201:4218: 'jig rten khams na mthu bo che //
NG0201:4219: 'jig rten g.yo 'gul byed pa'i bdag / lho yi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4220: khyab 'jug chen po bya ba ste //
NG0201:4221: dus tshod tshes grangs kun tu rgyug / sprul pa'i sku ni ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4222: shar gyi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4223: dmu bdud chen po ha li ka / byi nu ra tsa'i ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4224: dmu yi ki kang 'bebs par byed //
NG0201:4225: byang gi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4226: bdud po rog ti 'bar ba'i gzugs //
NG0201:4228: ki kang 'bar ba tsa ra ka / nub kyi phyogs nas bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4229: srid pa'i ma mo rnams dang rol //
NG0201:4230: ma mo'i ki kang kun gyi bdag / ljang sngon chen po'i ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4231: lho nub mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4236: sngon du su phrad khyur mid za //
NG0201:4237: khyod ni khro chen sprul pa ste //
NG0201:4238: lho nub mtshams nas sku bskyod nas //
NG0201:4239: lha srin sde brgyad dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4240: nub nas shar du bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4241: srid pa'i ma mo'i dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4242: nad ngan ki kang dbab pa'i dus la babs //
NG0201:4243: shar lho mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4244: dgra lha'i rgyal mo dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4245: thog dang bu yug ki kang ni //
NG0201:4246: dam sri gdug pa'i snying la 'bebs //
NG0201:4247: byang nas lho ru bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4248: bdud dmag kun gyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4249: bdud kyi ki kang hur thum 'bebs //
NG0201:4250: bdud kyi ki kang dgra la ya //
NG0201:4251: byang shar mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4252: srin po 'bum gyi dmag dpon phyed //
NG0201:4253: srin po'i ki kang dgra la ya //
NG0201:4254: gri thabs sna tshogs ki kang ya /
NG0201:4255: shar nas nub tu bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4256: dmu bdud yongs kyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4257: dmu rdo 'bebs pa'i las byed cing *//
NG0201:4258: gar rbad dmu yi ki kang gtong *//
NG0201:4259: nub byang mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4260: gshin rje yongs kyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4261: skye 'gro yongs kyi bla tshe sdud //
NG0201:4262: gshin rje'i ki kang dbang med 'bebs //
NG0201:4263: lho nas byang du bskyod pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4264: klu btsan kun gyi dmag dpon byed //
NG0201:4265: thog dang ser ba'i sna 'dren cing *//
NG0201:4266: thog ser mdze nad ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4267: nub byang mtshams nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4268: gtib grir gsod pa'i ki kang 'bebs //
NG0201:4269: mdun du gang byung khyur mid byed //
NG0201:4270: ki kang sna tshogs 'bebs pa'i bdag / ki kang sna tshogs dgra la ya //
NG0201:4271: zhes brjod cing rak+ta sbreng phrin las bcol //
NG0201:4272: gsad na bla phur gzugs la brdeg / om badzra ki li ki la ya /
NG0201:4273: shi kri bi tri ki li ki la ya /
NG0201:4274: che ge mo ma ra ya hum phat /
NG0201:4278: ba ra ta thum ru thum ru pa ra pa shu dan ta pa ra pa ta ya /
NG0201:4279: ru ti ru ti sha sa ya /
NG0201:4280: shan ti ku la tri dza /
NG0201:4281: zhes ni gsad pa'i las sbyor bya /
NG0201:4283: sngags kyi man ngag zhag gcig bya //
NG0201:4284: om me kha kha thun kha thun /
NG0201:4286: na bu ta na na kha le ra thun ra thun tu /
NG0201:4287: zhes pa'i sngags bzlas khro tshul bstan //
NG0201:4288: mig bzlog kha bskrad mig sbrin las //
NG0201:4289: khrag sprin dmar pos 'khrigs shing 'dril bar bsam //
NG0201:4290: rdzas rnams gtor zhing lus sprugs pas //
NG0201:4292: gnam sa ri brag kun tu yang *//
NG0201:4293: 'ba' ri sha yas gdon mi za //
NG0201:4294: 'jam dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:4295: chu 'khyags ser ba dbab pa khyab 'jug gza'i drag
NG0201:4296: sngags skabs te bzhi bcu pa'o // // de nas
NG0201:4297: yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos /
NG0201:4298: chu 'khyags drag tu dbab pa'i phyir //
NG0201:4299: rog ti gza' yi nang bsgrub gsungs //
NG0201:4300: dur khrod la sogs dgon pa ru //
NG0201:4301: dkyil 'khor gru gsum sbrag ma bya //
NG0201:4304: snel gri'i thod pa 'og tu gzhag / mngal khrag la sogs khrag sna tshogs //
NG0201:4305: dug dang snga sngo dkar gsum blug / rabs chad thod pas steng nas dgab //
NG0201:4306: gru gsum nang du gzhag par bya //
NG0201:4307: bsnyen pa bya ba'i thabs dag la //
NG0201:4308: lha bsnyen sum stong byas nas ni //
NG0201:4309: tshe bzhi bco lnga brgyad dus la //
NG0201:4310: gza' chen nyid kyi snying po bzlas //
NG0201:4311: stong rdzogs thun la nyung gis brab /
NG0201:4312: om bya sha me ke du ru ma shi ri kha ra dz+wa la a ka ta swa ha /
NG0201:4313: stong rdzogs thun khrag dag la bstim //
NG0201:4314: om dza pa ti ra hu ma ha kro d+ha sha ra na hum phat //
NG0201:4315: sngags la stong ngam khri ru bzlas //
NG0201:4316: bzlas pa rdzogs nas nyung gis brab //
NG0201:4317: nyi shu dgu'am tshes gcig la //
NG0201:4318: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas sa gtsang sba //
NG0201:4319: thun gcig gnas su rten tu bca' //
NG0201:4320: mis ma 'phrigs par gsang sngags bzlas //
NG0201:4321: om kro d+hi tra lo glo bur skyi 'dang phob //
NG0201:4322: trag rak+sha snying kha rag b+h+yo /
NG0201:4323: khrag ma mu sha ma b+h+yo /
NG0201:4330: rkyang rje rkyang mo tsu ru tsu ru hum phat /
NG0201:4331: de nas zor sngags mdzub bstan la //
NG0201:4332: yul gyi phyogs su bzlas pa bya //
NG0201:4333: ri bo'i rtser song thab zor 'bad //
NG0201:4334: chu skyes zla ba tshes bzhi nas //
NG0201:4335: nyi shu dgu mthar bsnyen rdzogs nas //
NG0201:4336: chu 'khyus zla ba kun tu dbab /
NG0201:4337: de ltar las rnams byas gyur na //
NG0201:4339: skyi 'dang ri rnams nyil bar byed //
NG0201:4340: 'jam dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:4341: chu 'khyags khrag tu dbab pa'i zla gsang nang bsgrub
NG0201:4342: kyi skabs te zhe gcig pa'o // // de nas
NG0201:4343: yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen pos 'di skad
NG0201:4344: ces gsol to // 'gal ba cham la dbab slad du //
NG0201:4345: khyab 'jug gza' yi gsang bsgrub gsungs //
NG0201:4346: sgra gcan chen po nyi zla'i gnyen //
NG0201:4347: drag po chen po ra hu la /
NG0201:4348: khrag tu dbab pa'i las 'di yin //
NG0201:4349: dur khrod la sogs gnas dag tu //
NG0201:4350: man+dal chag chag thig gdab bri //
NG0201:4351: dbus su gru gsum brtsegs ma bri //
NG0201:4352: mu khyud zlum po thod phreng can //
NG0201:4353: sgo bzhi rigs dang mthun par bri //
NG0201:4354: sprul sngon dag gi shun pa la //
NG0201:4355: rdzas kyi phud blugs ming rus gzhug / 'khyil pa'i
NG0201:4356: tshul gyis ga 'ur gzhag / gru gsum dbus su
NG0201:4357: bzhag la bsgrub // dkar thab dmar thab sngo thab gsum //
NG0201:4358: gru gsum rgyab ma dag la gzhag / sha rul khrag rul btsos dang rjen //
NG0201:4359: ra mchen sgrub sman gu gul nag / la phug til sgog pha ltar ba lus kyang mos //
NG0201:4360: snel gri'i thod par blugs la gzhag / dkar gsum klu sman mngar gsum dang *//
NG0201:4361: gu gul dkar po 'bras chen rnams //
NG0201:4362: ma ltar mos pas 'khar gzhong blugs //
NG0201:4363: mthun rdzas bsdus la thod par gzhag / tsa ra rog po'i rwa la ni //
NG0201:4364: sngags bris steng du ming byang gdags //
NG0201:4367: thun rdzas thod phreng steng du gzhag / rang nyid gshin rje gshed po ste //
NG0201:4368: yi dam bcas pa rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:4369: srog snying 'di ni nus thang brjod //
NG0201:4370: om bi sha la du ru+u ma shi kha dz+wa la a ta swa ha /
NG0201:4371: stong rdzogs thun la mchod pa bya //
NG0201:4373: 'jigs byed chen po ra hu la /
NG0201:4374: sku mdog dud kha mig gis khengs //
NG0201:4375: gshin rje gshed po'i zhabs drung du //
NG0201:4376: rgyal ba'i bstan bsrung khas blangs pa //
NG0201:4378: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di longs la //
NG0201:4379: dam nyams srog rtsa gcad pa dang *//
NG0201:4380: yul du lo nad ser ba phob /
NG0201:4381: hab ba sha mi ki du ru ma shi ki dz+wa la ti a tsi ti swa ha /
NG0201:4382: dus tshod brgyad la gtor ma sbyin //
NG0201:4383: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i mtshan ma rnams //
NG0201:4384: gzhung mthun nyams su lon pa dang *//
NG0201:4385: drag po thun gyi rdzas kyang blang *//
NG0201:4386: ga bu'i nang du sngags 'dis brab //
NG0201:4387: om mu ka ye ka pa ye a pa ye hrihsh+t+r-ihbi krin te yul 'di'i lo thog la /
NG0201:4388: tsa pa tri ra hu la ma ha kro d+ha ka pa ta /
NG0201:4389: shar shar ro shal te hum phat /
NG0201:4390: thig nig gcig med gnyis trag / brgyad bcad dud phrom gnam mthongs phye //
NG0201:4393: rkyang rje rkyang mo tsu ru hum phat /
NG0201:4394: stong ngam khri thon rdzas kyis brab //
NG0201:4395: de nas lha srin sprul pa brgyad //
NG0201:4396: sngags kyis gong gi mchan du brab /
NG0201:4399: de ni ma mo'i drag sngags so //
NG0201:4400: om a sa le ma b+h+yo /
NG0201:4401: ru lu ru lu ma ma trag rak+sha hril hril shar b+h+yo //
NG0201:4402: dgra bla'i rgyal mo'i drag sngags so //
NG0201:4403: om pa sha mi ki ra hu la hum /
NG0201:4405: de ni bdud kyi drag sngags so //
NG0201:4406: om ser khrag la mu sha gtub swa ha /
NG0201:4407: de ni srin po'i drag sngags so //
NG0201:4408: om ram tram thum shag ril ram shar b+h+yo /
NG0201:4409: de ni mu'i drag sngags so //
NG0201:4410: om ya ma ra dza ram hri la shar ram ram /
NG0201:4411: de ni gshin rje'i drag sngags so //
NG0201:4412: om na ga hril sen shag sad dun sa ma ya hril b+h+yo /
NG0201:4413: de ni klu btsan gyi drag sngags so //
NG0201:4414: ya ma snying ya ma khrag ra hu la hril
NG0201:4415: hril shag shag sen sen ya ya b+h+yo b+h+yo ram
NG0201:4416: ram hril hril / de ni bgegs kyi drag sngags so //
NG0201:4417: zla gcig dus brgyad phyogs nas brdeg / ling+ga bsnur
NG0201:4418: zhing thun rdzas brdeg / gtum chen bstod la gza'
NG0201:4419: mchog rbad // bla phur ling+ga dag la brdeg / tshes grangs thems nas grub rtags 'byung *//
NG0201:4420: rdzas dang thun zor sngags dang ming *//
NG0201:4421: dbus kyi rabs chad thod par blugs //
NG0201:4422: sa gzer yul dbus la sogs su //
NG0201:4423: skya rengs gzer du btab la bzhag / de nas thun gyi zor bya ste //
NG0201:4424: dam rdzas man+dal gong bzhin bya //
NG0201:4425: dam sri yul gyi chu sogs bsags //
NG0201:4426: lha bsnyen bsgrub sngags phyed du ste //
NG0201:4427: phyed ni man chad sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0201:4428: om mu ka ye ka ba ye a ba ye
NG0201:4429: hrihsh+t+r-ihba krin te yul 'di'i lo thog la dud phrom
NG0201:4434: dz+wa la ti ra hu la /
NG0201:4437: shar shar ta phob hum phat /
NG0201:4439: ag ne rag mo ko ra te swa ha /
NG0201:4440: rkyang rjes rkyang mo tsu ru tsu ru hum phat /
NG0201:4441: ho ho phrom mur mur sha ru ru phrom /
NG0201:4442: gong gi thig nig btags nas kyang *//
NG0201:4443: de la sham bu 'di yang gdags //
NG0201:4448: dgra bo'i lo thog snar mo la ma ra la hum phat /
NG0201:4449: snying po sngags kyi bar bar du //
NG0201:4450: mchod cing gtor ma dbul bar bya //
NG0201:4451: ra bsgral thabs kyis thugs dam bskang *//
NG0201:4452: thon nas gnam gzer ri la bya //
NG0201:4453: dkar thab dmar thab sngo thab gsum //
NG0201:4454: gcig tu dril la bzhi ru bya //
NG0201:4455: dmar ring zor ni phyogs su 'phangs //
NG0201:4456: gong gi sngags bzlas mdzub ris bya //
NG0201:4458: yang na chu bskyes rdzogs pa la //
NG0201:4459: khyab 'jug gtor ma rtag tu btang *//
NG0201:4460: bla phur btab la gsad las bya //
NG0201:4461: bar bar lha lnga dbye bar bya //
NG0201:4462: de ltar byas na rab 'bring gi / gnam lcags lce dang dmu rdo dang *//
NG0201:4463: chu 'khyags khrag tu dbab par bya //
NG0201:4464: de la 'di yi las ni dus gang yang rung bar yang */
NG0201:4465: khrag dang gu gul dang lcags zangs kyi phye ma
NG0201:4466: rnams la bsngags la yul gang yang rung ba de'i
NG0201:4467: lha rten nam chu mig tu sbas na /
NG0201:4468: yul de rlung gis khyer te 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
NG0201:4469: yang rdzas de rnams la bzlas te ri lu byas nas dgra'i khang thog tu bsgyur na //
NG0201:4471: yang de rnams la brjod nas chu mig kha byang
NG0201:4472: du bltas par sbas nas gang ltar drangs pas shwa
NG0201:4473: ser 'ong ngo *// srin rdo dang 'khar ba chag
NG0201:4474: pa la bzlas nas khyab 'jug rgyu ba'i dus su
NG0201:4475: brag kha byang du bltas par sbas na /
NG0201:4478: 'brug gi rus pa dang chu srin gyi sder mo
NG0201:4479: la bzlas nas 'og tu sbas nas phyogs su gtor
NG0201:4480: na / ser ba drag tu 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
NG0201:4482: khyi nag po'i mche ba la sngags nas dgra phyogs su gtor na skrang nad du 'gyur /
NG0201:4483: de la sogs te las thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NG0201:4484: ser ba bzlog pa dang shwa bzlog pa yang de dang 'dra ste //
NG0201:4485: nyung dkar la sngags nas gtor na bzlog par 'gyur //
NG0201:4486: mang ga ya ti la ma ga ti'i bye ma
NG0201:4487: la yang brjod nas gtor na thog bzlog par 'gyur
NG0201:4488: ro // gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:4489: chu 'khyags drag tu dbab pa gza'i drag sngags gsang bsgrub kyi skabs te bzhi bcu zhe gnyis pa'o ///
NG0201:4490: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen po gshin rje gshed pos /
NG0201:4491: 'jig rten khams su thog dbab pa'i phyir lha dbang
NG0201:4492: phyug chen po phyi ltar bsgrub pa 'di gsungs so
NG0201:4493: // lhor bltas brag chen seng ge mchongs pa 'dra //
NG0201:4494: yang na a ya yang dmar lo ma 'dra ba'am //
NG0201:4495: dur khrod la sogs dgon pa'i gnas dag tu //
NG0201:4498: 'phags pa la sogs mchod cing gtor ma gtong *//
NG0201:4499: dra phying gtsang ma mda' gang gru bzhi la //
NG0201:4500: mtshal lam ldong ros dag gis thig btab ste //
NG0201:4501: le'u tshe dgu pa dag gi tshad du bya //
NG0201:4502: dbus su ga pur dag gi chus bkrus la //
NG0201:4503: dar ram ras sam dkar la 'jam pa la //
NG0201:4504: lha chen dbang phyug dag gis gzugs bris te //
NG0201:4505: smyug ma gtsang ma dag la dgod par bya //
NG0201:4506: steng nas dmar po dar gyi gdugs kyis dgab //
NG0201:4507: de yi mtshams bzhir ljang gu'i 'phan bzhi gzug / phyogs bzhi'i le'u tshe bzhi po dag la yang *//
NG0201:4508: lha yi blon po bzhi yi gzugs bris dgod //
NG0201:4509: shar du dri za'i lha nyid dgod par bya //
NG0201:4510: lho ru gshin rje nub tu klu gdon lha //
NG0201:4511: byang du gnod sbyin lha ste bzhi po dgod //
NG0201:4512: de yi phyi rim me tog sna tshogs bskor //
NG0201:4513: mchod pa lnga dang gtor ma gcig / nang du rta tshil khrag dang snying yang stsal //
NG0201:4514: snying gi srog rtsar dmigs pa'i ming rus bri //
NG0201:4515: khre'u cu tse dag la dgra gzugs bya //
NG0201:4516: snying gar thig le'i dkyil du ming rus gzug / ske nas sngon dmar skud pas gdags byas te //
NG0201:4517: lag pa g.yas kyi srin lag rtse la dgal //
NG0201:4518: chas gos ljang nag mgo la thod nag bcing *//
NG0201:4519: dur khrod ras sam bram ze'i pags pa la //
NG0201:4520: ldong ros chu rtsas kha dog ser por bsgyur //
NG0201:4521: dug dang khrag gis 'khor la rtsibs brgyad bri //
NG0201:4522: 'khor lo'i rtsibs la gshin rje'i snying po bri //
NG0201:4523: dbus kyi lte bar lha chen snying po dgod //
NG0201:4524: phyi rim thog gi dbab sngags dag gis bskor //
NG0201:4525: 'khor lo mnga' gsol dbang bskur smon lam gdab //
NG0201:4526: bram ze la sogs mdze can thod par gzhug / de yi nang du gser dang lcags zangs dang *//
NG0201:4527: dngul dang snying sna khrag sna mang blugs te //
NG0201:4528: le'u tse'i dbus su man 'ji'i kha la gzhag / ting 'dzin rnam gsum rim gyis tshul bzhin bskyed //
NG0201:4529: dbang chen rim brtsegs steng du b+h+rum gcig bsam //
NG0201:4530: b+h+rum las 'bar ba'i lha yi gzhal med khang *//
NG0201:4531: phyi dang nang nas kun tu gsal bar bskyed //
NG0201:4532: dbus su ma he bam chen bsnol ba la //
NG0201:4533: nyi zla 'khor lo rab tu 'bar ba'i steng *//
NG0201:4534: ya las 'jam dpal gshed po 'bar ba'i sku //
NG0201:4535: zhal drug phyag kyang bcu gnyis gsal bar bskyed //
NG0201:4536: de yi 'khor na lha yi tshogs gnas te //
NG0201:4537: ma ha de ba hum zhes brjod pa yis //
NG0201:4538: dbus su lha chen ma ha de ba yang *//
NG0201:4539: sku mdog nag po spyan gsum mche ba can //
NG0201:4540: rtse gsum 'bar ba khyung gi rgyal mtshan g.yas //
NG0201:4541: zhags pa be con rdo rje g.yon pa na //
NG0201:4542: smin mtshams glog 'gyu bskal pa'i thog 'bebs bsgom //
NG0201:4543: 'khor gyi lha yang rta zhon thog 'bebs pa'o //
NG0201:4544: de bzhin ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bsgoms la //
NG0201:4545: gshin rje gshed pos lus bsrung dbang du bsdu //
NG0201:4547: las rnams rim gyis bgrod pa'i yang rtse nas //
NG0201:4550: ma ha de ba lha chen dbang phyug gtso //
NG0201:4551: bstan pa bshigs pa'i dgra rnams bsgral ba dang *//
NG0201:4552: sangs rgyas bstan bsrung dkon mchog bstod pa'i phyir //
NG0201:4553: 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NG0201:4554: om pra ma na rag sha e h+ye he dzahhum bam hoh /
NG0201:4555: dga' zhing gus pa'i thal sbyar pus btsugs nas //
NG0201:4556: lha mchog khyed kyi yon tan rab brjod cing *//
NG0201:4557: tsam pa ka dang pad+mas rab gtor nas //
NG0201:4558: deng 'dir bstod de khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0201:4559: khyod kyi thugs ni nam mkha'i dkyil 'dra zhing *//
NG0201:4560: 'od zer cha las 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NG0201:4561: thogs med mkha' lding ngang pa'i gdan steng su //
NG0201:4562: brtan par bzhugs nas bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NG0201:4563: 'khor gyi lha chen mi bzad thog 'bebs bzhi //
NG0201:4564: shugs kyi thogs med ta mchog gdan la bzhugs //
NG0201:4565: ma ha de wa pra ma na tsa ra zhi sa ma ya tish+tha ldan //
NG0201:4566: lha yul gtsang ma dag la rab bshams te //
NG0201:4567: bram ze mtshan ldan chags pas rab tu mchod //
NG0201:4568: 'bras dang ku shar bcas pa'i yon chab dang *//
NG0201:4569: ga pur gur gum gla rtsi ce pog sogs //
NG0201:4570: til mar bsung can rab gsal mar me'i mchog / du ru ka la sogs pa de yi chu //
NG0201:4571: lags na mar dang bcas pa'i bu ram bshos //
NG0201:4572: dung dang bye ru zangs dang kra shel dang *//
NG0201:4573: rnga ting rdza lnga mun dza ti mi li //
NG0201:4574: cha lang pi wang tam bu rgyud gcig pa /
NG0201:4575: glu gar rtsed 'jo rol mo dag la sogs //
NG0201:4576: bde ba'i yo byad thams cad ma lus kun //
NG0201:4577: mchod par 'bul lo thugs rjes bzhes su gsol //
NG0201:4578: om sarba pu dza push+pe d+hu pe a lo ke gan d+he ba lim pu dza hoh /
NG0201:4579: sku mdog nag po spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs //
NG0201:4580: drang srong cha lugs pad+ma'i phreng bas brgyan //
NG0201:4581: zhal bzhi gling bzhi yongs la khyab par gzigs //
NG0201:4582: snyan pa'i dril sgra gsung gi gdangs skad can //
NG0201:4583: dbang phyug chen po khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0201:4584: 'khor gyi lha yi blon po bzhi //
NG0201:4585: rta la zhon nas ral gri bskor //
NG0201:4586: thog ser 'bebs pa'i las la brtson //
NG0201:4587: khyod la bdag cag bstod phyag 'tshal //
NG0201:4588: sngags 'dis lhan rnams rab tu bsnyen //
NG0201:4589: om ma ha de wa ti dza ti dza lam
NG0201:4590: pra ma na pra ma na rak+sha kang kang la
NG0201:4591: yang hum / de ba ra tsa dza ma ha
NG0201:4592: ni dgra bo che ge mo ni thum thum rbad
NG0201:4593: yang hum / // shag len san sen yang sa na dzahdzahhum hum /
NG0201:4594: de skad bstod la bsnyen pa bgyi //
NG0201:4595: rang gis ma nyes dbang yang gzug / nyes byas bris sku'i mdun du bshags //
NG0201:4597: gshed po bstod la lha rnams bskul //
NG0201:4598: g.yas nas bskor zhing thugs dam bskul //
NG0201:4599: 'dod khams nyi shu'i yang rtse nas //
NG0201:4600: gzugs khams lha yi dga' tshal nas //
NG0201:4601: phau brang bde ba'i gzhal yas nas //
NG0201:4602: chos kyi rgyal mtshan dbang bskur ba'i //
NG0201:4603: lha chen dbang phyug chen po ni //
NG0201:4604: sku ni dmar ser 'bar ba la //
NG0201:4607: g.yas kyis pad+ma skyon dang bral //
NG0201:4608: tha mas bgrang phreng rig sngags spel //
NG0201:4610: tha ma blug snod dgra bgegs sbyong *//
NG0201:4611: dad pas bsam par yud kyis phyin //
NG0201:4612: pad+ma ser pos brgyan byas nas //
NG0201:4613: ras kyi kha tshar mgul rgyan can //
NG0201:4614: thugs dam drag tu bskul byas nas //
NG0201:4615: log pa'i dgra bgegs 'joms pa'i tshe //
NG0201:4616: sku ni sngo nag chen po la //
NG0201:4617: zhal gyi mche ba gdangs pa yis //
NG0201:4618: dgra bo bdun rgyud rtsad nas gcod //
NG0201:4620: thal mo brdab pas thog chen 'bebs //
NG0201:4621: mdzub mo bskul bas gling bzhi 'khrug / ljags brkyang srid pa g.yo bar mdzad //
NG0201:4622: dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra 'di //
NG0201:4623: thog chen 'bar bas lnga phung shig / tshe srog chod la bdun rgyud chod //
NG0201:4624: 'khor gyi blon bzhi las la bskul //
NG0201:4625: bar snang thog chen 'brul du chug / dbang po rnam lnga kha long kha //
NG0201:4626: bu smad 'khor g.yog nor phyugs la //
NG0201:4627: gser thog lcags thog tsa la la //
NG0201:4629: zangs thog 'khar thog rams se ram //
NG0201:4630: me 'od glog dmar khyugs se khyug / 'khor rnams shugs chen rta zhon cing *//
NG0201:4631: ral gri me 'od klad la bskor //
NG0201:4632: ki kang gshed bzhi'i las la 'gyed //
NG0201:4634: thog chen sna tshogs skar ltar 'khrugs //
NG0201:4635: nyams pa'i dgra la thog mda' ya //
NG0201:4636: skad cig tsam la phung bar gyis //
NG0201:4637: zhes rta snying bstab cing rak+ta sbreng *//
NG0201:4638: rtags su 'brug dang ser ba dang *//
NG0201:4639: glog dang thog dang shwa bud 'ong *//
NG0201:4640: grub pa'i rtags byung thog gta' gzhug / mkhar rmang lha rten chu mig gam //
NG0201:4642: lhag par dgra yi gro ga'am //
NG0201:4643: nyal ba'i sngas sam stan 'og tu //
NG0201:4644: 'khor lo bcas pa'i thod pa sba //
NG0201:4645: drag sngags 'di bzlas thod par gsib //
NG0201:4646: om sa ma dur bu rak+sha pra ma na /
NG0201:4647: ma ha de wa dgra yi yul khams su //
NG0201:4648: ro kha du kha ba hum phra ba swa ha /
NG0201:4649: zhes pa ni thod pa'i nang du bzlas //
NG0201:4650: gtor ma gtang zhing smon lam gdab //
NG0201:4651: bris sku dag la rten bcas la //
NG0201:4652: dra phying man+dal dag la dril //
NG0201:4653: rtag tu lha rnams mchod gyur na //
NG0201:4655: gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:4656: 'jig rten du thog dbab pa lha'i zla gsang skabs
NG0201:4657: te zhe gsum pa'o // // de nas yang bcom
NG0201:4658: ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen po gshin rje gshed pos
NG0201:4659: 'gal byed cham la dbab pa'i slad du //
NG0201:4660: thog 'bebs lha yi nang bsgrub gsungs //
NG0201:4661: srid par ma srid mgar gyis ma brdungs mtshon //
NG0201:4662: ye srid byang chub sems kyi dpal ngar can //
NG0201:4663: rlung gis ma blud gshags pa'i ngar //
NG0201:4664: ye blud chen po'i mtshon dpal ngar can des //
NG0201:4665: 'byung ba gzhan gyis mi brdzi mi tshugs shing *//
NG0201:4666: nyid kyis gang la thogs chag med par @#//
NG0201:4668: de nyid bsgrub phyir dur khrod la sogs su //
NG0201:4670: dbus su gru gsum e brtsigs te //
NG0201:4671: 'khor lo bzhi dang rol mtsho bdun //
NG0201:4672: gser ri'i dbus su ya man+ta ka ste //
NG0201:4673: steng du lha chen dbang phyug yab yum dgod par bya //
NG0201:4674: 'khor lo bzhi la lha yi blon po bzhi //
NG0201:4675: khrag zhag mar khu chang dang sbrang rtsi 'o ma dang *//
NG0201:4676: rgya tsho'i chu la sogs pa'i mtsho bdun no //
NG0201:4677: lha chen lnga la phur pa lnga dgod de //
NG0201:4678: dngul gyi phur pa sor brgyad shar du dgod //
NG0201:4679: dri za lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4680: gser gyi phur pa lho yi rtsibs la dgod //
NG0201:4681: gshin rje lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4682: zangs kyi phur pa nub kyi rtsibs la dgod //
NG0201:4683: klu dbang lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4684: lcags kyi phur pa byang gi rtsibs la dgod //
NG0201:4685: gnod sbyin lha yi blon por mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4686: mkhar ba'i phur pa dbus kyi e la 'god //
NG0201:4687: dbang phyug chen po ma ha de bar mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4688: gro ga shing shur ras sam dar dkar la //
NG0201:4689: lha rnams rang rang rtsa ba'i snying po dang *//
NG0201:4690: dbab pa'i sngags dang dmigs pa'i yul ming bri //
NG0201:4691: sngon dmar skud pas phur pa'i mgul du gdags //
NG0201:4692: rabs chad nag po'i thod pa kha sbyar la //
NG0201:4693: thod pa'i phyi nang med par khrag gis byug / steng gi thod pa yab tu mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4694: 'og gi thod pa yum du mnga' yang gsol //
NG0201:4695: thod pa steng mar yab kyi sku yang bri //
NG0201:4696: thod pa 'og mar yum gyi sku yang bri //
NG0201:4697: thod pa'i rtsibs rim dmigs pa'i ming rus bri //
NG0201:4698: dpral bar rus bri kha ru ming yang bri //
NG0201:4699: snying gar nr-i bri 'doms su bla dgas bri //
NG0201:4700: de yi tha mar lto sbyar dza yis bskor //
NG0201:4701: gro ga shing shun zhing gi pags pa la //
NG0201:4702: dgra bo'i gzugs bris dbang phyug yum la glan //
NG0201:4703: 'khar ba'i phur pa thod pa'i nang du gzhag / gro ga shog shog shing gi lo ma la //
NG0201:4704: lha chen tshogs bdag dbang phyug chen po khyod //
NG0201:4705: khyed kyi btsun mo ma ra ya 'dis sbyar //
NG0201:4706: 'khor gyi lha rnams myur du skul mdzod la //
NG0201:4707: 'di la drag po'i thog chen phob ces bri //
NG0201:4708: phur pa de yi mgul du gdags par bya'o //
NG0201:4709: thod pa'i nang du dme khrag skam po dang *//
NG0201:4710: gser phye zangs phye lcags phye 'khar phye dang *//
NG0201:4711: dngul dang thog lcags thog grir shi ba yi //
NG0201:4712: snying dang rus pa sha yang stsal //
NG0201:4713: thod pa kha sbyar mi yi rgyu mas bcings //
NG0201:4714: sgyed gsum kha la gru gsum steng du bzhag / chu skyes me tog sna tshogs dang *//
NG0201:4715: rin chen sna lnga sman rnams dang *//
NG0201:4716: 'dod pa'i longs spyod zas rnams dang *//
NG0201:4717: rgun chang sbrang dang 'bras chang dang *//
NG0201:4718: 'bru chang dang ni a su sha //
NG0201:4719: de dag mchod pa'i rdzas su dgram //
NG0201:4720: sna tshogs snying dang khrag tu sbyar //
NG0201:4721: bu ram 'bras kyi gtor ma bzhi //
NG0201:4722: lha yi blon po bzhi la dgod //
NG0201:4725: gzugs ming byas pa mdun du bzhag / sngags kyis brab cing gsad las bya //
NG0201:4726: ting 'dzin gzhal yas gdan dang bcas pa bskyed //
NG0201:4727: ya man+ta ka gsal bar bsgom //
NG0201:4728: gdan du yi dwags gding bar bya //
NG0201:4729: dbang phyug chen po gsal bsgoms te //
NG0201:4730: 'khor gyi lha bzhis bskor bar bsam //
NG0201:4731: om ma ha de ba ka la hum /
NG0201:4732: zhes brjod dbang phyug chen po yang *//
NG0201:4733: nag po chen po mche ba rab tu gtsigs //
NG0201:4734: phyag mtshan rtse gsum khyung gi rgyal mtshan g.yas //
NG0201:4735: zhags pas 'dren tshul be con rdeg tshul g.yon //
NG0201:4736: chibs su 'brug rta sngon po chibs //
NG0201:4737: gser gyi ral gri 'bar ba klad la bskor //
NG0201:4738: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i shang lang glo la btags //
NG0201:4739: de 'dra rab tu gsal bsgom bya //
NG0201:4740: shar phyogs lha yi phyag na dngul gyi gzhu bdungs shing *//
NG0201:4741: dngul gyi mda' ltong dngul gyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0201:4742: 'brug rta zhon nas ki kang 'phral la 'jug / dngul gyi thog 'bebs ser ba'i skyi 'dang gtong *//
NG0201:4743: lho nas gser gyi thog chen gong bzhin 'bebs //
NG0201:4744: nub nas zangs thog byang nas lcags thog 'bebs //
NG0201:4745: de 'dra gang la bsgoms la yengs par mi bya'o //
NG0201:4747: rnam snang mdzad nyid mi g.yo gtsug tor brtan //
NG0201:4748: byang chub chen po mchog gi phyag rgya ni //
NG0201:4749: bdud 'dul chen po'i sku ru sprul pa'i rgya //
NG0201:4750: byang shar mtshams nas shin tu sku bde bstan //
NG0201:4751: me lce bar snang sprin gtibs dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0201:4752: sku stod sngo nag mi bzad 'bar ba'i 'od phung can //
NG0201:4753: shin tu khro brjid dbang phyug gtum bag che //
NG0201:4754: thugs rje sprin ltar gtibs shing nam mkha' gang bar khyab //
NG0201:4755: gzir gnon stabs kyis dregs pa gzir zhing gnon //
NG0201:4756: bdud po nag po spyan gsum mche ba can //
NG0201:4757: bstan pa 'jig pa'i srog la spyan 'dren na //
NG0201:4758: dbang phyug lha chen 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NG0201:4759: dbang phyug chen po gnas nas bskyod tsa na //
NG0201:4760: rtse gsum 'bar ba khyung gi rgyal mtshan phyar te gshegs //
NG0201:4761: zhags pas 'dren cing be con snying la brdeg / nag po spyan gsum sdang mig bzlog pa'i bdud //
NG0201:4762: dbu skra 'bar ba phrog gzer ral pa can //
NG0201:4763: sku lus mon pa spyan gsum ser ba 'dril //
NG0201:4764: rno dpal mche ba zla tshes gyen du 'khyil //
NG0201:4765: spyan mig bzlog pas skyi 'dang rma 'dang 'bebs //
NG0201:4766: shangs nas rlung ni 'thor 'bud bu yug 'khrugs //
NG0201:4767: mdung dang gri rkang sku yi rten du bcas //
NG0201:4768: spyan mig mi mthun las kyi zla ba 'dril ba ltar //
NG0201:4769: 'od zer me ltar 'bar zhing gshegs su gsol //
NG0201:4770: e h+ye he ma ha ka la ma ha ka
NG0201:4771: la tri dza ka ru ni ka dr-i sh+ya hoh
NG0201:4775: lha chen dbang phyug 'khor ba'i g.yul bzlog pa //
NG0201:4776: sprul pa'i rlabs chen lha yi dmag dpung sdud //
NG0201:4777: dbang phyug legs ldan nag po'i 'khor gyis bskor //
NG0201:4778: dbang phyug lha chen sku la @#//
NG0201:4780: dbang phyug bsod nams gzi byin 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0201:4781: ston pas lung bstan 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0201:4782: dbang phyug nyi zla'i 'od ltar zhal gsal zhing *//
NG0201:4783: ma rig sgrib pa ma lus sel mdzad pa'i //
NG0201:4784: 'khor bcas lha yi tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0201:4785: me tog phreng la sogs pa dang *//
NG0201:4786: rin chen dbyig dang sgog btsod dang *//
NG0201:4787: la phug la sogs kun dang ni //
NG0201:4788: 'bras bu yid bzhin sna tshogs zas //
NG0201:4789: phyogs bcu chu skyes dang ni longs spyod rgyan //
NG0201:4790: ris su ma chad mchod pa'i longs spyod dbul //
NG0201:4791: dkyil 'khor mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0201:4792: zhal zas bdud rtsi dza gad sman gyis mchod //
NG0201:4793: e h+ye hi ma ha ka ru ni pa ti ma ha rak+sha du pa kha kha kha hi /
NG0201:4795: ma ha pe ta li kha kha kha hi hum /
NG0201:4796: dbang phyug chen po 'khor bcas la //
NG0201:4797: mchod sprin la sogs sna tshogs dang *//
NG0201:4798: rdzas dang yo byad dpag mi lang *//
NG0201:4799: bla med dang bas mchod 'bul bstod //
NG0201:4801: gdug pa ril mid mdzad pa'i khro gnyer can /
NG0201:4802: dug gsum rtsad gcod mche ba gtsigs pa po //
NG0201:4803: ye shes spyan gsum nyi zla'i ga'u la //
NG0201:4804: ston pa'i bka' brgyud bla med lung bstan dpal //
NG0201:4805: dam tshig chos kyi 'khor lo rnam snang mdzad //
NG0201:4806: bla re cod pan brjid pas bcings pa na //
NG0201:4807: nges par ston pa bcu yi bdag po 'phags //
NG0201:4808: rtag tu dur khrod 'bar ba'i gnas na bzhugs //
NG0201:4809: dur khrod gnas na ma mo'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NG0201:4810: nad gtong shri'i tshogs rnams kun mchod nas //
NG0201:4811: bstan pa bshigs pa'i mdangs 'phrog thal ba'i rdul du
NG0201:4812: rlog / stobs chen glang po'i pags pa gos su
NG0201:4813: gyon // lha klu gnyan gyi grong khyer thams cad du //
NG0201:4814: lha chen 'dud dpung che btsan gsum pa nas //
NG0201:4815: log 'dren dgra bgegs gzir gdul gnon pa'o //
NG0201:4816: dpa' bo chen po stag gi pags pas mtshan //
NG0201:4817: 'khor du lha yi blon po bzhi yis bskor //
NG0201:4818: phyogs rnams phyogs cha kun tu rnam grangs la //
NG0201:4819: smon lam khyad par mang po'i mthus sbyangs la //
NG0201:4820: sgyu ma lta bur rnam par thar pas rol //
NG0201:4821: phan mdzad dmag dpon khyod la yang *//
NG0201:4822: sdug bsngal tsha bas gdungs pa'i sems can la //
NG0201:4823: drag po'i thog chen lu gu rgyud du 'bebs //
NG0201:4824: lha chen dbang phyug khyod la bdag 'dud skyabs su mchi //
NG0201:4825: sngags 'dis lha rnams srog kyang bzung *//
NG0201:4826: om ma ha de ba ka la ka sti dza
NG0201:4827: re sde ri i na hri se ban dza na
NG0201:4828: ga ru ru te be kan phu pe he se
NG0201:4829: rbe da de bu pe na de ba te na
NG0201:4830: ma ra ya // khri tsho re zhing bskul bskyed bstod //
NG0201:4831: 'od dang sgra dang dri zhim dang *//
NG0201:4832: 'brug dang glog dang thog dang shwa //

NG0201:5221: snyan g.yas sbrul gyi gdengs ka yi //

NG0201:5256: rna ltag me tog dar nag cod pan 'phur //
NG0201:5257: khrag gi chang gis ra ro spyan gsum dmar //
NG0201:5258: mi ro rengs ba khar bcug mche ba bzhi //
NG0201:5259: rnam par gtsigs nas shin tu khrag la dgyes //

NG0201:5261: gdug pa brtul nas tshangs pa'i sgra sgrogs ma //

NG0201:5264: phyag bzhi g.yas kyi dang po ral gri bsnams //
NG0201:5265: 'og ma thod pa b+han+da dmar bskyil 'dzin //
