NG0201:5523: skabs su ging chen bco brgyad bskul //
NG0201:5524: nyi ma bzhi pa'i las kyang bya //
NG0201:5525: om ma ha ra dza thun b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0201:5528: dgra bo'i snying shag / tshal pa dum /
NG0201:5530: rlag dza ru thibs chug dgra bo'i khrag la 'jib /
NG0201:5531: b+hi ba b+hi ba dun dza /
NG0201:5534: khrag ta khrag la thun b+h+yo thun b+h+yo mugs /
NG0201:5535: nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe la /
NG0201:5536: drag tu sngags la brdeg par bya //
NG0201:5537: dkar po gcig gis thugs dam bskang *//
NG0201:5540: nyi zla 'char dang lder so dang *//
NG0201:5541: 'bag tu rmis na tha mar bshad //
NG0201:5542: btsad po zhang blon dge bshes sam //
NG0201:5543: dmag dpon rmis na 'bring du bshad //
NG0201:5544: rgyal po nyid mthong nyams su ston //
NG0201:5545: de ltar byung na rab tu bshad //
NG0201:5546: bskang bshags bya zhing dngos grub blang *//
NG0201:5547: dam tshig bsre zhing phrin las bcol //
NG0201:5548: de nas 'khor lo thod par bca' //
NG0201:5549: shar du kha bltas chu mig ngor //
NG0201:5550: rgyal rigs sbyor ba byas gyur na //
NG0201:5553: mkhar rmang gnan na gnam lcags 'bab //
NG0201:5554: 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:5555: rgyal po phyi ltar sgrub pa smyo 'bog gi skabs
NG0201:5556: te zhe dgu pa'o // // de nas yang bcom
NG0201:5557: ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos rgyal po nang du
NG0201:5558: bsgrubs te smyo 'bog gtong ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:5559: thog mar bla ma mnyes byas shing *//
NG0201:5560: sgrib pa sbyong zhing dam tshig bsrung *//
NG0201:5561: mtshan ldan dgon pa'i gnas nyid du //
NG0201:5562: lta ba rgya bskyed 'jam dpal bsnyen //
NG0201:5563: bla ma mnyes pa'i rim gro bya //
NG0201:5564: dkyil 'khor brtsig dang chag chag gdab //
NG0201:5565: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba ni //
NG0201:5566: thig bzhi btab la le'u tshe dgu //
NG0201:5567: dbus kyi le'u tshe dkar po la //
NG0201:5568: shar ser lho sngo nub dmar byang ni ljang *//
NG0201:5569: mtshams bzhi smug nag sgo dang bcas //
NG0201:5570: dbus su gru gsum re re bri //
NG0201:5572: rgya shug dkar po'i phur pa dgu / srog bdag dgu ru mnga' gsol la //
NG0201:5573: dar dkar srog snying bris te gdags //
NG0201:5574: 'di skad brjod la dgod par bya'o //
NG0201:5576: dbus phyogs shel re shel gyi khang pa nas //
NG0201:5577: khams gsum srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5578: srog bdag nag po ral pa can //
NG0201:5579: bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NG0201:5580: bsam pa bsgrub phyir gshegs nas kyang *//
NG0201:5581: pho brang dbus kyi le'u tshe la //
NG0201:5582: dgra bgegs bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NG0201:5583: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0201:5584: ging ka ra sa ma ya tish+tha lhan //
NG0201:5586: rgyal rigs srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5587: srog bdag rgyal po khu le shod //
NG0201:5588: dkyil 'khor shar gyi le'u tshe la //
NG0201:5589: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0201:5590: bram ze'i srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5591: rgyal po chen po ag ge yang *//
NG0201:5592: lho phyogs dkyil 'khor le'u tshe la //
NG0201:5593: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0201:5594: rjes rigs srog la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NG0201:5595: rgyal po chen po ug ge yang *//
NG0201:5596: de bzhin nub kyi phyogs su dgod //
NG0201:5597: dmangs rigs srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5598: rgyal po chen po bram ze yang *//
NG0201:5599: de bzhin byang gi phyogs su dgod //
NG0201:5600: bud med srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5601: rgyal po chen po shang ze yang *//
NG0201:5602: dkyil 'khor shar lho'i le'u tsher dgod //
NG0201:5603: byis pa'i srog la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NG0201:5604: rgyal po chen po da khod kyang *//
NG0201:5607: mi nag srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5608: rgyal po chen po ni khod kyang *//
NG0201:5609: nub byang dkyil 'khor le'u tsher dgod //
NG0201:5610: byol song srog la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0201:5611: rgyal po chen po nyi zla yang *//
NG0201:5612: byang shar dkyil 'khor le'u tsher dgod //
NG0201:5613: de nas mchog gi phur pa bzhi //
NG0201:5614: nyin bzhi'i ging bzhir mnga' gsol la //
NG0201:5615: ris mthun dar gyi cod pan gdags //
NG0201:5616: phrin las bcol phyir sgo bzhir gdab //
NG0201:5617: dar skud gsum dril mtha' ma bskor //
NG0201:5618: bla rgyan logs rgyan ci mang dgram //
NG0201:5619: dar dkar gur phub za 'og gdan yang bting *//
NG0201:5620: de nas dbus kyi srog bdag la //
NG0201:5621: gtsang phye bre gang lha bshos la //
NG0201:5622: ri rab tshul 'dra zhig byas la //
NG0201:5623: dbus su smyug ma tshigs dgu la //
NG0201:5624: mtshal gyi mkhar thabs nya mig bri //
NG0201:5625: rtse la bya rgod rgyal mtshan dang *//
NG0201:5626: dar dkar gdugs gcig steng nas dgab //
NG0201:5627: dngul gyi g.yer kha g.yag rnga phon //
NG0201:5628: lpags bu dkar po'i blud bu gdags //
NG0201:5629: tha ma'i tshigs la ming rus gdags //
NG0201:5630: gzhan yang smyug ma tshigs gsum brgyad //
NG0201:5631: mtshal dang ldong ros sgo sprad la //
NG0201:5632: mkhar thabs bris la rtse kha sprad //
NG0201:5633: lce la dar lce re yang gdags //
NG0201:5634: bar bar ra dkar blud bu dang *//
NG0201:5635: dung dang zangs dang rin po che //
NG0201:5636: byu ru mgron bu sa gser gdags //
NG0201:5637: tha ma'i tshigs la ming rus gdags //
NG0201:5638: lcang ma mtho re ba bzhi la //
NG0201:5639: mtshal lam rams kyis g.yung drung bris //
NG0201:5640: thod rer la lpags ming rus re //
NG0201:5641: de bzhin btags la sgo bzhir gzhag / gzhan yang thud dang nya sha dang *//
NG0201:5642: bu ram gtor ma 'bras chan dang *//
NG0201:5643: za 'og dar dang pags dkar dang *//
NG0201:5644: rin chen bstsal la phyogs bzhir gzhag / gcig ni dbus su gzhag par bya //
NG0201:5645: nya phyis dung phor 'khar gzhong du //
NG0201:5646: gser dang chang phud sbyar ba lnga //
NG0201:5647: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga ru gzhag / gcig tu mtshe dang nyung nag dang *//
NG0201:5648: chang phud gangs chu chu mig chu //
NG0201:5649: de gsum gcig tu bsres la gzhag / drag sngags rgyun du bzlas pa'i phyir //
NG0201:5650: bdag nyid shar bltas sngon du gzhag / gzhan yang spos dang me tog dang *//
NG0201:5651: mar me dri chab rnga gling dang *//
NG0201:5652: mchod pa'i yo byad phyogs bzhir dgram //
NG0201:5653: ra lug dkar po gang yod pa //
NG0201:5654: ra dang ze ba dmar por byug / ske ru dar dkar khug ma ru //
NG0201:5655: mtshe nyung klu sman sna tshogs dang *//
NG0201:5656: dgra yi ming byang bcug la gdags //
NG0201:5657: nub tu dar 'phan dkar po la //
NG0201:5658: 'phan lce ser po btags pa gcig / rgyal po'i gzugs bris mdung la gdags //
NG0201:5659: rtse la snying gcig bkal la gzug / gshin rje gshed por mnga' gsol la //
NG0201:5660: sngags bzlas bstod pa mang du bya //
NG0201:5661: ber gyon thod bcing rnga yang brdung */
NG0201:5662: snyan gsan dbab dang spyan drang dang *//
NG0201:5663: phyag 'tshal bzhugs dang mchod pa dbul //
NG0201:5664: bstod pa dbul zhing smon lam gdab //
NG0201:5666: dam bskang zhing phrin las bcol //
NG0201:5667: srog snying 'di ni rtag tu drangs *//
NG0201:5668: om tri stu ti bya 'gyur ra ka la ma ra ma ra ya swa ha /
NG0201:5669: de ni srog bdag rang gi snying po'o //
NG0201:5670: 'di ni 'khor srog bdag gi snying po'o //
NG0201:5671: om khu le ma ha be ram swa ha /
NG0201:5672: om ag ge ru rta swa ha /
NG0201:5673: om ug ge sha ma le swa ha /
NG0201:5674: om drang zi rta ba swa ha /
NG0201:5675: om shang ze shang ka ra swa ha /
NG0201:5676: om da khod bi si yang swa ha /
NG0201:5677: om ni khod ba ra hi te swa ha /
NG0201:5678: om sur+ya tsan+d+ra ma ta khu le swa ha /
NG0201:5679: de rnams srog gi snying po'o //
NG0201:5680: mi tshig g.yal dang sbrid pa spang *//
NG0201:5681: skya rengs shar nas 'khor rnams bskul //
NG0201:5682: grub pa'i rtags rnams ston par nges //
NG0201:5684: rab la sku ni dngos su ston //
NG0201:5686: tha mar rmi lam ltas su ston //
NG0201:5687: de la dbang bskur dam bsre bya //
NG0201:5688: rbad sngags bgrangs shing phrin las bcol //
NG0201:5689: a+om ma ha pra ma na rak+sha rak+ta tsa ra
NG0201:5690: mun tra ma ha shi de tso ka tsa la
NG0201:5691: bing bing dgra bo ma ra ya hab hab //
NG0201:5692: de ni rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams las la rbad pa'o //
NG0201:5693: de nas rta dkar po'i thod pa'i nang brnag pa'i ming rus bcug la /
NG0201:5694: rta thod za 'og dag gis gril //
NG0201:5695: dam sri smyo ru gzhug pa'i phyir //
NG0201:5696: khrag skam gu gul sbyar ba dang *//
NG0201:5697: mtshe nyung go ro tsa na la //
NG0201:5699: om ma ma ma rang ga thun b+h+yo /
NG0201:5700: ma ha ra dza thun b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0201:5701: ma ha ba b+ha b+ha ma ha de ba ma ha ru tra b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0201:5702: om tro ta ya tro ta ya /
NG0201:5703: tra ta ya tra ta ya /
NG0201:5704: k+shu lha k+shu lha ging ka ra ging ka ra /
NG0201:5705: ging dz+wa la ging dz+wa la /
NG0201:5708: d+ha sha gri ba d+ha sha gri wa /
NG0201:5709: phu tra dkar po b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0201:5710: de ni srog bdag 'khor gyi smyo 'bog tu sngags so //
NG0201:5711: de nas brnag pa'i ming rus la //
NG0201:5712: rang rang rtsa ba'i sngags brjod cing *//
NG0201:5713: phur pa rnams kyis rim pas gdab //
NG0201:5714: gtso bo'i phur pa snying la gdab //
NG0201:5715: khu le shod kyi gsang bar gdab //
NG0201:5716: rgyal po ag ge lag pa g.yas //
NG0201:5717: rgyal po ug ge dpung par gdab //
NG0201:5718: rgyal po drang ze'i lag pa g.yon //
NG0201:5719: shang ze'i rkang pa g.yas su gdab //
NG0201:5720: da khod dpung mgo g.yas su gdab //
NG0201:5721: ni khod dpung mgo g.yon la gdab //
NG0201:5722: nyi zlas rkang pa g.yon la gdab //
NG0201:5723: gsad pa nyi ma bzhi pa ste //
NG0201:5724: nyin bzhi lha yi ging bzhi bya //
NG0201:5725: de nas rta yi thod pa ru //
NG0201:5726: ling+ga'i thed shul mthun rdzas stsal //
NG0201:5727: lha khang rnams la btags gyur na //
NG0201:5728: smyo 'bog khrag skyugs ma ra ya //
NG0201:5729: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:5730: smyo 'bog gi zla gsang las rgyal po nang ltar
NG0201:5731: bsgrub pa'i skabs te lnga bcu pa'o // // de
NG0201:5732: nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos rgyal
NG0201:5733: po gsang bar sgrub pa'i thabs thams cad kyi mchog
NG0201:5735: rnal 'byor yon tan ldan pa des //
NG0201:5736: bla ma mnyes pa rab byas te //
NG0201:5737: mgo ni rma bya bzhin du dgug / dam tshig chen po srog bzhin bsrung *//
NG0201:5739: don ma yin rang don du //
NG0201:5740: dur khrod sa phug dgon par 'gro //
NG0201:5741: phyi bshags sdig sbyangs bsod nams bsag / ma nyes dbang gzugs glud gtor gtang *//
NG0201:5742: dkyil 'khor brtsig la chag chag gdab //
NG0201:5743: thig gdab dkyil 'khor cho ga bya //
NG0201:5744: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum bri //
NG0201:5745: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi thod phreng bcas //
NG0201:5746: gru chad sgo bzhi ldan pa la //
NG0201:5747: dur khrod rgyan dang ldan pa la //
NG0201:5749: sgo bzhi gru gsum re re bri //
NG0201:5750: de nas mchog gi phur pa dgu //
NG0201:5751: srog bdag dgu yi sngags bris la //
NG0201:5752: dbus su dkar po snying 'byin dgod //
NG0201:5753: rgyan dang cha lugs gsal bar bskyed //
NG0201:5754: shar phyogs rtsibs la khu le dgod //
NG0201:5755: lho yi rtsibs la ag ge dgod //
NG0201:5756: nub kyi rtsibs la ug ge dgod //
NG0201:5757: byang gi rtsibs la drang ze dgod //
NG0201:5758: shang ze shar la da khod lho //
NG0201:5759: ne khod nub la nyi zla byang *//
NG0201:5760: de ltar sgo bzhir dgod par bya //
NG0201:5761: 'khor gzhong dung phor bse gab tu //
NG0201:5762: snying sna tshogs kyi gtor ma bsham //
NG0201:5763: lug dkar snying srog ma bral ba //
NG0201:5764: srog rtsa'i nang du ming rus gzhug / snying rtse
NG0201:5765: gyen du bstan la gzhag / dar dkar tshil gyis
NG0201:5766: kha bcad la // dbus su srog bdag nyid la
NG0201:5767: gzhag / shar du khrag sna'i gtor ma gzhag lho
NG0201:5768: ru sha sna'i gtor ma gzhag / nub tu rus
NG0201:5769: pa'i gtor ma gzhag / byang du mkhal ma'i gtor
NG0201:5770: ma gzhag / de nas sgo bzhi'i gtor ma yang
NG0201:5771: kha bcad la // *// shar sgor mchin pa sna
NG0201:5772: tshogs gzhag / lho sgor sha chen 'bru sna gzhag
NG0201:5773: / nub sgor mcher pa sna tshogs gzhag / byang
NG0201:5774: sgor tshil bu sna tshogs gzhag / gtor ma de
NG0201:5776: bshos bu mkhyid re btsugs la gzhag / de la smyug rgod re la yang *//
NG0201:5777: phod dkar pags bu dkar po dang *//
NG0201:5778: ming byang re yang btags la gzhag / phyogs ma nor bar gzhag pa yang *//
NG0201:5779: man 'jil steng du gzhag par bya //
NG0201:5780: shar du lug dkar lho ru ra //
NG0201:5781: nub tu byang dkar byang du khyi //
NG0201:5782: bag zan gzugs byas dkar por bsgyur //
NG0201:5783: sems can dngos su yod na rab //
NG0201:5784: med na gang rung gcig gi sker //
NG0201:5785: ming rus bris te gdags par bya //
NG0201:5787: dam sri'i gzugs dang ming rus gzhug / sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma la //
NG0201:5788: tsil chen zhal khebs yod pa la //
NG0201:5789: rak+ta'i gsang nan chas pa gcig / dkyil 'khor byang
NG0201:5790: shar mtshams su gzhag / ting 'dzin rnams gsum gsal
NG0201:5791: bar bsgom // gzhal yas gdan bcas spyan drang bskyed //
NG0201:5792: bdag nyid gshed por gsal bsgom la //
NG0201:5793: rgyal po 'khor bcas gsal bar bsgoms //
NG0201:5794: spyan drang bzhugs mchod tshul bzhin bya //
NG0201:5795: rtag tu snying po 'di yang bzlas //
NG0201:5796: om 'bar sha ma ha ra dza swa ha /
NG0201:5797: om khu le ma ha be ra ma swa ha /
NG0201:5798: a+om ag ge ru rta swa ha /
NG0201:5799: om ug ge ma le swa ha /
NG0201:5800: om drang ze ba b+ha swa ha /
NG0201:5803: om da khod pi pi pha ra swa ha /
NG0201:5804: om ni khod ba ra hi ti swa ha /
NG0201:5805: om sur+ya tsan+d+ra ma ha khu le swa ha /
NG0201:5806: de ni rtsa ba'i drag sngags te /
NG0201:5807: grub rtags sku yang dngos su ston //
NG0201:5808: me dang 'od dang sgra yang ston //
NG0201:5809: sgra dang byi la seng ge 'bag / dge bshes btsad po lta bu dang *//
NG0201:5810: dmag dpon lta bur ston par nges //
NG0201:5811: rgyal po drag tu sngags 'dis rbad //
NG0201:5812: om ma ha dra ma rak+sha rak+ta tsa ra mu
NG0201:5813: tra ma ha ni te tso ka tsa la bing
NG0201:5814: bing dgra bo ma ra ya hab hab /
NG0201:5816: lha dang dbye ba drag po'i sngags 'dis dbral //
NG0201:5817: ma ha sa ma ya rak+sha ma ha ra dza thun thun phrol phrol //
NG0201:5818: de nas bsgrub pa thon nas kyang *//
NG0201:5819: gsad pa'i phur pas gdab pa ni //
NG0201:5820: dbus nas phyung la 'di skad do //
NG0201:5822: khro bdag chen po snying 'byin gyis //
NG0201:5823: dpa' bo chen por dbang bskur bas //
NG0201:5824: dgra snying dkar nag mtshams su gdab //
NG0201:5825: btab nas myur du brlag gyur cig / ki li ki la ya tsit+ta mugs //
NG0201:5828: khro bdag chen po khu le shod //
NG0201:5829: gsod pa'i phur par byin brlabs te //
NG0201:5830: phrag khyim g.yas dang g.yon du gdab //
NG0201:5831: btab pas khrag skam myur du gsod //
NG0201:5832: badzra mu ti tsa sha rak+ta rngubs lhan //
NG0201:5834: khro bdag srog bdag ag ge yang *//
NG0201:5835: 'gugs pa'i bdag por mnga' gsol nas //
NG0201:5836: nu ma g.yas dang g.yon du gdab //
NG0201:5837: btab pas mkhris pa k+sha yas sod //
NG0201:5838: tsi li tsi li ma sa ma thibs thibs /
NG0201:5840: khro bdag sgrol ging ug ge yang *//
NG0201:5841: rno ba'i dpal du byin brlabs nas //
NG0201:5842: spyi bo'i btsug tu btab pas kyang *//
NG0201:5843: klad gzer mgo dang 'dar bus sod //
NG0201:5844: mas bu ta tshal pa tshal pa ka ru hum hum /
NG0201:5846: khro bdag shan pa drang ze yang *//
NG0201:5847: 'debs pa'i dpal du byin brlabs nas //
NG0201:5848: mkhal khung gnyis su gdab par bya //
NG0201:5849: btab pas chu 'gag sked nad sod //
NG0201:5850: bi ma la bi khu ya bim nad shad phat dza /
NG0201:5852: khro bdag srog gcod shang ze yang *//
NG0201:5853: zur gsum rtse mor byin brlabs te //
NG0201:5854: mchin pa pho gdung rtsa la gdab //
NG0201:5855: btab pas mchin nad khrag gis sod //
NG0201:5856: ma sa la khum ta ra la tshang pu re ra dgra bo ma ra ya dza /
NG0201:5858: khro bdag gsod dga' da khod kyang *//
NG0201:5859: thogs med 'debs par dbang bskur nas //
NG0201:5860: sha mtshan rmen bu'i dkyil du gdab /
NG0201:5861: btab pas sbos nad grum bus sod //
NG0201:5862: kha la ru tse kha mal sha phu phat dza /
NG0201:5864: dgra bla'i rgyal po mi khod kyang *//
NG0201:5865: rtse gsum ngar can rab 'byin bskyed //
NG0201:5866: mcher pa'i dbus su btab nas kyang *//
NG0201:5867: mcher nad lkugs nad smyo 'bog thong *//
NG0201:5868: me kha kha ru tse bag sha ru tra rag me mu ru mu ru phat dza /
NG0201:5870: gsang ba'i srog bdag nyi zla yang */
NG0201:5871: phur pa'i lha ru dbang bskur nas //
NG0201:5872: rkang pa'i mthil du gdab par bya //
NG0201:5873: zha grum smur nad 'theng grum gtong *//
NG0201:5874: 'ba' lu ba ga te rag sha kha khrag rngubs rngubs //
NG0201:5876: sngags btab nas thun sngags brab //
NG0201:5877: a+om ma ma ma ra ya thun b+h+yo /
NG0201:5878: ma ra ra tsa thun b+h+yo b+h+yo ma ha ba
NG0201:5879: ba ma ha de ba ma ha ru tra b+h+yo
NG0201:5880: b+h+yo / thun gyis brgyab ste brlan par 'gyur //
NG0201:5881: ling+ga gtubs la gtor mar stsal //
NG0201:5882: ri gsum rtse la yas stags bskyal //
NG0201:5883: rgyal po bsrung ba'i sngags ni //
NG0201:5884: om kha du she sha sha pra la ma ma ru tra /
NG0201:5886: srog bdag 'khor dang bcas las nor sgrub pa'i sngags la /
NG0201:5887: om dza ma be le she ba la go me sa srum srum trum trum swa ha /
NG0201:5888: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pas byes su gar 'gro yang dgra bgegs mi 'byung ba ni /
NG0201:5889: om nas ne nas ne ham shi ka ra ka
NG0201:5890: ra ma ra ma ra ru lu ru lu phat
NG0201:5891: phat b+ho b+ho / rgyal pos gal te bdag gam gzhan la 'tshe bar gyur na //
NG0201:5893: pu ma ha ra dza ba shan zhil zhil shan ting swa ha /
NG0201:5894: ma ha ra dza shan ting swa ha /
NG0201:5895: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pas rigs rgyud 'phrog pa dag rabs bcad pa'i sngags la //
NG0201:5896: om ma ha ka la gangs dre mo bdud rnams rngam rngam swa ha /
NG0201:5897: rgyal pos ye 'drog sum brgya drug cu dang thob shor gtong ba'i sngags la //
NG0201:5899: yam be ra srog rtsal kha sa kha sa me ru me ru swa ha /
NG0201:5900: rgyal pos ser ba 'bebs pa'i sngags la //
NG0201:5901: om phra ta phre sha thor b+h+yo /
NG0201:5904: kha shar rta be shar shar /
NG0201:5906: rgyal pos ltas ngan 'bebs pa'i sngags la //
NG0201:5907: om shar ging ram shag rgyug rgyug / ram rgyug
NG0201:5908: / srog la rgyug sha sha dgra bo'i snying la
NG0201:5909: sha / 'phru til ram khyer sod srog rgyal pos
NG0201:5910: ya cha stab bsnol gtong ba'i sngags la /
NG0201:5911: om ma ha brag shing kha me ru kha la
NG0201:5912: a tsi ma sha dgra bo phrol phrol shig b+h+yo
NG0201:5913: / zhes sngags kyi don bstan las rnams 'grub /
NG0201:5914: gang la bya yang thogs pa med /
NG0201:5915: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:5916: rgyal po gsang bar bsgrub pa'i smyo 'bog gi skabs
NG0201:5917: te nga gcig pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan
NG0201:5919: 'gal ba cham la dbab slad du //
NG0201:5920: gnod sbyin gdug pa'i zla gsang gsungs pa //
NG0201:5921: dad pa gsum ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NG0201:5922: dam tshig rang gi srog bzhin bsrung *//
NG0201:5923: bla ma mnyes pa'i rim gro bya //
NG0201:5924: dur khrod nags tshal dgon par 'gro //
NG0201:5926: bsod nams tshogs kyi yan lag bsag / ma nyes dpang gzug glud gtor gtang *//
NG0201:5927: gnod sbyin 'di nyid bsgrub par bya //
NG0201:5928: lcang lo can gyi pho brang na //
NG0201:5929: las grub rigs kyi zhing khams nas //
NG0201:5930: gnod sbyin bye ba sa ya gnas //
NG0201:5931: de dag nang nas dregs pa'i sku //
NG0201:5932: mthu stobs ldan pa'i gang bzang bsgrub //
NG0201:5933: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi khri brtsegs la //
NG0201:5934: steng du gnod sbyin sku gzugs bzhag / tsan+dan rigs las 'bur du brkos //
NG0201:5935: chu zheng gab ba gel gel po //
NG0201:5936: sku mdog sngon po gzi ldan pa //
NG0201:5939: ut+pal sngon po'i phreng bas mdzes //
NG0201:5940: g.yas na shing tog dmar po bsnams //
NG0201:5941: g.yon na mi lpags rgyal mtshan bsnams / gzas pa'i
NG0201:5942: gzugs byas snying gar gzhug / de yi dbus su
NG0201:5943: dong gru gsum // rtse mo byang du bltas pa la //
NG0201:5944: nang du khrag dang sol bas byug / til gyi phye la dgra yi gzugs //
NG0201:5945: mi khrag bla dgas bris la gzhug / zhabs mas bril la tshon skud bcings //
NG0201:5946: gru gsum brus pa'i nang du gzhug / mtha' ma
NG0201:5947: rtsang gis bskor te gzhag / gzugs kyi ske nas
NG0201:5948: sngo dmar gdags // sne gcig sku yi zhabs la gdags //
NG0201:5949: sngags pa'i mdun du dam rdzas dgram //
NG0201:5950: la phug rus phye ske tshe la //
NG0201:5951: de bzhin gtor ma byas te gzhag / nyung nag lan tshwa dug tu sbyar //
NG0201:5952: gzugs la brab cing ngan sngags bzlas //
NG0201:5954: de bzhin rim pas las rnams bya //
NG0201:5955: dur khrod ras la 'khor lo ni //
NG0201:5956: dug khrag sbyar bas bri bar bya //
NG0201:5957: rim pa bzhin du drag sngags dgod //
NG0201:5958: spyan drang bzhugs mchod bstod pa bya //
NG0201:5959: phrin las bcol zhing gnad nas bskul //
NG0201:5960: lha dang phral zhing rdzas kyis bdug / drag sngags
NG0201:5961: bzlas shing 'khor lo gzhug / bsad pa las kyi
NG0201:5962: sbyor la 'jug / mnan bsreg 'phang ba gsum la
NG0201:5963: gtad // dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:5964: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang las /
NG0201:5965: gang ba bzang po phyi ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te
NG0201:5966: nga gnyis pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan
NG0201:5967: 'das gshin rje gshed pos gang ba bzang po nang
NG0201:5969: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum la //
NG0201:5970: zla gam gsum gyis bskor ba bri //
NG0201:5971: dmar smug me ri ra bas bskor //
NG0201:5972: dbus su gshed po yab yum ste //
NG0201:5973: mdun du gang ba bzang po dgod //
NG0201:5974: mtshan ldan thod pa dum gsum du //
NG0201:5975: la phug rus pa'i phye ma dang *//
NG0201:5976: snying sna khrag sna sbyar la gzhag / dbus kyi gru gsum mthur du bskor //
NG0201:5977: nang du rabs chad thod pa gzhug / nyung nag nyung dkar lan tshwa dang *//
NG0201:5978: dug dang sme khrag sbyang bas dgang *//
NG0201:5979: dmigs pa'i ming rus ji bzhin byas //
NG0201:5980: thod pa'i nang du gzhug par bya //
NG0201:5981: dur khrod grong khyer bcom nas kyang *//
NG0201:5982: mtshan ma'i ras blangs skyang nul bya //
NG0201:5983: ldong ros chu rtsa ser pos phyung *//
NG0201:5984: dug khrag sbyar nas 'khor lo bri //
NG0201:5985: de bzhin yi ge dgod byas la //
NG0201:5986: thun gyi thod pa kha yang bcad //
NG0201:5987: de nas rim pas las rnams bya //
NG0201:5990: grub pa'i gnod sbyin chen po spyan 'dren na //
NG0201:5991: bye ba sa ya'i 'khor dang rab chas te //
NG0201:5992: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NG0201:5993: e h+ya hi rak+sha ba sna ba bi sa ma ya ho ha /
NG0201:5994: gser ltar rab tu bstan pa'i ri ngos la //
NG0201:5995: rma bya rab gnas gser du snang ba ltar //
NG0201:5998: grub pa'i dbang po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0201:5999: brtan par bzhugs shig gnod sbyin mchog / rin chen gcal bkram sa gzhi la //
NG0201:6001: khri chen dpangs la brtan par bzhugs //
NG0201:6002: sa ma ya tish+tha lhan s+t+wam //
NG0201:6003: gser dang bcas pa'i skyems phud ma nyams pa //
NG0201:6004: dung chen snod du sbyar nas mchod par 'bul //
NG0201:6005: dar gyi lhab lhub glu \u0f84gar rol mo bcas //
NG0201:6006: bsam pa dag pas sbyar nas mchod pa dbul //
NG0201:6007: dril bu sgra snyan spos dang dri //
NG0201:6008: mar me bshos dang gtor ma khrag / mos pas 'bul lo bzhes su gsol /
NG0201:6009: om ra ra so pa ba'u pu tsa kra ma pu tsa ho ha /
NG0201:6010: de nas gsang sngags rab bzlas la /
NG0201:6011: om ba hu ri rta dza /
NG0201:6012: ma d+ha la bag sha dza /
NG0201:6013: ra tra ma ru ru dza /
NG0201:6014: snying la shar shar ru dza /
NG0201:6015: srog la breng breng thum dza /
NG0201:6016: gnod sbyin sku dang 'od dang sgra //
NG0201:6017: sa g.yos thog dang char chen 'ong *//
NG0201:6018: gong gi rdzas kyis rab tu brdeg / thugs dam bskul te phrin las bcol //
NG0201:6019: dus drug sngags 'di gzugs la brdeg / om dza lam ma ha dza lam /
NG0201:6021: sti bu stud de pa lam bag sha swa ha /
NG0201:6022: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
NG0201:6023: thams cad grub pa'i sngags zhes brjod //
NG0201:6024: 'khor lo bcas kyi dam rdzas de //
NG0201:6025: byang bltas chu mig dogs sbas na //
NG0201:6026: khrag skyugs 'chi bar the tshom med //
NG0201:6027: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:6028: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang gang
NG0201:6029: ba bzang po nang du bsgrub pa'i skabs te nga
NG0201:6030: gsum pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das
NG0201:6031: gshin rje gshed pos gang ba bzang po gsang ba
NG0201:6033: dam tshig dbang sgo thub pa'i bus //
NG0201:6034: bla ma mnyes phyir yid 'thad dbul //
NG0201:6035: mi don ma yin rang don du //
NG0201:6036: bsgrub pa gong bzhin tshul bshams te //
NG0201:6037: de rting man ngag 'di bzhin bya //
NG0201:6038: a ka ru dang du ru ka / lug mig kar+sha pa na le //
NG0201:6039: sngags ni 'di dag rab tu brjod //
NG0201:6040: om dz+wa la ma ha dz+wa la /
NG0201:6041: yag sha bag sha so pu sdu de pa lam /
NG0201:6043: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
NG0201:6044: sngon du bsnyen pa sum 'bum bya //
NG0201:6045: lus bsrung sbyor ba 'di bzhin bya //
NG0201:6046: dpung pa dag la btags gyur na //
NG0201:6047: nad rnams thams cad byang bar 'gyur //
NG0201:6048: de nas gsad pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0201:6049: kar ni ka dang bal bu dang *//
NG0201:6050: 'u su rdo dreg sha ka ra //
NG0201:6051: ngang pa'i sgro la bskus nas kyang *//
NG0201:6052: gzugs la dus drug mchod byas te //
NG0201:6053: phyag byas bzlas pa byas gyur na //
NG0201:6054: longs spyod dpag med thob par 'gyur //
NG0201:6055: khrag dang nyung rgod rta mchin dang *//
NG0201:6056: ba lang dag la bzlas byin na //
NG0201:6057: rta bong la sogs mig zlum rnams //
NG0201:6059: tsit+ta rus pa gyo mog gsum //
NG0201:6060: sngags 'di bzlas nas byin gyur na //
NG0201:6061: om b+ha hu ri ri dza /
NG0201:6062: ma g+ha la bag sha dza /
NG0201:6063: ra ta ma ru ru dza /
NG0201:6064: snying la shar shar ru dza /
NG0201:6065: srog la breng breng thum dza /
NG0201:6069: bse dang ka ka ru la yang *//
NG0201:6070: sngags re bzlas te byin gyur na //
NG0201:6072: b+hi li ka dang a mar dang *//
NG0201:6073: bu+u ram yang ru ram sbyar te ri lu bya //
NG0201:6074: zla ba gzas zin dus su bya //
NG0201:6075: ling+ga byas te bsdums byas nas //
NG0201:6076: chu mig nang du thod par gnan //
NG0201:6078: bse zho btsan dug sbyar nas kyang *//
NG0201:6079: gsang sngags gong ma bzlas byas nas //
NG0201:6080: sha la reg pa'i gos la bsku /
NG0201:6081: lhog pa dkar pos 'chi bar nges //
NG0201:6083: yang na zha grum 'gro ma nus //
NG0201:6084: dang por khas blangs bzhin du bya //
NG0201:6085: phag pa spyang ki'i mche ba dang *//
NG0201:6086: wa yi ril ma spyang rtug par /
NG0201:6087: nyi ma gung ngam nam phyed na //
NG0201:6088: sum 'bum bzlas te don po yi //
NG0201:6091: srin rdo gdung chen sha ri ram //
NG0201:6092: de rnams thod pa dum gsum du //
NG0201:6093: yugs sa'i khrag la sbyar la stsal //
NG0201:6094: gong gi sngags bzlas lha rten sba //
NG0201:6096: 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:6097: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang las
NG0201:6098: gang ba bzang po gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs
NG0201:6099: te nga bzhi pa'o // // de nas yang bcom
NG0201:6101: 'gal ba cham la dbab slad du //
NG0201:6102: gdug pa klu yi zla gsang gsungs //
NG0201:6103: nub phyogs pho brang rgya mtsho'i chu //
NG0201:6104: ngo mtshar chu bo bzhi 'babs pa //
NG0201:6105: rab tu mi srun klu yi gnas //
NG0201:6106: de nyid dregs pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0201:6107: bcom ldan gshin rje gshed po yis //
NG0201:6108: lag na rdo rjer sku sprul te //
NG0201:6109: lag na rdo rje thugs khros te //
NG0201:6110: gser mig 'bar ba'i nga rgyal gyis //
NG0201:6111: gdug pa'i klu rnams bred 'gyur te //
NG0201:6112: rab tu mi srun klu rnams kyis //
NG0201:6114: kye ma'o rdo rje gzugs mdzes pa //
NG0201:6115: rab tu rngams pa'i rdo rje'i so //
NG0201:6116: lcags mchu 'bar ba rab tu brjid //
NG0201:6117: gser mig 'bar ba rab tu bgrad //
NG0201:6118: mgo la yid bzhin nor bus brgyan //
NG0201:6119: shes rab thabs ldan gshog pa brkyang *//
NG0201:6120: thabs ldan sder mo rnam par gdengs //
NG0201:6121: kye ma'o sku stod mchog gi g.yang gzhis brgyan //
NG0201:6122: sku smad sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan //
NG0201:6123: thod pa tshar gsum se ral kha //
NG0201:6124: rtsal 'phags khyad par de bzhin mthong *//
NG0201:6125: bdag cag rnams kyi dam tshig lha //
NG0201:6126: drag po'i cha byad zla las rgyal //
NG0201:6127: drag po chen po bka' bzhin bgyid //
NG0201:6128: zhes 'dzer zhing 'thon nas dam tshig smras te sku la 'khril lo //
NG0201:6129: na du tra sa na d+h+ri pa la du ba ni gar si ti swa ha /
NG0201:6130: de nas gser mig 'bar ba yis //
NG0201:6131: nga rgyal chen po bstan te /
NG0201:6132: dbang du bsdu phyir dam tshig phyag rgya bstan //
NG0201:6133: dang po gnyis ni nang du bsnol //
NG0201:6134: zla rnams rab tu skyong pa ste //
NG0201:6138: ta ki dza de byi dzahde hum ya hum ya /
NG0201:6139: hu lu hu lu pu ru te pu ru swa ha /
NG0201:6140: zhes brjod nas che ba rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0201:6141: de nas rigs bzhi'i klu rnams la //
NG0201:6142: rab tu che ba bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0201:6143: nyid kyi gzhal yas khang chen po //
NG0201:6144: rab tu brjid pa 'di nyid du //
NG0201:6145: byol song rigs bzhi dang thabs cig tu 'dug pa'i gnas 'di lta ste //
NG0201:6146: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus gnas 'bar //
NG0201:6147: ri rab mchod rten gzugs 'dra la //
NG0201:6148: bum pa yid bzhin lcang los brgyan //
NG0201:6149: sbrul gnyis dar 'phyang lta bus mdzes //
NG0201:6150: rigs bzhi'i rgyan gyis rab tu bklubs //
NG0201:6151: sgo bzhi ka brgyad rab tu ldan //
NG0201:6152: de 'og gsum gnyis rab tu mdzes //
NG0201:6153: byol song longs spyod rab tu ldan //
NG0201:6154: de nyid bum pa'i khong seng na //
NG0201:6155: gser mig 'bar ba dang thabs cig tu bzhugs pa 'di lta ste /
NG0201:6156: gzi brjid mtha' yas dung skyong dang *//
NG0201:6157: gang po nor ldan la sogs dang *//
NG0201:6158: dga' bo 'jog po ma dros dang *//
NG0201:6159: rigs bzhi'i gtso bo klu brgyad de //
NG0201:6160: sku la 'khril te rab tu gnas //
NG0201:6161: gyad nor med la sogs pa'i rgyan //
NG0201:6162: dar dpyang ma dang pad+ma'i rgyan //
NG0201:6163: gzi brjid ma dang dung can ma //
NG0201:6164: klu mo rigs bzhi la sogs pa dang thabs cig tu bzhugs so //
NG0201:6165: de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos gnyen po sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:6166: dgon pa dur khrod mtsho gling ngam //
NG0201:6167: chu mig nags na gnas pa'i bar //
NG0201:6169: dri spos sman gyis chag chag gdab //
NG0201:6170: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud ldan //
NG0201:6171: sgo bzhi rigs dang ldan pa bri //
NG0201:6172: dbus su lag na rdo rje ste //
NG0201:6173: 'khor lo bzhi la bya khyung bzhi //
NG0201:6174: gru chad mchod pa'i bum pa bzhi //
NG0201:6175: sman lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0201:6176: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0201:6177: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:6178: sgo la mchod pa'i gtor ma bzhi //
NG0201:6179: b+ha ma hasti bcas pa yi //
NG0201:6180: sor mo lnga yi bcangs pa'i rjes //
NG0201:6181: mkha' lding mchod pa'i rdzas su gzhag / de nas ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NG0201:6182: dang po stong pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0201:6183: gnyis pa snying rje 'byung ba dang *//
NG0201:6184: gsum pa rgyu yi rnam pa las //
NG0201:6185: bam gyi sa bon las byung ba'i //
NG0201:6186: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus su ni //
NG0201:6187: lam las ri rab rin chen bskyed //
NG0201:6188: de steng khrom las ga ru da /
NG0201:6189: rdo rje gshog pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0201:6190: bya khyung rgyal po bzhi byung bas //
NG0201:6191: dkar dang dmar dang ser dang ljang *//
NG0201:6192: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du bsgom //
NG0201:6193: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NG0201:6194: ye shes mkha' lding stobs po che //
NG0201:6196: dbu gsum rdo rje'i mchu khra la //
NG0201:6197: ring la dmar zhing spyan yang dmar //
NG0201:6198: zhal gdangs ral pa sprugs pa'i tshul //
NG0201:6199: ye shes gshog gdengs sku yang shin tu g.yo //
NG0201:6200: sku dang yan lag rin chen baidur brgyan //
NG0201:6201: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po 'khor @#//
NG0201:6203: bar pa lcags kyu tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0201:6204: g.yon gyi dang pos rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NG0201:6205: bar pa zhags pa tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0201:6206: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0201:6207: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po gzi brjid 'od po che //
NG0201:6208: dbu gsum mdog dmar ral pa lcang lor 'khyil //
NG0201:6209: zhal gdangs ye shes gshog pa chen po gdengs //
NG0201:6210: sku dang ye shes yan lag me chen 'bar //
NG0201:6211: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0201:6212: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma rin po che //
NG0201:6213: g.yon gyi dang po rdo rje pad+ma 'phyar //
NG0201:6214: bar ma zhags pa tha ma dbyug to bsnams //
NG0201:6215: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0201:6216: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po mi mgo can //
NG0201:6217: dbu gsum mdog ser ral pa gyen du 'khyil //
NG0201:6218: yan lag rin chen sku las me chen 'bar //
NG0201:6219: ye shes gshog pa rgya chen brkyang bskum mdzad //
NG0201:6220: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rin chen 'bar //
NG0201:6221: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma dpag bsam shing *//
NG0201:6222: g.yon gyi dang po ye shes ral gri 'phyar //
NG0201:6223: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0201:6224: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NG0201:6225: ye shes mkha' lding rlung gi shugs //
NG0201:6226: dbu gsum mdog ljang ral pa 'khyil //
NG0201:6227: sgra skad sna tshogs bzhad cing smin ma bskyod //
NG0201:6228: yan lag rin chen brgyan pas sku 'bar ba //
NG0201:6229: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po ral gri phyar //
NG0201:6230: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma shing thog bi ja pur //
NG0201:6231: g.yon gyi dang po 'khor lo 'bar ba bsnams //
NG0201:6232: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0201:6233: de rnams rtsa ba'i snying po khrom las bskyed //
NG0201:6234: de bzhin spyan drang bzhugs gsol phyag bya dang *//
NG0201:6235: mchod dang bstod dang bzlas pa tshul bzhin bya //
NG0201:6236: ba lim la sogs byed pa dang *//
NG0201:6237: b+ha ma hasti bcings pa yis //
NG0201:6238: sor mo lnga yis bcangs pa'i rjes //
NG0201:6239: zan chang dkar gsum 'bru dang sman gyis mchod //
NG0201:6240: om ra dza ma ha ga ru da /
NG0201:6241: hum ba lim pu tsa ba lim ta kha hi /
NG0201:6243: de nas sngags 'di rgyun du bzlas //
NG0201:6244: ong kam ong kam khyung ka ra khyung ka ra /
NG0201:6246: om badzra ma ha kro d+ha hum phat /
NG0201:6247: sngags de rtsa ba rgyun du drangs //
NG0201:6248: mkha' lding gso ba'i las byed na //
NG0201:6249: bdag gam gzhan la gdug pas 'jigs //
NG0201:6250: ga ru rgyal po mchod 'dod pas //
NG0201:6251: gnas sam khang pa'i sgo ngos te //
NG0201:6252: snum pa'i sa'am bag zan la //
NG0201:6253: ga ru da yi gzugs bcas te //
NG0201:6254: ba lim la sogs pu tsa dang *//
NG0201:6255: b+ha ma hasti bcings pa yi //
NG0201:6256: sor mo lnga yi pu tsa des //
NG0201:6257: ga ru da nyid la ni dbul //
NG0201:6258: snying po lnga po gang yang rung *//
NG0201:6259: gcig gis sna drangs brjod rt-ing la //
NG0201:6260: ga ru da gnyis brjod nas kyang *//
NG0201:6261: de rting pu dza rab tu brjod //
NG0201:6262: thog mar om dang swa has dbul /
NG0201:6263: 'di ltar gzhung bzhin byas nas ni //
NG0201:6264: ka la sha tas zin pa la //
NG0201:6265: grol bar 'gyur ba the tshom med //
NG0201:6266: de nas gnyen po rigs bzhi la //
NG0201:6270: rig sngags bdag po mthu stobs bdag po'i sku //
NG0201:6271: e ma'o phyag gi mthil na rdo rje 'bar 'dra bas //
NG0201:6272: zhal nas gsungs skad bton pas khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0201:6273: stong gsum drag tu g.yos pas klu chen pho mo 'dul //
NG0201:6274: mkha' lding rgyal po 'jigs byed ga ru da /
NG0201:6275: lcags kyu 'dab gshog chen po brgyang bas ni /
NG0201:6276: gser gyi 'od 'phro rlung sgra drag po yis //
NG0201:6277: rgya mtsho chen por kun tu brdabs pa yis //
NG0201:6278: klu rgyal 'khor dang bcas pa zil gyis gnon //
NG0201:6279: 'jigs byed gser gyi spyan rnon chen pos ni //
NG0201:6280: tshangs pa chen po'i yul sa rtse nas gnon //
NG0201:6281: gal te klu rnams dam las 'das gyur na //
NG0201:6282: rgya mtsho'i snying po rgya mtsho'i lbu ba la //
NG0201:6283: gshog pa chen po rgya mtshor byas nas ni //
NG0201:6284: klu rnams thams cad dbang du bsdus nas ni //
NG0201:6285: me yi snying po 'bar bas bsreg byas te //
NG0201:6286: lus ni rul myags dri ni nga bar 'gyur //
NG0201:6287: nad kyi rnam grangs mang pos 'debs pa dang *//
NG0201:6288: lus la nad ngan sha bkra 'byung bar 'gyur //
NG0201:6289: ga ru da tsa le tsa le hum phat /
NG0201:6290: hum nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po tshangs pa'i bya //
NG0201:6291: gser 'dab bya khyung ga ru da //
NG0201:6292: drang srong 'khor gyi stobs po che //
NG0201:6293: rigs gsum mgon po rdo rje rgyal //
NG0201:6294: mnga' ris 'khor du klu yis bskor //
NG0201:6295: rdo rje rnon po spu gri'i so gnyis gtsigs //
NG0201:6296: gser gyi spyan gnyis khro gnyer can //
NG0201:6297: thabs ldan rdo rje'i rwa gnyis brjid //
NG0201:6298: yid bzhin nor bu gtsug na 'bar //
NG0201:6299: lcags kyi mchu chen rno dbal gyis //
NG0201:6300: rab tu gdug pa'i klu rnams spyi nas 'dren //
NG0201:6301: rdo rje'i sder gshog brkyangs pa'i rlung mo ches //
NG0201:6302: klu rgyal gdug pa dbang du sdud par mdzad //
NG0201:6303: ces bstod de dbang du bsdu'o //
NG0201:6304: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:6305: gdug pa glu bsgrub kyi zla gsang gi skabs te
NG0201:6306: nga lnga pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan
NG0201:6307: 'das gshin rje gshed pos gdug pa klu bsgrub 'di
NG0201:6308: yang gsungs / mtsho 'gram chu mig shing gcig rkang *//
NG0201:6309: nags rdzongs mthug po dur khrod du //
NG0201:6311: ba las byung ba'i rnam pa lnga //
NG0201:6312: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga la byug / de nyid byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir //
NG0201:6313: hum sa ma ya om gyi sngags //
NG0201:6314: bya ba byed pas byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:6315: bdag nyid chen por rab brtags te //
NG0201:6316: thams cad grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0201:6317: bdag nyid spyi bor sa dmigs te //
NG0201:6318: bdag po bzhi yis dbang bskur ro //
NG0201:6319: rdo rje'i sbu gur ma bsams te //
NG0201:6320: g.yu bye'u sngon mos dbang bskur ro //
NG0201:6321: tri dang ya bsam dregs pas dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0201:6322: snying gar hum bskyed bdag dbang bskur //
NG0201:6323: lte bar om yig gnyen por ro //
NG0201:6324: de nas thig dang ri mo bri //
NG0201:6326: gru chad sgo rnams de bzhin bri //
NG0201:6327: lte ba mthing ga pad+ma dkar //
NG0201:6328: mu khyud dmar po gru chad @#//
NG0201:6330: sgo rnams ser po sgo 'bur rigs //
NG0201:6331: de bzhin tshon rnams dgye bar bya //
NG0201:6332: dbus su gnyen po dgod par bya //
NG0201:6333: pad+ma brgyad la klu chen brgyad //
NG0201:6334: rang rang rtsa ba'i sngags kyang bri //
NG0201:6335: rtsibs mchan de mi bri bar bya //
NG0201:6336: gru chad bzhi la klu mo bzhi //
NG0201:6337: na ba phu na gru chad la //
NG0201:6338: sgo 'bur ha sa tram ga rnams //
NG0201:6339: shar nas bskor te rim par dgod //
NG0201:6340: ces rgyun du bzlas pa'i yi ge dgu po 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:6341: hum na ga ra dza sa ma ya che ge mo zhig tsit+ta dz+wa la zhes bsgrub par bya'o //
NG0201:6342: zhag dgu bar du khrus byas te //
NG0201:6343: zas rnams lnga ni spang bar bya //
NG0201:6344: de nas grub pa'i rtags rnams ni //
NG0201:6345: dngos su longs spyod tshogs rnams 'byung *//
NG0201:6346: bar ni bas ldag thor ba 'byung *//
NG0201:6347: de nyid mngon du gyur tshe'o //
NG0201:6348: rig pa'i sham du gdags par bya //
NG0201:6349: smi ti gi ti las la gzud //
NG0201:6350: ces don thams cad grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0201:6351: dbang bskur bar bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:6352: dar dkar gzhi ma btings nas ni //
NG0201:6354: dkar po la sogs mu khyud ldan //
NG0201:6355: dbus su dam tshig sa bon sa na 'dra min 'dug sa ha dgod //
NG0201:6356: de nas yid 'ong bum pa la //
NG0201:6357: bdun pa dgu pa'i ri mo bri //
NG0201:6358: dge bsnyen gnyis por rab tu dmigs //
NG0201:6359: kha dog tshang ba'i ras kyis bcings //
NG0201:6360: rma bya 'om bu bra ma dang *//
NG0201:6361: drag po'i rdzas la bdug par bya //
NG0201:6362: ras la sogs pa'i gzungs thag gdags //
NG0201:6363: sder gshog phyag rgya snying gar bstan //
NG0201:6364: sman lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0201:6365: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0201:6366: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:6367: a+om ahhum na ga yu lu /
NG0201:6368: na ga yu ru dz+wa la ni /
NG0201:6369: na ga sa ma ya swa ha /
NG0201:6370: dmigs pa'i yan lag gsum pa'i rgyud //
NG0201:6371: yi ge rtsa gcig sbrul par bshad //
NG0201:6372: hum skyes bdag po gnyis nas sprul //
NG0201:6373: yan lag yi ge rtsa gcig las //
NG0201:6374: 'od zer sna tshogs bdud rtsir sprul //
NG0201:6375: yi ge dmigs pa'i gnas lnga ru //
NG0201:6376: bdud rtsi bum pa brtan par bya //
NG0201:6377: mkha' lding rgyal po de nyid bsam //
NG0201:6378: de nyid gtsang ma'i ras kyis dkris //
NG0201:6379: gur gum sman nam chus bsres bkru //
NG0201:6380: de bzhin ma smin zas rnams bza' //
NG0201:6382: kye ma'o rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bdag / bdag gi dam tshig mngon dga' bas //
NG0201:6384: khyod kyi dam tshig gtso lags kyi //
NG0201:6385: longs spyod klu yi pho brang nas //
NG0201:6386: rigs pa'i rgyal pos dbang bskur cig / ces gsol to //
NG0201:6387: nyon cig skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NG0201:6388: longs spyod klu yi rigs kyis 'grub //
NG0201:6389: pho brang yid 'ong mngon dga' nas //
NG0201:6390: rab tu gdug pa'i klu rnams la //
NG0201:6391: yid bzhin rin chen rab gnas pas //
NG0201:6392: de ring khyod kyis bcang bar gyis //
NG0201:6394: de nas yang bar chad bsal ba'i phyir //
NG0201:6395: rma byas brdeg cing gu gul bdug / ces gsungs so //
NG0201:6396: snying po rigs bzhi dbu rgyan @#//
NG0201:6398: dar gyi cod pan me tog phreng *//
NG0201:6399: longs spyod tshogs gyi zhal zas dang *//
NG0201:6400: rten gyi bum pas dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0201:6401: de nas dam tshig rten 'brel gyi snying po 'di sbyin par bya'o //
NG0201:6402: rigs ldan thogs med rgyug pa yi //
NG0201:6403: sngags ldan sngags kyi bdag po khyod //
NG0201:6404: de ring dam tshig 'di zung la //
NG0201:6405: yid bzhin rin chen gter bzhin chongs //
NG0201:6406: nam mkha'i dngos po mi gnas la //
NG0201:6408: snang med sprul ba'i ngo bo las //
NG0201:6409: rnam shes ldan pa'i thogs med ni //
NG0201:6410: rnam shes sku yi ngo bo las //
NG0201:6411: yi ge phreng ba nyid du bkod //
NG0201:6412: na ga li li hri la pa tri sni ra /
NG0201:6414: tri ya ku ru pa tri yam /
NG0201:6415: he he hum hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0201:6416: zhes rten 'brel gyi snying pos yongs su rdzogs par bya'o //
NG0201:6417: de bsgrub bar du klu las gad mi bya //
NG0201:6418: de yi sbyor ba yongs su rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:6419: klu yi sbyor ba tshang bar bsag par bya //
NG0201:6420: 'di ni dang por sngon du rab tu gces //
NG0201:6421: de nas klu yi sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:6422: na ga gnas shing gar na gnas pa'i sa //
NG0201:6423: de yi drung nas 'jam pa'i sa blangs la //
NG0201:6424: sa gnyen sbyin po dag dang mnyam bsres la //
NG0201:6425: klu yi ra dza de yi gzugs byas la //
NG0201:6426: lus bcu mgo gcig sbrul mgo bdun gyis brgyan //
NG0201:6427: g.yas na rin chen 'bar ba'i bum pa thogs //
NG0201:6428: kha dog mthing ga lus kyis chu srin mnan //
NG0201:6429: pho yi yi ge 'di ni 'di yi rgyu yin te //
NG0201:6430: na ga ra dza su ki ni s+t+wam shes de bzhin bskyed la //
NG0201:6431: na ga ra dza ba su gi ni dza dza /
NG0201:6433: de ltar gsal nas nyi shu pa nyid rtag par bzlas //
NG0201:6434: ji ltar nus bzhin du mang bzlas te //
NG0201:6435: de ltar bzlas tshe gzugs de ga bur gzhug / gzhan gyis mi mthong rang gi spyod yul nyid //
NG0201:6436: rtags dang mtshan ma rang rang gzugs su 'byung *//
NG0201:6437: bzlas pas skyo na mchod pa dbul par bya //
NG0201:6438: na ga ra dza'i gzugs la thim par bsam //
NG0201:6439: de nas gtad pa'i las byed 'dod na //
NG0201:6440: bdag nyid mthu stobs bdag por bsam byas la //
NG0201:6441: thugs kar mkha' lding ra dza gsal byas te //
NG0201:6442: chu gtor mngar dang ldan pa sbyin byas la //
NG0201:6443: seng ldeng phur pa bdag 'dra bsam //
NG0201:6444: de yi gsang sngags nyid kyi byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:6445: bdag gis de nyid dril zhing na gar bsdig / ka la ru pa tsag tshag dam dam //
NG0201:6446: brgya'am stong du bzlas pa byas nas ni //
NG0201:6447: gsang sngags 'di yis gtad par bya bar gsungs //
NG0201:6448: a+om na ga ra dza dzahhum bam hoh /
NG0201:6449: che ge mo a kar+sha ya a kar+sha ya hum /
NG0201:6452: na ga chings na ga chings /
NG0201:6453: na ga sdom na ga sdom /
NG0201:6454: de skad ces ni lan gnyis brjod //
NG0201:6455: mi 'di bdun rgyud rtsa ba chod //
NG0201:6458: gdug pa klu yis dgra 'di ma bsad na //
NG0201:6459: phyag na rdo rje rang gi mgo 'gems so //
NG0201:6460: khong nas snying khrag 'dzag par byed //
NG0201:6463: de nas gnan pa'i sngags 'di gsungs //
NG0201:6464: mdze thod dam pha mes kyi thod pa ru //
NG0201:6465: ming dang rus bcug sngo dmar skud pas bcings //
NG0201:6466: bud med zhabs mas gtums la khyim gyi gting du sba //
NG0201:6467: nub sgor kha bltas khyim gyi bdag po la //
NG0201:6468: ba dmar glang dmar 'bri yi rwa co'i nang *//
NG0201:6469: ming rus 'chi rkyen gang 'dod bris pa de //
NG0201:6470: lto phye sbal lcong lto ru bcug nas ni //
NG0201:6471: hum gis mtha' sgor ba ni tshig mi bya //
NG0201:6472: kun la gang 'dod 'chi rkyen bris te sba /
NG0201:6473: om lam sum lam pra ti sna nan ti ste ti sta /
NG0201:6474: om che ge mo lam nan /
NG0201:6477: om nam nam ti khas bye'u char khas /
NG0201:6481: na ga pu ka na ga pu ka / na ga lam na ga lam swa ha /
NG0201:6482: bdag la mi tshugs bya phyir gang mi smos //
NG0201:6483: gnon pa'i rkang pa rdo rje rgya gram bsam //
NG0201:6484: sa brko rang gi gri'am rab tu spang *//
NG0201:6485: ma nyes dpang gzug lha srin dbang du bsdu //
NG0201:6486: de ltar byas na las rnams nges par 'grub //
NG0201:6487: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:6488: gdug pa klu nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te nga drug pa'o ///

NG0201:6500: che ge mo sa ma ya dza dza /

NG0201:6529: na ga ku ma ra b+h+yo //

NG0201:6560: ma mo la sogs pa 'dus pa phal mo che

NG0201:6568: dpa' brtul myur ba'i shugs kyis dregs pa sgrol //
